(212, 'Cch n tp, lm bi thi tt nghip THPT mn Ton hiu qu', 'cach-on-tp-lam-bai-thi-tt-nghip-thpt-mon-toan-hiu-qu', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: black;">(<span style="font-size: 10pt;">GD&T)-Thc s Nguyn Sn H  Trng THPT Chuyn i hc S phm H Ni c nhng lu  rt chi tit gip hc sinh n tp v lm bi thi mn Ton tt nghip THPT 2012 mt cch hiu qu nht.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I. Hng dn chung v vic n tp v lm bi thi</span></strong><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"><br /> <img style="float: left;" src="data/giaoduc/hocsinh/hocsinh.jpg" alt="alt" height="238" width="318" /><br />  Khi n tp cn ch : Nh cng thc, hiu phng php gii cc dng bi tp, vn dng kin thc  suy lun v tnh ton chnh xc trong cc tnh hung c th. Khi lm bi thi cn ch  tiu ch 3 : ng kt qu,  , trnh by p<br /> <br /> <em><b><span style="font-family: Arial;">1. Hng dn n tp</span></b></em><br /> <br /> - Nh v hiu c tt c cc cng thc trong Sch gio khoa THPT lp 12, bit vn dng vo cc bi tp c th.<br /> <br /> - n tp h thng cc dng ton trong sch gio khoa v sch bi tp mn Ton lp 12<br /> <br /> - S dng ti liu Hng dn n tp thi tt nghip THPT nm hc 2011  2012 ca Nh xut bn gio dc<br /> <br /> - Tham kho mt s  thi tt nghip THPT mn ton nhng nm gn y  bit mc  kin thc ca mt  thi tt nghip THPT.<br /> <br /> - Tham kho cu trc  thi tt nghip mn Ton ca B gio dc nm 2010<br /> <br /> - Tham kho ni dung gim ti mn ton THPT c B gio dc v o to thng bo u nm hc 2011-2012<br /> <br /> - Tham kho p n v thang im ca  thi tt nghip THPT nhng nm gn y  rt kinh nghim trong vic trnh by.<br /> <br /> - Mc d trng tm kin thc thi tt nghip tp trung  chng trnh lp 12 nhng phn ln cc bi ton THPT u lin quan n vic rt gn mt biu thc, gii phng trnh v bt phng trnh bc nht, gii phng trnh v bt phng trnh bc hai, gii h phng trnh, gii phng trnh cha du gi tr tuyt i, gii phng trnh cha n  mu, gii phng trnh v t, gii bt phng trnh v t, gii phng trnh v bt phng trnh tch. Hc sinh cn phi nm vng cc kin thc, k nng ni trn v mt s kin thc lin quan c hc  cc lp 7, 8, 9, 10 nh: quy tc ph ngoc, quy tc nhn hai a thc, quy tc chia a thc cho a thc (tnh hung thng gp l chia tam thc bc hai cho nh thc bc nht), nh l v du ca nh thc bc nht, nh l v du ca tam thc bc hai.<br /> <br /> <em><b><span style="font-family: Arial;">2. Hng dn lm bi thi</span></b></em><br /> <br /> - Hc sinh cn phi ch  tiu ch 3 : ng   - p trong mt bi thi: kt qu ng,  , trnh by p. Thang im ca bi thi thng c t bn cnh p s ca mi php ton. Nu hc sinh tnh ton sai hoc vit nhm th mt rt nhiu im. Nu hc sinh vit sai  phn no th s mt im ton b phn sau  khi c lin quan vi nhau v ni dung.<br /> <br /> + Hc sinh phi vit ng cc cng thc ton, vit ng cc k hiu ton, <br /> <br /> rt gn ng cc biu thc v kt qu ng  tt c cc php ton. <br /> <br /> + Hc sinh phi trnh by  ; cc bi ton thi tt nghip bm st ni dung sch gio khoa v u c quy trnh gii, v vy hc sinh phi trnh by y  cc  trong quy trnh gii mt bi ton nh: quy trnh kho st v v  th hm s, quy trnh tm gi tr ln nht v nh nht ca hm s trn mt tp hp, quy trnh tnh tch phn bng phng php i bin...Thang im ca bi thi s cn c vo cc bc trong quy trnh gii ton, nu hc sinh trnh by  cc  th s khng b mt im. Ngoi ra, hc sinh cn phi c p s hoc kt lun trong li gii mi bi ton v biu im thng c 0,25 im  phn kt lun, p s.<br /> <br /> +  t im cao, hc sinh phi trnh by p, din t tt, cc  r rng. Thang im ca bi thi thng c sau mi suy lun logic hoc sau mi php bin i, tnh gi tr biu thc... V vy, sau mi suy lun logic hoc bin i, tnh ton biu thc; hc sinh nn xung dng, chia  r rng. Trnh tnh trng vit li gii mt bi ton nh vit mt on vn, khi  nu hc sinh sai  dng cui cng th c th b mt nhiu im. <br /> <br /> - t iu kin v kim tra iu kin: Khi vit mi biu thc ton hc, nu gp biu thc cha n  mu, biu thc cha cn bc hai, biu thc logarit, hc sinh cn c thi quen t iu kin  cc biu thc c ngha. Ngoi ra, vi biu din i s ca s phc z=a+bi ta phi iu kin a, b l cc s thc. Trc khi kt lun p s bi ton, hc sinh cn c thi quen kim tra li iu kin.<br /> <br /> - Lm bi d  cng c tinh thn: Hc sinh cn c  thi vi lt, chn bi d lm trc v vit ngay vo bi thi, khi trnh by c vo bi thi, tinh thn lm bi ca hc sinh s tt hn. Bi kho st v v  th hm s l bi c sn quy trnh gii v lun xut hin trong cc k thi tt nghip THPT, hc sinh c th lm ngay bi kho st trc. Nu hc sinh lm bi kh khng ra kt qu th c th mt tinh thn lm bi.<br /> <br /> <strong><span style="font-family: Arial;">II. Hng dn n tp tng ch </span></strong><br /> <br /> <em><b><span style="font-family: Arial;">1. Ch  ng dng o hm  kho st v v  th ca hm s.</span></b></em></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial; color: black;">Hc sinh<em><span style="font-family: Arial;"> </span></em>cn nm vng cc vn  sau y:<br /> <br /> - Quy trnh kho st v v  th cc hm s: hm a thc bc ba, hm trng phng, hm phn thc bc nht trn bc nht. Trong phn ny, hc sinh cn luyn tp nhiu k nng tnh o hm, xt du o hm, lp bng bin thin ca hm s. Biu im thng tp trung vo cc mc quan trng nh: tp xc nh, nghim ca o hm, du ca o hm, cc tr, cc khong n iu, gii hn v tim cn (nu c), bng bin thin, tnh i xng ca  th hm trng phng, giao im ca  th vi trc Oy, v ng dng ca  th hm s v cc im c bit, cc ng tim cn (nu c). Vi hm phn thc bc nht trn bc nht, cn ch  rng gii hn ca hm s khi x dn n v cc s bng mt hng s thc (khng c nhm ln l hm s c gii v cc khi x dn n v cc)<br /> <br /> - Cc dng tip tuyn: tip tuyn ti mt im c hong  cho trc,tip tuyn ti mt im c tung  cho trc, tip tuyn i qua mt im cho trc, tip tuyn c h s gc cho trc, tip tuyn song song hoc vung gc vi mt ng thng cho trc. Khi lp phng trnh tip tuyn, ta thng phi lp phng trnh  tm honh  ca tip im. Tm iu kin  mt ng thng tip xc vi  th hm s<br /> <br /> - Cc dng tim cn ca  th hm s: tim cn ng, tim cn ngang.<br /> <br /> - S lin h gia s giao im ca ng thng v  th hm s vi s nghim thc phn bit ca phng trnh honh  giao im. Quan st s im chung ca ng thng y=m vi  th y=f(x)  bin lun s nghim thc ca phng trnh f(x)=m hoc xt s nghim thc ca phng trnh  suy ra s giao im.<br /> <br /> - Du hiu nhn bit hm s ng bin, hm s nghch bin trn mt khong xc nh; iu kin  hm s ng bin, nghch bin trn mt khong xc nh.<br /> <br /> - Cc iu kin  hm s c cc tr: iu kin cn  hm s t cc tr, iu kin   hm s t cc i, cc tiu. Tm iu kin  hm s t cc i hoc cc tiu ti mt im cho trc.<br /> <br /> - Phng php tm gi tr ln nht v gi tr nh nht ca hm s trn mt tp hp s (on, khong, na khong). Kho st trc tip hm s ban u hoc hoc kho st gin tip hm s ca bin mi (i bin).<br /> <br /> - Phng php vn dng tnh n iu ca hm s  chng minh bt ng thc, gii phng trnh, h phng trnh.<br /> <br /> <em><b><span style="font-family: Arial;">2. Ch  Hm s ly tha, hm s m v hm s logarit. </span></b></em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial; color: black;">Hc sinh cn nm vng cc vn  sau:<br /> <br /> - iu kin xc nh ca biu thc logarit.<br /> <br /> - o hm ca hm ly tha, hm s m v hm s logarit.<br /> <br /> - Cc phng php bin i tng ng gii phng trnh, bt phng trnh m, logarit: phng php a v cng c s, phng php logarit ha; mt s phng trnh c bit c th c chuyn v phng trnh tch, bt phng trnh tch.<br /> <br /> - Phng php t n ph gii phng trnh, bt phng trnh m, logarit.<br /> <br /> - Phng php s dng tnh n iu ca hm s  gii phng trnh, bt phng trnh logarit<br /> <br /> - Phng php th, phng php t n ph gii h phng trnh m, logarit.<br /> <br /> <em><b><span style="font-family: Arial;">3. Ch  Nguyn hm, tch phn v ng dng. </span></b></em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial; color: black;">Hc sinh cn nm vng cc vn  sau:<br /> <br /> - Cc cng thc o hm c gii thiu trong Sch gio khoa lp 11.<br /> <br /> - Bng nguyn hm, tch phn ca mt s hm s thng gp: Hm ly tha, hm s m, hm s logarit, hm s lng gic<br /> <br /> - Nh cc biu thc vi phn ca sinx, cosx, tanx, cotx, ex, lnx, xk <br /> <br /> - Phng php i bin s tnh nguyn hm, tch phn: Ch  i bin s ng thi vi i vi phn, vi bi ton tnh tch phn th i bin s ng thi vi i vi phn v i cn. Ch : vi phn v cn phi c vit tng ng vi bin di du nguyn hm, tch phn.<br /> <br /> - Phng php ly nguyn hm tng phn, tch phn tng phn. Nu biu thc di du nguyn hm tch phn c mt trong dng (ax+b)sinnx, (ax+b)cosnx, (ax+b)emx+n th ta chn u=ax+b, nu biu thc trong nguyn hm tch phn c dng (ax2+bx+c)lnx th ta chn u=lnx; trong cc trng hp trn, chn dv l thnh phn cn li di du nguyn hm, tch phn.<br /> <br /> - Vi nguyn hm, tch phn ca hm lng gic, hc sinh cn ch  cng thc lng gic bin tch thnh tng, cng thc nhn i, cng thc h bc (Sch gio khoa lp 10). <br /> <br /> - ng dng tch phn tnh din tch hnh phng.  lm tt phn ny, hc sinh cn rn k nng tnh tch phn ca hm cha du gi tr tuyt i; k nng xt du ca biu thc bc nht, biu thc bc hai, phn thc hu t bc nht trn bc nht. Hc sinh cn ch  vit ng cng thc tnh din tch thng qua tch phn ca hm cha du gi tr tuyt i sau  tu thuc vo hon cnh c th mi ph du gi tr tuyt i hoc chuyn v gi tr tuyt i ca tch phn. <br /> <br /> - ng dng tch phn tnh th tch ca khi trn xoay: Hc sinh cn ch  hng ng thc ng nh: bnh phng mt tng, bnh phng mt hiu. Nu xoay hnh quanh trc Ox th dng vi phn dx, nu xoay hnh quanh trc Oy th dng vi phn dy<br /> <br /> <em><b><span style="font-family: Arial;">4. Ch  s phc. Hc sinh cn nm vng nhng vn  sau:</span></b></em><br /> <br /> - Dng i s ca s phc, phn thc v phn o ca s phc, s phc lin hp ca mt s phc, m un ca s phc, iu kin  mt s phc l s thc, iu kin  mt s phc l s o. Ch : Khi vit dng i s z=a+bi ta phi c iu kin a, b l cc s thc. <br /> <br /> - Php ton gia hai s phc. Ta c th p dng tnh cht ca s phc tng t nh i vi s thc  l: tnh cht giao hon, tnh cht kt hp, tnh cht phn phi gia php nhn v php cng, hng ng thc ng nh. Cc k nng nhn v chia biu thc vi i lng lin hp thng c s dng khi bin i rt gn phn thc lin quan n s phc. Ch  l ch c du bt ng thc gia hai s thc nhng khng c du bt ng thc gia hai s phc bt k.<br /> <br /> - Phng trnh bc nht i vi s phc: s dng php ton gia cc s phc hoc s dng dng i s ca s phc  gii phng trnh.<br /> <br /> - Phng trnh bc hai nghim phc: Nu en ta bng 0 hoc en ta l s thc dng th ta s dng cng thc nghim nh i vi phng trnh bc hai nghim thc. Nu en ta khng phi l s thc th phi chn cc s thc m, n  c th biu din en ta bng biu thc (m+ni)2<br /> <br /> - Phng trnh tch vi nghim phc c bin i tng t nh i vi nghim thc<br /> <br /> - Phng trnh dng A2+B2 = 0 ta khng th gii tng t nh i vi nghim thc m phi chuyn v phng trnh tch (A+iB)(A-iB)=0<br /> <br /> - S dng dng i s ca s phc  tm cn bc hai ca s phc.<br /> <br /> - Biu din hnh hc ca s phc: Tm tp hp im biu din s phc tha mn mt tnh cht xc nh. Tnh hung thng gp l vit z=x+yi vi x, y l cc s thc, bin i cc iu kin lin quan n z tng ng vi x, y tha mn mt phng trnh ng thng hoc ng trn.<br /> <br /> - Dng lng gic ca s phc (dnh cho hc sinh ban nng cao): Cho s phc di dng i s, biu din s phc di dng lng gic, tm acgumen, s dng cng thc Moa-vr tm ly tha bc n ca s phc; s dng dng lng gic  thc hin php ton gia hai s phc. Trong phn ny, hc sinh cn nm vng mt s cng thc lng gic ca lp 10 nh cng thc lin quan n gi tr lng gic ca hai gc ph nhau, hai gc b nhau, hai gc i nhau, cng thc cng, cng thc nhn i<br /> <br /> <strong><i><span style="font-family: Arial;">5. Ch  Khi a din.</span></i></strong> Hc sinh cn ch  nhng vn  sau<br /> <br /> - Cng thc tnh din tch ca tam gic, din tch hnh thang, din tch hnh ch nht, th tch ca khi chp, th tch khi lng tr tam gic v lng tr t gic. <br /> <br /> - Trong phn th tch, hc sinh thng phi tnh ng cao ca hnh chp hoc hnh lng tr. Cc tnh hung thng gp: <br /> <br /> i) hnh chp u c ng cao i qua tm ca mt y; <br /> <br /> ii) hnh lng tr ng c ng cao bng cnh bn.<br /> <br /> iii) hnh chp hoc hnh lng tr c mt cnh bn vung gc vi mt y, khi  chiu cao ca hnh chp bng  di ca cnh bn, hnh chiu vung gc ca cc cnh bn cn li trn mt y l on thng c mt u mc l chn ng cao. T  c th xc nh gc gia ng thng cha cnh bn v mt phng cha y ca a din<br /> <br /> iv) hnh chp hoc hnh lng tr c mt mt bn vung gc vi mt y, khi  ng cao ca hnh chp hoc hnh lng tr l ng cao ca mt bn v hnh chiu ca mi ng thng thuc mt bn trn y trng vi giao tuyn. T  c th xc nh gc gia ng thng cha cnh bn v mt phng cha y ca a din<br /> <br /> - Hc sinh nm vng cch xc nh gc gia hai ng thng, gc gia ng thng v mt phng, gc gia hai mt phng. <br /> <br /> - Nu gi thit ca bi ton c hai mt phng vung gc vi nhau th thng k thm ng ph l ng thng trong mt mt phng v vung gc vi giao tuuyn, khi  ng ny s vung gc vi mt phng cn li. Nu gi thit c hai mt phng cng vung gc vi mt th ba th thng dng n giao tuyn ca hai mt phng v giao tuyn s vung gc vi mt th ba<br /> <br /> -  lm tt ch  ny, hc sinh phi nh nh l Pytago trong tam gic vung, nh l cosin trong tam gic, h thc lin h gia gc v cnh trong tam gic vung. <br /> <br /> <em><b><span style="font-family: Arial;">6. Ch  Hnh cu, hnh tr, hnh nn</span></b></em><br /> <br /> - Nm vng cng thc din tch ca mt cu, th tch ca khi cu, din tch xung quanh ca hnh tr, th tch khi tr, din tch xung quanh ca hnh nn v th tch khi nn.<br /> <br /> - Vi dng ton hnh cu, hc sinh phi bit xc nh tm mt cu ngoi tip a din. C th cn phi xc nh tm ca ng trn ngoi tip mt mt ca a din, t  xc nh trc ca ng trn ngoi tip. Mt s trng hp thng gp: <br /> <br /> i)cc nh a din cng nhn hai im c nh di mt gc vung, khi  tm mt cu l trung im on ni hai im c nh; <br /> <br /> ii)hnh chp c cc cnh bn bng nhau, khi  y ca a din l a gic ni tip ng trn v hnh chiu ca nh trn y trng vi tm ng trn ngoi tip ca y, trc ca ng trn ngoi tip y cha ng cao hnh chp; hnh chp u c tm mt cu ngoi tip thuc ng cao; <br /> <br /> iii) hnh chp c y l tam gic vung, khi  trc ca ng trn ngoi tip y l ng thng i qua trung im ca cnh huyn v vung gc vi y. <br /> <br /> Nh vy,  nm vng dng ton ny, hc sinh phi nm vng cc loi quan h vung gc: ng thng vung gc vi ng thng, ng thng vung gc vi mt phng, hai mt phng vung gc.<br /> <br /> <em><b><span style="font-family: Arial;">7. Phng php ta  trong khng gian</span></b></em><br /> <br /> - Nm vng cng thc ta  tch c hng ca hai vc t. Bit s dng tch <br /> <br /> c hng ca hai vc t  tnh din tch tam gic, tnh th tch khi hp, th tch khi t din (ban nng cao). S dng tch c hng ca hai vc t  xc nh vc t ch phng ca ng thng khi vc t ch phng vung gc vi hai vc t cho trc, s dng tch c hng ca hai vc t  xc nh vc t php tuyn ca hai mt phng khi vc t php tuyn vung gc vi hai vc t cho trc.<br /> <br /> - Nm vng cc dng phng trnh ng thng: phng trnh tham s v phng trnh chnh tc, nm vng phng trnh mt phng v phng trnh mt cu. Ch  cc dng mt phng c bit (song song vi cc mt phng ta , cha cc trc ta ,).<br /> <br /> -  lp phng trnh ng thng, hc sinh thng phi ch ra mt im thuc ng thng v vc t ch phng. C th s dng quan h song song, quan h vung gc v tch c hng  tm vc t ch phng<br /> <br /> -  lp phng trnh mt phng, hc sinh thng phi ch ra mt im thuc mt phng v vc t php tuyn. C th s dng quan h song song, quan h vung gc v tch c hng  tm vc t php tuyn<br /> <br /> <em><span style="font-family: Arial;">- Mt s dng ton v kin thc lin quan:</span></em><br /> <br />  i) Lp phng trnh mt phng tha mn mt trong cc iu kin: mt phng cha ba im phn bit, cha mt ng thng v mt im ngoi ng thng, i qua mt im v vung gc vi mt ng thng cho trc, i qua mt im v song song vi mt mt phng cho trc, i qua mt im v song song vi hai ng thng cho trc, tip xc mt cu ti mt im cho trc, mt phng cha mt ng thng v song song vi mt ng thng khc.<br /> <br /> ii) Lp phng trnh ng thng tha mn mt trong cc iu kin sau: ng thng i qua hai im cho trc, i qua mt im v song song vi mt ng thng cho trc, i qua mt im v vung gc vi mt mt phng cho trc, i qua mt im vung gc vi hai ng cho trc, i qua mt im ng thi vung gc v ct mt ng cho trc, ng thng l giao tuyn ca hai mt phng cho trc.<br /> <br /> iii) Lp phng trnh mt cu tha mn mt trong cc iu kin sau: mt cu c tm v bn knh cho trc, c tm v i qua mt im cho trc, c tm v tip xc vi mt mt phng cho trc, c tm v tip xc vi mt ng thng cho trc (ban nng cao), cha bn im cho trc.<br /> <br /> iv) Gc gia hai ng thng, gc gia hai mt phng (ban nng cao).<br /> <br /> v) Khong cch t mt im n mt phng, khong cch t mt im n ng thng, khong cch gia hai ng thng cho nhau. <br /> <br /> - Trong nhiu trng hp, hc sinh phi tham s ha ta  ca 