(209, 'TRNG THPT C LOA  VI NGY HI LM  DNG DY HC CA NGNH', 'trng-thpt-c-loa-vi-ngay-hi-lam-dung-dy-hc-ca-nganh', '', '<p style="text-align: right;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 19pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Lm  dng dy hc l mt hot ng din ra thng nin i vi cc trng THPT trong mi nm hc nhm pht huy tnh sng to trong vic lm  dng dy hc ca gio vin  gp phn nng cao cht lng v kt qu gio dc ca ngnh .</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 19pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><img style="float: left;" src="data/giaoduc/hoaanhdao.jpg" alt="" height="149" width="199" />Hi thi lm  dng dy hc cp cm ca ngnh nm hc 2011-2012 din ra vo trung tun thng ba.  hng ng ngy hi ,Trng THPT C Loa ngay t u nm hc  pht ng phong tro thi ua lm  dng dy hc trong ton gio vin v ng thi thng xuyn quan tm, ng vin ti cc c nhn v tp th t nhm chuyn mn lm  dng dy hc.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 19pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Sn phm  dng dy hc nm hc 2011-2012 ca trng THPT C Loa  c hon tt vo thng hai v trng by ti phng hi ng t ngy 18 thng 2.  dng day hc nm nay ca nh trng gm 09 sn phm  dng ca tt c cc t nhm chuyn mn v c phn chia thnh 03 nhm sn phm : Nhm 1 gm cc sn phm bng a hnh ca t Ngoi ng, L v nhm Sinh ; nhm 2 l sn phm tranh nh, m hnh bng biu ca cc t nhm Vn ,S, a ,GDCD ; nhm 3 l cc thit b m hnh mu vt ca t Ton v nhm Ho .</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 19pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Nhn chung sn phm  dng dy hc nm nay u c cht lng tt, c kh nng ng dng cao, ph hp vi thc tin dy hc, mi m, sng to nh du mt bc chuyn bin ln trong vic lm  dng dy hc ca cc gio vin nh trng .</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 19pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> chun b cho hi thi sn phm  dng dy hc cp cm cc trng THPT, nh trng  t chc thi  dng dy hc cp trng vo th t ngy 29 thng 2 . Ban gim kho ca cuc thi l cc thy c trong Ban gim hiu nh trng v cc thy c l t trng cc t chuyn mn . Cuc thi din ra nghim tc v y trch nhim song cng rt si ni bi nhng cu hi tranh lun t pha Ban gim kho vi tc gi ca  dng dy hc, tt c u mun i n mt s nh gi chnh xc, khch quan , cng bng v tho ng .</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 19pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Sau mt bui chiu lm vic nghim tc v y trch nhim, Ban gim kho  la chn ra c: 02 sn phm gii nht, 03 sn phm gii nh, 04 sn phm gii ba v mt sn phm  i d thi cp cm. Hai sn phm gii nht thuc t Ho - Sinh ca hai tc gi l thy ng Thanh m v thy ng o Hiu. Ba sn phm gii nh thuc t Vn,Ton v nhm S ca ba tc gi l thy T Xun i, c Hong Kim Lin v c Phm Bch Dip. Bn sn phm gii ba thuc t L, Ngoi ng v hai nhm a, GDCD. Mt sn phm c chn i d thi cp cm l sn phm ca thy ng Thanh m, sn phm ny c Ban gim hiu v cc gim kho nh gi rt cao hy vng s t gii trong k thi cp cm .</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 19pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Hot ng thi lm  dng dy hc tuy l mt hot ng din ra thng nin trong mi nm hc song hot ng ny vn lun mi bi mi nm li c thm nhng pht minh rt mi ca gio vin trong vic ch tc ra nhng  dng phc v cho cng tc dy hc, nh du nhng bc ci tin v sng to ca gio vin trong dy hc  gp phn nng cao cht lng v kt qu gio dc ca ngnh .</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Dng Cc</span></b></span></p>', '', 1, 3, 0, 19, '2012-03-10 02:59:43', 62, '', '2012-04-10 12:24:46', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-03-10 02:57:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 4, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 92, 'robots=\nauthor=');
