(201, 'Trng THPT C Loa vi hot ng thanh tra s phm nm hc 2011-2012', 'trng-thpt-c-loa-vi-hot-ng-thanh-tra-s-phm-nm-hc-2011-2012', '', '<p style="text-align: right;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 36pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Thanh tra s phm nh gio l mt hot ng din ra thng xuyn trong mi nm hc nhm thc y s pht trin ca ngnh . Theo quyt nh ca Chnh thanh tra S gio dc v o to, trng THPT C Loa s c n on thanh tra hot ng s phm vo ngy10/1/2012 vi mt s b mn nh : a l, Gio dc cng dn, Ho, Sinh-CN, Sinh hc, Th dc, Ting anh, Tin, Ton, Vn.</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="data/giaoduc/090226174913-860-447.jpg" alt="" height="295" width="438" />Ti trng THPT C Loa nhng ngy u tin ca hc k II ny, thy v tr nh trng ang quyt tm thi ua dy tt- hc tt  c c kt qu cao nht trong hc k II v nm hc. Song song vi hot ng  nh trng v mt s thy c gio cn ang khn trong chun b cho t thanh tra hot ng s phm vo 2 ngy 10 v 11/1/2012 do S gio dc v o to quy nh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  to iu kin cho on thanh tra hon thnh tt nhim v trong 2 ngy v lm vic ti nh trng , Ban gim hiu trng THPT C Loa  sp xp thi kho biu  trong 2 ngy thanh tra hot ng s phm, cc gio vin thuc din thanh tra c t nht 2 tit dy v gi thi kho biu cho on thanh tra. Nhng gio vin c thanh tra trong nm hc 2011-2012 ny gm 15 thy c cng  c Ban gim hiu nh trng thng bo v xp lch dy hp l trong 2 ngy thanh tra .</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ngy 10/1,on thanh tra  n trng lm vic ho cng khng kh hot ng si ni ca tt c thy v tr trng THPT C Loa. Nhng lp vinh d c n cc thy c thanh tra gio vin v hc sinh dng nh cng phn khi hn bi nhng tit hc  c thy v tr u nh c th hin v khng nh mnh. Trong lp hc tr th hng hi cn thy th say sa to nn nhng tit hc tht hiu qu.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hot ng thanh tra din ra trong 2 ngy  kt thc. Hai ngy lm vic nghim tc v y trch nhim c on thanh tra v Trng THPT C Loa  c mt kt qu ng ghi nhn nht l i vi nhng thy c c thanh tra ai cng thy mnh c khng nh v trng thnh hn trc. on  thanh tra xong 13 thy c vi kt qu l 03 thy c t gii, 09 thy c t kh v 01 thy c t yu cu. Nhng thy c t gii nh c Diu Thu ( vn) c Chinh Thu (a), thy Nguyn Vn Ch ( th dc). y chnh l nhng thy c rt nhit tnh tm huyt, yu ngh  c on thanh tra nh gi rt cao. </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; t thanh tra nh k ca S ln ny din ra sm hn so vi nhng nm trc. Song trng THPT C Loa, c bit l nhng thy c c thanh tra, cng  hon thnh tt nhim v ca mnh vi kt qu nh gi tht ng phn khi. Tuy nhin bn cnh nim phn khi,t ho ca mt s thy c th  u  trong nhng thy c c thanh tra vn cn c cht bn khon tic nui v gi dy cha th hin c ht mnh v ti tin chc rng cc thy c cng s quyt tm hn trong nhng gi khc  dn hon thin mnh hn khng ch vi hot ng thanh tra m ngay vi chnh hc sinh thn yu ca mnh. <br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Dng Cc</span></p>', '', 1, 3, 0, 22, '2012-01-18 09:32:02', 62, '', '2012-04-10 12:22:25', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-01-18 09:30:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_mod