(198, 'TRNG THPT C LOA VI CHNG TRNH NH GI HC SINH QUC T', 'trng-thpt-c-loa-vi-chng-trinh-anh-gia-hc-sinh-quc-t', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><strong>Vit Nam  ng k tham gia chng trnh Quc t, nh gi hc sinh (gi tt l PISA) vo nm 2012 do t chc hp tc v pht trin kinh t (OECD) khi xng</strong>. </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><img style="float: left;" src="data/giaoduc/hocsinh/hoc_sinh_thamg_gia.jpg" alt="" height="160" width="214" /> chun b cho k nh gi chnh thc vo thng 4 nm 2012, B gio dc v o to  khi ng tt c cc s gio dc v mt s trng THPT ( c khi dn lp v cng lp) th nghim nh gi  cp quc gia vo cui thng 12 nm 2011 trong  c Trng THPT C Loa- Mt ngi trng c b dy lch s vi 45 nm xy dng trng thnh v pht trin. Ti trng THPT C Loa nhng ngy cui thng 12 ny khng kh chun b cho chng trnh nh gi hc sinh quc gia cng rt si ng. </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Song song vi vic chun b kt thc hc k I kh bn rn th Ban Gim hiu, gio vin v c hc sinh cng ang ro rit khn trng chun b cho k nh gi hc sinh quc gia do B gio dc v o to yu cu. Chng trnh nh gi hc sinh quc gia  c nh trng trin khai ti ton th gio vin v hc sinh ngay t khi c cng vn ca S gio dc v o to cho nn tt c gio vin v hc sinh dng nh cng  sn sng n i t nh gi ny.\r\n<table style="background-color: #fdd0aa; border-color: #ffffff; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; float: left; width: 349px; height: 268px;" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #008080;">Theo quy nh ca B gio dc hc sinh u c lm bi trc nghim trong 40 pht v sau 10 pht ngh ngi cc em li bt tay vo phn t lun vi thi gian l 80 pht. Ngy 31/12 cc em s kho st mn Ngoi ng. Vi mn Ngoi ng, hc sinh s phi tri qua 3 phn nh gi. Phn u tin cc em lm bi trc nghim trong 20 pht, tip sau  n phn c hiu v ngn ng 40 pht v cui cng kt thc bng bi t lun vi thi gian l 30 pht. Mt k kho st nghim tc song cng khng qu gy cng thng cho hc sinh. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #008080;">Cc em hc sinh tham gia u cm thy thoi mi v c c lp th nghim nh gi kh nng ca mnh. Khng ch vy cc em cn rt vinh d v mnh c l hc sinh i din cho 1950 hc sinh thn yu ca Trng THPT C Loa tham gia nh gi hc sinh Quc gia ng trc s hi nhp v gio dc Trng THPT C Loa l Trng u tin trong Cm ng Anh v cng l mt trong nhng trng u tin c B gio dc o to chn tham gia nh gi hc sinh quc t vo thng 4 nm 2012 ti y. </span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #008080;">&nbsp;<br data-mce-bogus="1" /></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Chng trnh nh gi bt u t ngy 29/11. Ngay bui sng ngy 29 mt s gio vin thuc 03 b mn c la chn nh gi l: Vn, Ton, Ngoi ng- khi 11 c tham gia tr li phiu hi kho st kt qa hc tp . Tt c din ra nghim tc di s gim st ca thanh tra B gio dc . </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Ngy 30 - 31 cc em hc sinh chnh thc c bc vo kho st.Ci ho hc ch i nhng ngy ngh hc k v tt dng lch ang n gn cng vi s tan long khng th khng c trong nhng ngy cui k  hc sinh  phi nhng ch cho mt khng kh trang nghim ca k kho st nh gi ny. Ngy 30/12, cc em bt u c kho st 02 mn Vn v Ton. </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Bn cnh nim vinh d t ho th cng khng phi khng c nhng kh khn m bc u gp phi. Song Trng THPT C Loa vi s cho li vng chc ca Ban giam hiu cng i ng gio vin vng vng nhit tnh v say m vi ngh chc chn s vt qua nhng kh khn th thch   i n ci ch cui cng  l s thnh cng trong hi nhp Quc t gio dc vo thng 4 nm 2012. </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Dng Cuc</span></p>', '', 1, 3, 0, 24, '2012-01-06 02:58:13', 62, '', '2012-04-10 12:23:19', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-01-06 02:57:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 14, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 122, 'robots=\nauthor=');
