(195, 'TRNG THPT C LOA BC VO THI HC K I  NM HC (2011-2012)', 'trng-thpt-c-loa-bc-vao-thi-hc-k-i-nm-hc-2011-2012', '', '<p style="text-indent: 36pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Mt tm l kh ph bin  nhiu trng hc trc dp Noel v tt dng lch l n np dy v hc c phn xo trn, t tp trung hn. Tuy nhin n trng THPT C Loa ( ng Anh- H Ni) vo nhng ngy ny khng kh hc tp rt rn rng, thy v tr ang gng ht sc mnh  k thi hc k thnh cng tt p.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;<img style="float: left;" src="data/giaoduc/cimg2612.jpg" alt="" height="176" width="236" />Theo lch thng nin ca nh trng c n tun th 3 ( t 19-24/12) hc sinh s tham gia thi hc k I. K thi hc k I nm nay bt u cng vi nhng t gi ma ng bc u tin thi v. Ci lnh khc nghit ca ma ng Min Bc khng lm gim i c sc nng cng nh tnh hnh chun b thi c ca trng. Ngay t ngy 08/12, khi lch thi c thng bo khng kh hc tp chun b cho thi c  lan to khp trng. Di s ch o ca Ban gim hiu ng u l thy Ng c Nm- Hiu trng Nh trng, cc  cng mn hc ca cc t c chun b chu ao, vic phn cng giao vin ra  thi cng c khn trng v m bo b mt an ton tuyt i. Chng trnh hc k I  kt thc. Hc sinh cc khi lp tp trung mit mi n tp  mong t c kt qu tt nht trong k thi ny.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> thc hin mt k thi nghim tc Ban gim hiu  ch o gio vin ch nhim cng nh cc gio vin b mn song song vi vic n tp chu o cho hc sinh gio vin cn thng xuyn nhc nh, qun trit ti hc sinh v nhng quy nh trong thi c v cho hc sinh k cam kt thc hin thi nghim tc trc khi thi.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Tun ny t 12 n 17 thng 12 cc mn thi ring nh: S, a, Cng dn, Gio dc quc phng,Th dc   c bt u. Tun sau t 19- 24/12 tip n cc mn thi tp trung ( Nhng mn thi tp trung gm: Ton, Vn, Ngoi ng, L, Ho). Nhng mn thi tp trung cc em c xp theo s bo danh ca phng thi. Bi thi c dc phch trc khi chm  m bo s cng bng nghim tc.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Vic thi hc k I nh vy c th s hi ng ngng vi cc em hc sinh khi 10 v y l ln u tin cc em chnh thc thc hin mt k thi hc k u tin  cp THPT nhng cc em s quen dn vi cc ln thi hc k sau v nh vy sau ny cc em s khng ng ngng khi n vi cc k thi ln nh thi tt nghip v cao ng i hc. Chc chn sau k thi ny cc em s thy th v hn v c c lp lm bi, c thy kt qu nghim tc, thc cht ca mnh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; line-height: 20pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;Chun b bc vo k thi nn khp trng u u cng ch c chuyn v  ti thi c. Hc sinh trao i vi nhau v nhng bi kh, hi nhau v nhng cch gii hay, phng php hc tp hiu qu. Cc thy c th ng vin nhau gng ht sc mnh mong sao c th truyn t cho hc sinh y  cc kin thc  bc vo k thi mt cch t tin. Tt c  sn sng  bc vo ngy hi ln, mt im nhn quan trng ca nm hc 2011-2012./.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial;">Dng Cc</span></b></span></p>', '', 1, 3, 0, 22, '2011-12-22 03:29:10', 62, '', '2012-04-10 12:20:18', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-22 03:27:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 7, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 94, 'robots=\nauthor='),
