(179, 'ON TNCS H CH MINH TRNG  THPT C LOA 45 NM T HO', 'oan-tncs-h-chi-minh-trng-thpt-c-loa-45-nm-t-hao', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Ch tch H Ch Minh  tng ni:  Mt nm khi u l ma xun, mt i khi u l tui tr, tui tr l ma xun ca cuc i. K t ngy tch ra khi trng cp 3 ng Anh A v C Loa thnh lp trng mi, lp lp on vin thanh nin l nhn t quan trng ng gp vo s pht trin ca nh trng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">45 nm qua, on trng  ln mnh c v c cu t chc, qui m v cht lng phong tro. Hin nay on trng c 30 chi on (29 chi on hc sinh, 1 chi on gio vin) v 14 chi hi Hi lin hip thanh nin Vit Nam, vi gn 2000 on vin, thanh nin. Ban chp hnh on trng v Ban chp hnh Hi lin hip thanh nin c 13 ng ch, 2 thy c C vn on. y u l nhng th lnh on, hi tiu biu trong hc tp v rn luyn, nng ng, nhit tnh trong cng tc.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">\r\n<table style="float: left; width: 293px; height: 185px;" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><img src="data/giaoduc/img_0025.jpg" alt="" height="202" width="270" /></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Nh li nhng nm chin tranh c lit, hng ngn on vin thanh nin tnh nguyn ln ng nhp ng vi tinh thn x dc Trng Sn i cu nc, m lng phi phi dy tng lai. Nhiu ng ch trong s   nm li trn nhng no ng hnh qun, nhng cnh rng, nhng lng mc, ng rung; nhiu ng ch tr v mang trn mnh bao vt thng. Nhng s hi sinh  cng t thm thm truyn thng ca on vin thanh nin nh trng ni ring, truyn thng ho hng ca dn tc ni chung.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Trong kh khn chung ca t nc sau chin tranh, on vin thanh nin nh trng va tch cc hc tp, rn luyn va cng cc thy c gio o ao nui c, lm rung, ng gch xy dng trng, gip cc hp tc x ci to mt bng, o mng lm thy liM hnh gn hc i i vi hnh, l lun gn vi thc tin  gp phn a nh trng tr thnh mt trong nhng trng c phong tro gio dc hng nghip hiu qu.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Trong xu th t nc chuyn sang thi k cng nghip ha  hin i ha, on vin, thanh nin nh trng lun xc nh c nhim v ca mnh,  l khng ngng hc tp, rn luyn nng cao trnh  v ngy mai lp nghip. on trng lun l trung tm tp hp on vin thanh nin thng qua cc hot ng tp th, cc cuc thi, cc phong tro hng nm nh: thi ging ht hay, thi n sinh duyn dng, hc sinh thanh lch, lm  dng hc tp, sng to khoa hc, thi u th dc th thaophong tro n n p ngha, l lnh m l rchNhng phong tro ny  gp phn khng nh vo thnh tch hc tp, rn luyn ca on vin, thanh nin. T l on vin thanh nin c hc lc Kh - Gii, hnh kim Kh - Tt ngy cng cao; cc gii thng, huy chng m on vin thanh nin t c trong cc k thi ngy cng nhiu.</span></p>\r\n', '\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">on trng cng rt quan tm gio dc l tng, li sng, o c tc phong cho on vin thanh nin thng qua cc hot ng tham quan di tch lch s, mt tinh, giao lu, ngoi kha, tuyn truynnhn cc ngy l ln. Cng tc tp hun, bi dng chnh tr cho cn b lp, cn b on, c tin hnh hiu qu, c cht lng. on trng  to ra mt sn chi va si ni va a dng, ph hp vi tui tr va c tnh nh hng cht ch.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">T trong nhng phong tro   xut hin rt nhiu gng mt on vin thanh nin tiu biu nh: Phm Thu An (gii nh mn Vn ton quc - 1991); Nguyn c Mnh (gii 3 mn Ton ton quc - 1999); Phm Th Ti (Gii Khuyn khch mn a l ton quc  2000); Nguyn Ph Huy (t 30 im trong k thi i hc - 2004); Nguyn Vn Minh (sng ch ra my ht phn g phc v cho gia nh v my tng hoa cho thy ch nhim  2006); Bi Bch Ngc, Nguyn Th Thanh Hoa (Bng khen ca Trung ng on  2005, 2007); o Thanh Tng (29,5 im trng Kinh t quc dn, gii ba vng thi thng ng ln nh Olympia - 2008); o Thanh Lim ( 2 Huy chng vng Karatedo thnh ph - 2008); Nguyn Hng Minh (Gii Nh Giai iu tui hng thnh ph, gii Khuyn khch Festival ting Anh thnh ph - 2010)Cng t y nhiu cn b lp, cn b on  trng thnh, nhiu ng ch  c kt np vo ng cng sn Vit Nam, nhiu ng ch  tr thnh cn b on xut sc  cc trng i hc, Cao ng hoc lnh o ca c quan, on th x hi. D  cng v no, on vin, thanh nin trng THPT C Loa lun mang trong mnh bu nhit huyt ca tui tr, sn sng cng hin cho s nghip xy dng v bo v T quc.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Tht t ho nhn li chng ng 45 nm on trng THPT C Loa xy dng v trng thnh, d  trong bt c hon cnh no on vin thanh nin lun chng t l nhn t quan trng lm nn thnh tch ca nh trng, xng ng vi k vng ca lnh o nh trng v cc cp b on. on trng lin tc c Thnh on H Ni, Huyn on ng Anh tng giy khen v nhiu nm c Trung ng on tng Bng khen l n v xut sc trong cng tc on v phong tro thanh nin khi THPT, THCN&amp;DN (nm 2005, 2007).</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Pht huy truyn thng, on vin thanh nin trng THPT C Loa khng ngng hc tp, rn luyn vng bc vo i cng hin sc lc v tr tu cho qu hng, t nc.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 0, 5, '2011-11-09 14:23:08', 91, '', '2012-04-10 12:35:20', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-09 14:17:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 10, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 314, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(178, 'K HOCH CNG TC THNG 11 - 2011', 'k-hoch-cong-tac-thang-11-2011', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><img style="float: left;" alt="logo truong" src="images/logo%20truong.jpg" height="188" width="162" /><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp; 1- Cng tc t</span></b><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> </span></b><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">t</span></b><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">ng </span></b><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"></span></b><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">o </span></b><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">c</span></b><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">:</span></b></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- Tip tc thc hin thi ua trong i ng cn b, gio vin, nhn vin v cc lp hc sinh, lp thnh tch cho mng 45 nm ngy thnh lp trng v ngy nh gio Vit Nam 20-11. Thng qua  nu cao tinh thn t ho ca mi thy c gio ang cng tc di mi trng c b dy truyn thng 45 nm v gio dc truyn thng Tn s trng o  cho hc sinh ton trng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- Cng on v nh trng phi hp, tng cng n c to khng kh thi ua dy tt si ni trong nh trng, trn tinh thn  nu cao trch nhim, tnh t gic thc hin nhim v ca gio vin, nhn vin.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- Tip tc c cc bin php gio dc, bin php kim tra thc hin k cng n np ca hc sinh, chn chnh cc hin tng vi phm trang phc, b gi, i hc mun, li hc kt hp tuyn truyn gio dc  thc thc hin php lut cho hc sinh, quan tm gio dc i tng hc sinh cha ngoan. Yu cu 100% hc sinh phi mc ng trang phc th thao khi tham gia hc qun s quc phng, v vy gio vin nhm TDQP phi thc hin y  lm gng cho HS.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- Tng cng ch o, hng dn cc lp luyn tp cc tit mc vn ngh, TDTT tham gia ma ht v hi khe ph ng, to khng kh hot ng si ni. T chc tt hot ng thi HS thanh lch.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- T chc tuyn truyn v tm hiu v truyn thng nh trng, v ngy nh gio Vit Nam trong cc gi sinh hot di c, nhm th hin c tinh thn tn s trng o, tnh cm tt p ca thy, tr. </span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">2- Cng tc chuyn mn:</span></b></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- Hon thnh vic vo im s ci gia hc k 1, thc hin t 07 n 12/11. </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- <span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Cc t chuyn mn kim tra tin  thc hin chng trnh ca gio vin trong t.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- T chc d gi theo k hoch, ch  cc gio vin ng k gi dy tt, to khng kh si ni trong hot ng dy hc.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- T Ng vn, t a l- GDCD, T Ngoi ng t chc d gi rt kinh nghim cho cc gio vin tham gia thi gio vin dy gii vng cm ; thi gian thi: mn a l v Ng vn thit vo tit 2, mn Anh vn v GDCD thi vo tit 3 sng ngy 25/11.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- Hng dn gio sinh thc tp, m bo thi gian, cht lng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- Tip tc hng dn hc sinh 12 thi vng 2 HS gii d thi vo 07/11 . </span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">3- Cng tc c s vt cht, lao ng, hng nghip, dy ngh.</span></b></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- Tng v sinh cc khu vc trong khun vin nh trng v trc cng trng. m bo sch, p trong ngy l. </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- Bin php: T chc cho cc lp hc sinh khi 10 lao ng; kim tra n c v yu cu nhn vin lao cng, v sinh tng thi gian lao ng hng ngy. Gii quyt dt im bi rc  gc sn vn ng, ct sch c khu vc sn vn ng. C ra v sp xp gh  pha sau nh hiu b, phun ra sch sn pha sau khu nh th cht v phng hp mi. Di chuyn mt s cy cnh  sn trng v sn gia phng hp v nh WC. </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- Bo v phi kim tra, n c cng tc an ninh, trt t, bo qun c s vt cht, lp hc trong v ngoi gi hnh chnh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- Sa cha nh WC tng 1 nh A  lm khu v sinh cho GV; b sung dng c v sinh, thng ng rc thi cho cc dy hnh lang, khu vc sau nh hiu b, nh th cht, khu vc nh mi xy </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- B sung mt s thng ng rc vo khu vc nh mi xy, th cht</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">4- Cng tc sinh hot tp th.</span></b></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- Gio vin ch nhim thng bo kt qu rn luyn, hc tp gia hc k I cho gia nh hc sinh. </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- Gio vin ch nhim tng cng gio dc  thc, thi  hc tp ca hc sinh; tch cc ng vin v theo di gim st cc hot ng ca lp  thu c kt qu cao nht. </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- on thanh nin tp trung cao  luyn tp cc tit mc vn ngh, th thao  thi u v biu din; Chi on gio vin tp mt s bi ht v ngi gio vin, la chn tit mc tham gia biu din cho mng 45 nm v ngy 20  11. </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- T chc L mt tinh k nim 45 nm thnh lp trng v cho mng <b>Ngy nh gio Vit Nam</b> vo ngy 18/11. Ngy 16, 17 cho HS ngh hc  lm cng tc chun b, trang tr khnh tit. </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- Cc lp c k hoch trang tr lp hc nhn thng cho mng ngy Nh gio Vit Nam.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- Sinh hot di c vi ch  v Nh trng, v ngy Nh gio Vit Nam, "Tn s trng o"; "Ung nc nh ngun"; "K nim v thy c v mi trng".</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;<b>5- Cng tc t chc, qun l.</b></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- T chc L k nim 45 nm xy dng v pht trin trng THPT C Loa v k nim ngy nh gio Vit Nam vo ngy 18/11. Cc tiu ban kim tra, ln phng n b tr c s vt cht, phn cng lc lng tham gia cc cng vic ca bui l, theo k hoch  xy dng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Yu cu tt c cc /c CB- GV- NV ca nh trng hy chung tay thc hin tt nhim v khi c Ban t chc phn cng. </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> th hin s thng nht v tn trng khch v d  ngh mc ng trang phc do nh trng may o, nam phi tht cvt.&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">- Ban ch o hng dn gip  gio sinh thc tp s phm