(177, 'T hnh chnh - ng hnh cng thi gian', 't-hanh-chinh-ng-hanh-cung-thi-gian', '', '<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;"><img style="float: left;" src="data/giaoduc/Gioithieu/cimg2603.jpg" alt="" height="296" width="397" /></span>&nbsp;Cng vi s hnh thnh v pht trin ca cc t chuyn mn trong nh trng, T Hnh chnh l mt b phn cng khng th thiu trong trng THPT C Loa. T m nhim nhiu cng vic khc nhau nh vn th, k ton, th qu, y t, th vin, th nghim, thit b, lao cng, bo v v mt s cng vic khc. C th ni 45 nm qua T Hnh chnh  c nhng ng gp ng k trong vic xy dng v pht trin nh trng.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">T nhng ngy u thnh lp trng, T Hnh chnh ch c vi ng ch kim nhim nhiu cng vic khc nhau nh vn th kim k ton , th vin kim th qu v c bit trong thi k chin tranh ph hoi ca  quc M, c s vt cht ca nh trng cn ngho nn, trang thit b cn thiu thn nhng vi s tn ty ht lng v cng vic, anh em trong t  m bo kp thi mi tiu chun ch  v thc hin phn phi cng bng cho cn b, gio vin nh: tem phiu lng thc, thc phm, ng sa, xch lp... v nhng  dng vn phng phc v cc thy c ging dy trong nh trng.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">c bit trong thi k i mi cng vi s pht trin mnh m ca cng ngh thng tin, cc ng ch trong T  c c i tp hun a cng ngh thng tin trong cng tc vn phng nh vn th, k ton, th vinVi s on kt nht tr, s gip  ln nhau trong cng vic, t  t c nhng thnh tch ng t ho, nhiu nm t t danh hiu t lao ng tin tin, nhiu c nhn c giy khen trong cng tc nh bo him y t hc sinh, ch thp , th vin nh trng t chun. Hin nay t c tt c 12 thnh vin, mi thnh vin u c trch nhim, gng mu trong cng vic, lun t hc hi  nng cao trnh  chuyn mn hon thnh xut sc cng vic c giao.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">T Hnh chnh t ho v nhng ng gp cng sc ca mnh trong s pht trin ring ca nh trng v s pht trin chung ca ngnh gio dc. Tuy nhin pha trc cng vic cn nng n, i hi mi thnh vin trong t phi n lc hn na trong mi mt  p ng nhu cu ngy cng cao ca x hi, gp phn xy dng trng THPT C Loa ngy cng vng mnh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">T trng Phm Th Thach<br /></span></p>', 1, 1, 0, 6, '2011-11-08 15:18:27', 62, '', '2012-04-10 11:43:59', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-08 15:13:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 25, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 216, 'robots=\nauthor='),
