y Tng chuyn v trng THPT Phan nh Phng , c Chi chuyn v trng THPT ng a, c Phng chuyn v trng THPT ng a ( hin c l Hiu trng ca trng ny), Thy Thi vn Khoa chuyn ln lm chuyn vin s gio dc v cn nhiu thy c khc na nh thy Phm Qu Liu ,thy Dng ,thy Quyt , c Lng , c Vn</span></p>\r\n', '\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Tip ni nhng thy c gio i trc, cc thy c ca t Vt l  cng ngh hm nay khng ngng tu dng, hc tp nng cao trnh  chuyn mn, nghip v  phc v s nghip gio dc ngy mt tt hn. Nhiu hc sinh ra trng vn cn nh v nhc nhiu n tm gng tn tu , ht lng vi hc sinh nh thy Bu, thy Ton, thy L, thy Nam ,thy Th ,c Hn .... p ng li s tn tnh dy bo ca thy c l s n lc khng ngng ca hc sinh.  l s hc sinh&nbsp;  i hc cao ng khi A ngy cng tng, hc sinh thi hc sinh gii cp thnh ph gn y t nhiu gii cao nh em: Bi c Phng (Gii nh HSG thnh ph mn Vt l nm 2004), em Nguyn vn Thng (Gii nh HSG thnh ph mn Vt l nm 2005), Ch vn Bn (Gii ba HSG thnh ph mn Vt l nm 2005), em Trng vn Ngha , Nguyn vn Sn (Gii ba HSG thnh ph mn Vt l nm 2006) ,em Bi Bch Phng, (Gii ba HSG thnh ph mn Vt l nm 2007),em Nguyn nh Quang (Gii nh HSG thnh ph mn vt l nm 2008) em Nguyn Hng Hnh, Nguyn vn Bc (Gii ba HSG thnh ph mn Vt l nm 2009), em Nguyn vn Vit, Lu tun Cng(Gii nh v ba HSG thnh ph mn Vt l nm 2010) v cn nhiu em c gii khuyn khch trong cc k thi hc sinh gii ...</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">T vt l hin nay gm 15 thy c gio, 100% trnh  i hc v sau i hc, Nhiu thy c  t c nhng thnh tch trong ging dy v trong chuyn mn nh thy Trn Qu Nam t gii nh  Hi thi gio vin dy gii thnh ph b mn Vt l cp THPT  nm hc 2005-2006, thy ng vn Phong t gii ba  dng dy hc t lm cp thnh ph nm hc 2009- 2010. C nhng thy c cn rt tr nhng  khng nh c mnh, vng trong chuyn mn, nhit tnh trong cc hot ng tp th. Tt c cc thy c gio u sn sng p ng c yu cu trc mt v lu di ca nh trng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">T nhiu nm nay, T vt l  Cng ngh t chc v duy tr c hiu qu phong tro i mi v ni dung, chng trnh, i mi phng php ging dy, bi dng hc sinh gii vt l. Cc thnh vin trong t u ch  ng mc n cng tc nghin cu khoa hc, c rt kinh nghim, t hc, t bi dng, khng ngng nng cao trnh  chuyn mn, nng lc s phm. Hin nay, hu ht gio vin trong t  s dng thnh tho my vi tnh v khai thc ti liu qua mng Internet. c bit, ch trng son v ging bi bng gio n in t ca nh trng  c mi thnh vin trong t nhit tnh hng ng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Cc thnh vin t vt L  Cng ngh lun on kt gip  nhau cng tin b. Lun phn u: Mi thy c gio l mt tm gng sng cho cho hc sinh noi theo. <span style="color: black;">Hy vng trong tng lai T Vt l- Cng ngh s pht huy c truyn thng, gt hi c nhiu thnh qu tt p, bi dng c nhiu hc sinh gii v nhng con ngi c ch cho t nc</span></span>.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;">T.Q.N</p>', 1, 1, 0, 6, '2011-11-08 14:24:13', 91, '', '2012-04-10 11:51:37', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-08 14:20:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 7, 0, 7, '', '', 0, 271, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(174, 'T S - a - Gio dc cng dn truyn thng, t ho v trch nhim', 't-s-a-giao-dc-cong-dan-truyn-thng-t-hao-va-trach-nhim', '', '<p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">\r\n<table style="float: left;" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><a href="images/dsc_0613.jpg"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;"><img title="Xem nh ln" style="float: left;" src="images/dsc_0613.jpg" alt="alt" height="231" width="347" /></span></a></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nTrng THPT C Loa c vinh d mang tn vng t c b dy vn ha v giu truyn thuyt lch s. Tri qua 45 nm xy dng v trng thnh, trong thnh tch chung ca nh trng khng th khng ni n ng gp ca cc th h thy c t S - a  Gio dc cng dn.</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">Nh nhng ngy u mi thnh lp, trng cp 3 C Loa cn bao ngn ngang, kh khn, vt v nhng cc thy c ca t  cng v<span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">i <span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">tp th s phm nh trng va tham gia lao ng xy dng trng lp, va ging dy trn bc ging. Nhiu th h hc tr ny  trng thnh nhng khng qun c nhng bi ging hay, nhng k nim vui, bun t nhng thi k y kh khn, gian kh y.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">Nhng nm thng thi bao cp, rt nhiu thy c gio trong t nh c Phan Th Tun, thy Phm V ng, thy Nguyn Hu Dng, thy ng B Lan, c Nguyn Th Li, thy Nguyn Hong To...khng qun thiu thn, gian kh ca i sng thng ngy, bm trng, bm lp, lun gn b vi nh trng, tt c v hc sinh thn yu. Tp th cc thy cc c lun l tm gng sng v o c, ti nng v s sng to cho lp lp hc tr. Cc thy, cc c xng ng vi nim tin yu ca cha m hc sinh v nhn dn.</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">K tc truyn thng, th h gio vin tr ca t hm nay lun c gng ht mnh vi mt mong c cao qu l c cng hin ngy mt nhiu hn cho s nghip trng ngi. 45 nm  tri qua, vi nhng n lc ht mnh, cn b gio vin t hng nm u t cc danh hiu lao ng tin tin, chin s thi ua. Nhiu thy c cn c S GD - T H Ni cng nhn l gio vin dy gii cp thnh ph, c sng kin kinh nghim t gii thnh ph, c tng lng trc thi hn. Trong  in hnh l cc thy c: thy Trnh Xun Ngt (<i>nguyn t trng u tin t S- a- Gio dc cng dn t ngy trng mi thnh lp sau l Ph hiu trng nh trng</i>) t gio vin dy gii nhiu nm. Thy Chu Thi Chung, Thy L Quang Vinh, thy Nguyn Hu Dng l gio vin dy gii. c bit, thy ng B Lan  5 ln tham gia thi gio vin dy gii thnh ph v c 5 ln u t<span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%;"> <span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">gii. Thy L Vn Chung, thy L Thanh Tng, C Nguyn Th Chinh Thu cng t danh hiu gio vin dy gii cp thnh ph.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">Tp th cc thy c L Vn Chung, L Thanh Tng, Nguyn Th Chinh Thu, Phm Bch Dip , Nguyn Th M H, Nguyn Th Thng, Hong Th Thanh... l cc thy c gio tuy tui i, tui ngh cn tr nhng cng nhiu nm lin t danh hiu chin s thi ua cp c s. Nhiu thy c trng thnh t t  tham gia cng tc lnh o nh trng nh Thy Trnh Xun Ngt nguyn Ph hiu trng nh trng, thy Trn nh Bi nguyn Ch tch cng on nh trng v hin nay l thy L Vn Chung l Ph hiu trng, ch tch cng on nh trng, thy L Thanh Tng l Ph hiu trng. Rt nhiu<span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%;"> <span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">thy, c gio trong t c vinh d ng trong hng ng ca ng nh thy ng nh Nhn, c o Th Hin, c Nguyn Th Li</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">Nhiu th h hc tr c thy c du dt  t gii cao trong cc k thi cp thnh ph, thm ch t gii quc gia. Tiu biu trong s  l cc em: ng Th Mai Lan; Bi Th Bch Thy, Trng Lan Chi, Nguyn Th Hi, Bi Hng Nhung, Nguyn Qunh Hng, Trnh Kim Tuyn, ng Th m, Nguyn Th Mai Anh...c bit c em Phm Th Ti  tng t gii Khuyn khch quc gia mn a l hay em Nguyn Bch Lin  tng tham gia i tuyn quc gia mn Lch s. Cc em l nhng bng hoa ti thm t p thm vn hoa tr tu ca trng THPT C Loa. V cn bit bao th h hc tr trng thnh t nh trng  v ang ng gp sc mnh vo s nghip xy dng v bo v qu hng, t nc.</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">Bn cnh cng tc ging dy, tp th t cn xy dng nhiu chuyn  phc v cho cng tc gio dc nh cc chuyn  v an ton giao thng; phng chng ma tu HIV/AIDS, lch s H Ni, a l H Ni, gio dc v gii tnh, v dn sCng vi nh trng, cc thy c gio trong t hng nm cn a hc sinh i tham quan hc tp ti cc di tch lch s - vn ha; t chc cc hot ng d ngoi Tm v ci ngun ti Vn Miu Quc T Gim hay Cn Sn, Kip Bc Cc chuyn , cc hot ng  u rt hay, thit thc v hiu qu,  gp phn gio dc hc sinh tt hn.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">Nhn li chng ng gn na th k, cc thy cc c, c ngi  ngh hu, c ngi  i xa, c ngi  chuyn cng tc hoc vn tip tc gn b vi ngh ngay ti trng nhng cng n ca cc thy cc c, s nghip ca cc thy cc c vn mi to sng trong k c cc th h hc tr.</span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;"></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;"></span>T Lch s - a l - Gio dc cng dn hm nay k tha v pht huy thnh tch ca cc th h tip ni th h, to ra c mt phong cch lm vic nghim tc, xy dng c mt t m on kt, gp phn a nh trng ngy cng ln mnh, t ho vi tn gi trng THPT C Loa.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><strong>N.T.C.T</strong><br /></span></p>', '', -2, 17, 0, 185, '2011-11-08 14:12:04', 73, '', '2011-11-09 10:39:03', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-08 14:10:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 7, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 97, ''),
