(172, 'T Ha- Sinh- Cng ngh on kt, sc tr v sng to', 't-hoa-sinh-cong-ngh-oan-kt-sc-tr-va-sang-to', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="color: #0000ff;"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> Trong cuc sng lun on kt, gip  nhau cng pht trin. Trong ging dy lun ch trng n vic lm thc hnh, th nghim  gip cc em hiu bi su hn, rn luyn k nng thc hnh, gn kin thc vi thc t cuc sng. Nhng bi ging ca cc thy c  thi vo tm hn cc em nim yu thch mn hc, cho cc em s hng th vi vic khm ph th gii </span></span></b></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><b><b><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';"><img style="float: left;" src="data/giaoduc/Gioithieu/dsc_0615.jpg" alt="" height="246" width="370" /></span></b></b></b></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Cng vi s pht trin chung ca trng THPT C Loa trong sut 45 nm qua, t Ho  Sinh  Cng Ngh ca trng lun l tp th on kt, gn b v pht huy tt th mnh ca mnh trong cng tc gio dc ca nh trng. Vi c th l t gm nhng b mn lun gn lin vi thc hnh, th nghim v thc t cuc sng, t Ho  Sinh - Cng Ngh lun thc hin tt phng chm Hc i i vi hnh, trong ging dy lun ch trng n vic lm thc hnh, th nghim  gip cc em hiu bi su hn, rn luyn k nng thc hnh cho cc em, gn kin thc vi thc t cuc sng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Thng qua cc bui sinh hot chuyn mn, d gi rt kinh nghim  gip cho cc gio vin nng cao cht lng chuyn mn v bn thn mi thy c gio cng lun xc nh cho mnh tnh yu ngh, t trau di chuyn mn nghip v, tch cc hc hi kinh nghim t th h i trc  vn ln t kt qu cao trong ging dy. Tiu biu nh thy Ng Thiu A, c  Th Phng, c Nguyn Th Thuy u t danh hiu gio vin gii cp thnh ph. Rt nhiu cc thy c trong t l chin s thi ua nhiu nm lin. T t danh hiu tp th tin tin nhiu nm lin tc.</span></p>\r\n', '\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; T nhng ngy u thnh lp, s hc sinh t, trang thit b dy hc cn thiu thn. n nay, trong thi k i mi, trng pht trin v quy m. S lp tng ln, s gio vin trong t ngy mt nhiu. Hin ti s gio vin tr l ch yu. iu kin dy v hc tt hn. Cc trang thit b dy hc c tng cng. Cc thy c gio  phn u i mi phng php ging dy, tch cc s dng  dng dy hc, khng ngng nng cao cht lng b mn. Cc thy c trong t  tch cc son gio n in t, lm v sng to ra nhng  dng dy hc gip cc em hc sinh c trc quan sinh ng v mn hc. Phong tro vit sng kin kinh nghim c duy tr, nhiu sng kin kinh nghim xp loi B cp thnh ph. Kt qu hc tp ca hc sinh c nng cao. Nhiu em phn u t hc sinh gii cp thnh ph b mn Ho v mn Sinh, nh cc em: Nguyn Vn ng, Ng Trng Cnh, Nguyn Anh Tun, Nguyn Th Thuy, Nguyn Th Thuy, Nguyn Th Thuy  Nhiu em  i hc vi s im khi A v khi B rt cao nh: Nguyn Ph Huy, Nguyn Th Ngc H, o Thanh Tng&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>Trong s trng thnh ca nh trng, t Ho  Sinh  Cng Ngh cng  trng thnh cng nm thng. T lc ban u ch c vi thy c dy kim nhim nhiu mn, sau 45 nm,  c 38 thy c  v ang tham gia ging dy v sinh hot chuyn mn  t. Mi thy c n y vi nhng iu kin khc nhau nhng u c nt chung l gn b vi t, yu ngh, c gng ht mnh v hc sinh. C nhng thy c ch ging dy ti trng trong thi gian ngn nhng n tng v tp th t vn cn mi trong k c mi ngi. </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>Cho mng k nim 45 nm thnh lp trng, tp th t Ho  Sinh  Cng Ngh s tip tc phn u thi ua dy tt, hc tt, gi vng danh hiu tp th lao ng tin tin. Mi thnh vin ca t s c gng nng cao nng lc chuyn mn, trau di o c ngh nghip, tch cc hc hi  nhanh chng vn ln p ng yu cu mi trong gio dc, phn u xng ng vi truyn thng tt p ca t cng nh ca nh trng v s tin cy ca hc sinh v x hi.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">T trng ng Thanh m </span></p>', 1, 1, 0, 6, '2011-11-08 13:27:30', 62, '', '2012-04-10 11:50:27', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-08 13:16:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 18, 0, 6, '', '', 0, 158, 'robots=\nauthor='),
