(155, 'Trng trung hc ph thng C Loa v p truyn thng 45 nm "Xy dng v pht trin"', 'trng-trung-hc-ph-thong-c-loa-v-p-truyn-thng-45-nm-qxay-dng-va-phat-trinq', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: windowtext;">Trng trung hc ph thng C Loa thnh lp nm 1966 v c xy dng trn mnh t C Loa lch s thuc huyn ng Anh, ngoi thnh H Ni. Thi k u , trng c t ti Bi Miu, xm Mt, x C Loa v gi l trng cp 3 ng Anh A. n nm hc 1969-1970, trng chnh thc chuyn v x ng Hi, huyn ng Anh ly tn l trng cp 3 C Loa v nay l trng trung hc ph thng C Loa.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: windowtext;"><img style="float: left;" src="data/giaoduc/logo truong.jpg" alt="" height="159" width="136" />Nm trn mnh t a linh nhn kit, ni cn in nhng du tch ca mt triu i, mt on s bi hng. Thnh C Loa gn lin vi truyn thuyt rt m , su sc, y tnh trit hc v nhn vn ca dn tc Vit: T vic vua An Dng Vng nh , xy thnh  dng nc v gi nc; n chic n thn Kim Quy c sc mnh ch ni th ni tan, ch ngn th ngn chy to nn chin cng k diuTrng trung hc ph thng C Loa  tng bc trng thnh trong ci ni truyn thng lch s v vn ha, 45 nm vi nhng du n khng phai,  cc th h thy, tr cng nhau n li v thm nim tin, nim t ho v nhng nt truyn thng tt p ca nh trng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nm thng u tin trng c thnh lp l nhng nm khng chin chng M cu nc y th thch. Hnh nh trng trong nhng nm xa xa y, ch c 7 lp hc, chia lm 3 ni ( xm Mt, Bi Miu, Mch Trng), phng hc tranh tre, l na. D c nhiu kh khn nhng thy v tr nh trng vn lun n lc thi ua  Dy tt- Hc tt ; trong 9 nm lin (1966-1975) , trng lin tc c cng nhn l trng tin tin chng M cu nc . Chnh nhng nm chin tranh khc lit y, nhiu th h thy, tr ca trng  ln ng  X dc Trng Sn i cu nc , chin u ti cc chin trng B-C-K; trong s  c ngi  hi sinh tnh mng, c ngi b mt phn mu tht ca mnh  chin trng, tr thnh lit s, thng bnh binh; c ngi tr thnh dng s dit M.<img style="float: left;" src="data/giaoduc/Gioithieu/dsc_4925.jpg" alt="" height="207" width="312" /></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: windowtext;"> Trong xu th pht trin chung ca x hi, tp th gio vin nh trng lun  thc su sc trch nhim ln lao v s mnh cao c ca s nghip trng ngi nn mi thy, c u c gng ht mnh, u t ln c cng sc, tr tu trong vic t hon thin v p dng cc phng php ging dy theo yu cu mi: Ch  nh hng, pht trin t duy sng to ca hc sinh, a cng ngh thng tin vo phc v ging dy kt hp vi cch dy truyn thng l bng en phn trng. Nh trng rt ch trng n vic nng cao cht lng dy v hc; to mi iu kin thun li  gio vin ch ng nng cao trnh : T t hc,</span></p>\r\n<table class="MsoNormalTable" style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #ffcc99; border-collapse: collapse; margin-left: 6.75pt; margin-right: 6.75pt; height: 391px; width: 278px;" align="right" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style="height: 134.2pt;">\r\n<td style="width: 168.35pt; border: 1pt solid #0070c0; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 134.2pt;" valign="top" width="224">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: windowtext;">Mi nm hc qua i u nh du s trng thnh vng vng ca nh trng: S lng hc sinh ng k vo trng nhiu hn, im u vo lp 10 cng tng ln ng k. T nm 1991-2000 v cho n nay, quy m nh trng ngy cng pht trin, gi n nh t 36-40 lp hc; mi nm c t 1600- 1900 hc sinh.  lun c c s quan tm, tin cy ca cc cp lnh o, cha m hc sinh, nhn dn a phng, ng thi khng nh c v tr ca nh trng trong ngnh Gio dc Th ; thy v tr trng trung hc ph thng C Loa qua nhiu th h cng nhau mit mi, n lc, khng ngng phn u vn ln trong cng tc dy v hc  xy p cho trng ln mnh. Vi truyn thng D kh khn n u cng phi tip tc thi ua dy tt v hc tt,  Tt c v hc sinh thn yu,  Dy tr bng c tm lng, xy dng  Trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc; trng  c c mt i ng ng o cc cn b qun l gii, gio vin dy gii, gio vin ch nhim gii, c vn on gii, cn b Cng on xut scTnh n nay, i ng cn b, gio vin, nhn vin ca trng l 104 ngi, 94 gio vin t trnh  chun chim 100%, trong  21 gio vin c trnh  trn chun, chim 23%; nhiu gio vin l chin s thi ua, gio vin dy gii cp thnh ph.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: windowtext;">t bi dng, n m cc lp hng dn son ging gio n in t, mi chuyn gia Vin Gio Dc v dy i mi phng php dy hc . Hng thng, t nhm chuyn mn sinh hot u n, duy tr thng xuyn hot ng d gi v thao ging  nhng thy, c giu kinh nghim s l ngi truyn la, a  gip  nhiu th h ng nghip k cn trng thnh. Hng nm, trng c 25%- 40% gio vin tham gia vit sng kin kinh nghim  c kt, chia s vi ng nghip. Cng vi vic xy dng, hon thin i ng cn b, gio vin vng vng v t tng chnh tr, gii v chuyn mn nghip v; nh trng lun quan tm n cht lng gio dc ton din hc sinh, c bit quan tm n gio dc o c v vn ha: T l hc sinh xp loi hc lc kh gii, hnh kim kh tt; t l hc sinh lp 12  tt nghip, hc sinh gii thnh ph ngy mt tng ( nu nh nm 1997 ch 3-5 hc sinh ca trng t hc sinh gii thnh ph th nm hc 2007-2008 t 9 hc sinh, nm hc 2008-2009 c 11 hc sinh t gii, trong s  c hc sinh t gii quc gia ). Trong nhng nm qua , s hc sinh t gii t 3%-5%, hc sinh tin tin t 35%-40%; s hc sinh xp loi o c kh, tt u t trn 95%, loi yu di 1%; t l hc sinh thi  vo cc trng i hc, cao ng t 25%-30%; t l thi  tt nghip u t trn 95%, c nm t 99%. c bit nm hc 2010-2011, c 13 hc sinh t gii hc sinh gii thnh ph. T l thi  tt nghip l 100%. T l hc sinh xp loi kh, gii vt ch tiu  ra trong hi ngh CBVC u nm: Loi gii t 176 hc sinh chim 9,04%, tng 39 hc sinh so vi nm hc trc; loi kh t 922 hc sinh, chim 47,35%, tng 93 hc sinh so vi nm hc trc. C c thnh qu , l c qu trnh c gng vt bc, phn u vn ln ca tp th cn b, gio vin , hc sinh nh trng.</span></p>\r\n', '\r\n<table class="MsoNormalTable" style="width: 546px; background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #ffe4cd; border-collapse: collapse;" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 185.4pt; border: 1pt solid white; padding: 0in 5.4pt;" valign="top" width="247">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: windowtext;">Tri qua qu trnh xy dng v pht trin, trng trung hc ph thng C Loa  t c nhng thnh tch ng t ho: T nm 1998 n nay lin tc l trng hc tin tin xut sc cp thnh ph, nm hc 2007-2008 nh trng c cng nhn l n v l c u thi ua thnh ph H Ni; Trong nhiu nm, Chi b lun l t chc c s ng trong sch, vng mnh; Cng on c s trng hc lun t danh hiu vng mnh; t chc on thanh nin  c nhn bng khen ca Thnh on, Trung ng on. Thng 5 nm 2009, trng vinh d c UBND thnh ph H Ni ra Quyt nh s 2400/Q- UBND v vic tng Bng cng nhn l trng THPT t chun quc gia giai on 2001-2010; thng 6 nm 2010, UBND thnh ph H Ni ra quyt nh s 3165/Q-UBND cng nhn trng l c s gio dc t tiu chun cht lng cp  3, cp  cao nht.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: windowtext;">45 tri quaNgi trng trung hc ph thng C Loa trong hin ti c khung cnh s phm khang trang, xanh- sch- p. Vi 39 phng hc  tiu chun din tch v nh sng, trong  c 03 phng th nghim L, Ha, Sinh; 03 phng thc hnh tin hc vi 100 my tnh ni mng; 02 phng hc a nng. Th vin vi ngun sch a dng, th loi phong ph. Phng truyn thng vi hnh nh n thn v trang sch lm biu tng mang n mt khng gian truyn thng thing ling m p. Bn cnh  l khu lin hp th thao v h thng cy xanh ta bng rp mt sn trng; mi khi ma h v, trong nng vng chi chang sc mu rc la ca hoa phng xen ln mu tm du dng, bng khung, man mc ca cnh bng lng   li trong lng thy, tr nh trng tht nhiu cm xc kh qun.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: windowtext;">Th h ni tip th h, t ho v qu kh, trn trng hin ti  hng ti tng lai. Thy, tr trng trung hc ph thng C Loa ngy nay , ang v s vit tip truyn thng v vang ca nh trng vi nim tin, mong c, quyt tm dng xy ngi trng ngy cng pht trin ton din, xng ng vi s tn nhim cao ca cc bc cha m hc sinh, ca a phng, xng ng l im sng ca ngnh Gio dc Th .</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;" align="right"><span style