(166, 'T NGOI NG - TH DC - QUC PHNG- HI NHP VA PHAT TRIN', 't-ngoi-ng-th-dc-quc-phong-hoi-nhap-va-phat-trien', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;" align="justify">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style="width: 120px; height: 147px;" id="table3" align="left" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://nguoivienxu.vietnamnet.vn/dataimages/original/images155882_coloa1.jpg"> </a>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="data/giaoduc/dsc_0114.jpg" alt="" height="180" width="141" /></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="Image" style="text-align: center;">\r\n<p><strong>C  Thi inh</strong><br />T trng t Ngoai ng- Th duc<br />Quc phong</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 6pt; text-indent: 36pt; text-align: justify;">Cng vi s hnh thnh v pht trin ca trng THPT C Loa trong 45 nm qua l s ra i ca mt tp th lun on kt gn b v tng bc trng thnh,  l t ngoi ng- th dc- quc phng.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;Khi thnh lp trng nm 1966 b mn ngoi ng ( thuc t x hi ca trng) ch c hai Thy gio dy ngoi ng Thy  dy ting Trung v Thy Hng dy ting Nga. Nm 1992, cng vi xu th pht trin ca t nc nhu cu ca x hi v ting Anh ngy cng cao i hi trng phi c mt i ng gio vin c trnh  chuyn mn vng vng, m trong thi im  gio vin ting Anh trn c nc u thiu trm trng . Khng qun ngi kh khn cc Thy C gio dy ting Trung, ting Nga v cc b mn khc ca trng  tnh nguyn i hc bi dng  chuyn i b mn mnh ang ging dy sang dy b mn ting Anh.( C Tam dy ting Trung sang dy ting Anh, C Tuyt Mai dy ting Nga sang dy ting Anh, Thy Quc Lan dy K thut sang dy ting Anh). Trng cng ln mnh, b mn ngoi ng ngy cng thu ht nhiu thnh vin mi, n nm 2004 b mn ngoi ng tch t x hi ra thnh mt t b mn mi,  l t T NGOI NG - TH DC - QUC PHNG. Hin nay, t c 17 thnh vin thuc ba nhm ngoi ng (ting Anh), th dc v quc phng. Cc thnh vin trong t l nhng Thy C gio vng chuyn mn,nhit tnh trong ging dy v lun phn u hon thnh tt nhim v ca mnh.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Bn cnh ci chung, mi Thy C trong t  bit pht huy th mnh ca mnh  xy dng t b mn ngy cng vng mnh. Nhiu Thy C t danh hiu gio vin dy gii cp thnh ph, nhiu nm lin l chin s thi ua : Thy ng Ngc Hng, C  Th nh, C Ng Thy H, Thy Trn Thanh Bnh, Thy Nguyn vn Tr. Nhiu th h hc tr  c cc Thy C du dt t nhiu gii cao trong cc k thi hc sinh gii thnh ph nh cc em : inh th Li ( t 8 huy chng : 3 vng, 2 bc, 1 ng trong hi khe ph ng thnh ph H Ni . Ngoi ra em cn t 2 gii chy bo H Ni mi), Nguyn Th Hng Minh ( t gii ba cuc thi ht ting Anh ton thnh ph), Trnh th Linh, Nguyn th phng Hoa ( Gii khuyn khch mn ting Anh),.... Khng ch dng li  , mi Thy C trong t cn l mt tm gng sng v tinh thn hc v t hc. Cc Thy C lun lun trn tr  tm ra phng php ging dy c hiu qu nht cho i tng hc sinh ca mnh, lun lun t mnh hc hi, nng cao v cng ngh thng tin  son ra nhng bi ging in t c cht lng gip hc sinh ca mnh tip cn vi lng tri thc khng l, nhm to s hng th, trc quan cho hc sinh. Nh vo nng lc chuyn mn vng vng, s nhit tnh, tn ty, kin nhn, khng qun ngi kh khn ca cc gio vin, c bit l cc gio vin ging dy khi 12 m t lun<span> </span>c t l hc sinh lp 12 ( mn ting Anh) t im TNPT trn trung bnh<span> </span>cao hn kt qu ca ton thnh ph. Khng nhng ch quan tm ti tri thc m cc Thy C trong t cn gip  nhiu em hc sinh c hon cnh kh khn trong trng. Nhn thy s thnh t ca hc sinh l mt nim hnh phc v b bn ca ngi Thy.  cng l mt trong nhng ng lc tip sc cho cc thnh vin ca t<span> </span>ngoi ng- th dc- quc phng ngy cng vng tin, ngy cng yu ngh v ng vng trn bc ging. Trong 45 nm qua,  c nhiu th h hc sinh ra trng, phn ln cc em  trng thnh v thnh t.  l mt mt nim hnh phc ln lao nht ca ngi gio vin, cng nh ca mi thnh vin t chng ti. Bn cnh cng tc chuyn mn, nhiu Thy C trong t cn kim nhim cc cng tc on th :Thy Trn Thanh Bnh ( th dc- quc phng) lm c vn on trng, Thy ng Ngc Hng ( th dc) tham gia cng on, C  Th nh ( ting Anh) tham gia cng tc trong chi y ca trng. Cc gio vin trong t u c  thc tham gia xy dng tp th, lun nhit tnh vi cc phong tro chung v vn ngh v th dc th thao.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 6pt; text-indent: 36pt; text-align: justify;">T ngoi ng - th dc - quc phng lun lun on kt gn b mt lng mong mun xy dng t v trng THPT C Loa ngy cng pht trin, ln mnh, c nhiu thnh cng v t nhiu thnh tch hn na  xng ng vi lng tin yu v s tin cy ca ph huynh v hc sinh.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 6, '2011-11-04 09:04:57', 62, '', '2012-04-10 11:49:14', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-04 08:54:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 21, 0, 5, '', '', 0, 163, 'robots=\nauthor='),
