(158, 'Gii thiu di tch C Loa', 'gii-thiu-di-tich-c-loa', '', '<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong> Thnh C Loa gn lin vi nhng truyn thuyt k th ca dn tc Vit, v vic vua An Dng Vng nh , xy thnh; V chic n thn Kim Quy bn mt pht h hng trm tn gic; V mi tnh bi thng v cm ng ca M Chu - Trng Thu... T bao i nay, ngi thnh c ny cng vi nhng nhn vt lch s c huyn thoi ho  i vo tim thc ca ngi dn Vit Nam.</strong> </span></p>\r\n<table id="table3" style="height: 183px; width: 241px;" align="left" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://nguoivienxu.vietnamnet.vn/dataimages/original/images155882_coloa1.jpg"> <img src="http://e-cadao.com/queta/coloa1.jpg" style="float: left;" border="0" height="153" width="219" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="Image"><span style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #000000;"><a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=157:ban-giam-hiu-nha-trng&amp;catid=157:bgh-co-cau-to-chuc-&amp;Itemid=162"><span style="color: #000000;"></span></a><a><span style="color: #000000;">y l to thnh c vo bc nht</span></a></span> Vit Nam c vua Thc An Dng Vng xy t th k th 3 trc Cng nguyn  lm kinh  nc u Lc (tn nc Vit Nam thi ), nay thuc huyn ng Anh, ngoi thnh H Ni.&nbsp; aaa</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Thnh c xy dng kiu vng c (nn gi l Loa thnh) tng truyn c ti 9 vng, di thnh ngoi l ho su ngp nc thuyn b i li c. Ngy nay  c Loa cn li 3 vng thnh t: Thnh Ngoi (8km), Thnh Gia (hnh a gic, chu vi 6,5km) v Thnh Trong (hnh ch nht, chu vi 1,6km). Thn thnh ngy nay cn c chiu cao trung bnh t 4-5m, c ch cn cao ti 12m, chn thnh rng ti 20-30m. Cc ca ca 3 vng thnh cng oc b tr rt kho; khng h nm cng trn mt trc thng m lch cho i rt nhiu. Do  ng ni hai ca thnh  cng mt hng u l mt ng quanh co, li c  phng ng  hai bn nn gy rt nhiu tr ngi cho qun ch khi tin nh thnh. </span></p>\r\n', '\r\n<table id="table4" style="height: 165px; width: 208px;" align="right" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://nguoivienxu.vietnamnet.vn/dataimages/original/images155883_coloa-lehoi.jpg"> <img src="http://e-cadao.com/queta/coloa-lehoi.jpg" style="float: right;" border="0" height="135" width="184" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="Image">\r\n<p align="center"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: #ff3300; font-size: xx-small;">L hi n C Loa</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Qua cc giai on lch s, C Loa c rt nhiu tn: Loa thnh (thnh c), thnh Cn Ln, thnh T Long, Cu thnh, Thnh Vit Vng, thnh Kh L, C Loa thnh. n th k th X, thi k Ng Quyn lm vua, C Loa li tr thnh kinh  ln th hai. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">T trung tm thnh ph, i 18 km n x C Loa thuc huyn ng Anh, bn s tm thy vt tch cn li ca ba vng thnh xa bng t v ni cc nh kho c tm c hng vn mi tn ng, li cy, ru st, xng th vt...</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Qua cng lng, cng l cng Thnh trong l ti nh lng C Loa. Theo truyn thuyt th  l nn c ca in ng triu, ni b quan triu hi ngy xa nn trong nh cn tm honh phi "Ng triu di quy".</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Cnh nh l Am B Cha tc l miu th cng cha M Chu, nm np di gc a gi c th. Miu am b bng nh cuc i ngn ngi ca nng cng cha ng thng "tri tim lm ch  ln u". Trong am c mt tng  hnh ngi ct u. Ai cng bo  l tng M Chu.<br /> Qua am M Chu ti n Thng, tc n An Dng Vng, tng truyn l dng trn nn ni cung ngy trc. n ny mi lm li hi u th k XX, c i rng   bc tam cp ca n l di vt i Trn hoc L s. Trong n c tng An Dng Vng bng ng mi c cng dp lm li n. Trc n l Ging Ngc, tng truyn l ni Trng Thu t t v hi hn. Nc ging ny m em ra ngc trai th ngc sng bi phn!</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Nm 1962, C Loa c xp hng di tch lch s - vn ho cp nh nc. N c y  cc loi hnh di tch: nh, n, cha, am, miu. Trong  hm cha bit bao gi tr vn ho Vit Nam qua bao th h.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Trong khu vc Thnh Ni cn lu gi nhiu di tch lch s - kin trc ngh thut: Khu n Thng th An Dng Vng, khu nh Ng triu di quy, am th M Chu v cha Bo Sn vi hng trm pho tng...</span></p>\r\n<table id="table5" style="height: 127px; width: 158px;" align="left" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://nguoivienxu.vietnamnet.vn/dataimages/original/images155884_coloa-den.jpg"> <img src="http://e-cadao.com/queta/coloa-den.jpg" style="float: left;" border="0" height="97" width="140" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="Image">\r\n<p align="center"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: #ff3300; font-size: xx-small;">n C Loa</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Cc nh kho c hc cn trng by  y rt nhiu hin vt qu gi ca ngi Vit c  khai qut c trong lng t C Loa: Trng ng C Loa, tin ng, ru ng, hng nghn mi tn ng, li cy, cc vt dng bng gm, t nung,...</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Hng nm, l hi C Loa tng nh vua An Dng Vng c t chc vo ma xun, ngy mng 6 thng ging. C 8 lng trong x C Loa t chc rc kiu truyn thng t v sn nh C Loa, dng l, th hin tm lng thnh knh i vi v vua c cng lao to ln trong vic dng nc v gi nc, ch ng sau cc vua Hng.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Hng ti 1000 nm Thng Long - H Ni (nm 2010), C Loa ang tng bc c tu b, tn to  xng ng vi Th  ngn nm vn hin, Thnh ph H Ni  lp d n Quy hoch bo tn, tn to v pht huy tc dng di tch khu thnh C Loa. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Khu di tch C Loa theo quy hoch mi s gm: khu di tch thnh C Loa, khu tng nim An Dng Vng v cc di tch lch s vn ho khc, vi tng din tch hn 830 ha thuc a phn cc x C Loa, Vit Hng, Dc T, Uy N. Pha ty bc gii hn bi ng quy hoch ni khu  th 34 (d kin) i khu cng nghip ng Anh, pha ng bc c gii hn bi ng C Loa - Yn Vin, pha nam v ty nam gii hn bi ng lin khu vc huyn ng Anh. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Quy hoch khu di tch C Loa s c thc hin n nm 2020 vi cc khu quy hoch chnh: <br /> Khu vc di tch thnh: Cc vng thnh bao gm lu v ho c bo v chng s xm phm, vng thnh ni s c tn to li ton b vi chiu di hn 1.700m. Thnh ngoi v thnh trung s tn to li mt s on  xung cp  phc v vic khai thc di tch, cc on tn to ch yu tp trung ti 8 ca ra vo. </span></p>\r\n<table id="table6" style="height: 135px; width: 169px;" align="right" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://nguoivienxu.vietnamnet.vn/dataimages/original/images155885_coloa.jpg"> <img src="http://e-cadao.com/queta/coloa.jpg" style="float: right;" border="0" width="150" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="Image"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Khu trung tm di tch C Loa bao gm: khu vc sn tip n t ti pha nam ca thnh ni; khu vc trung tm thnh ni s hnh thnh mt khng gian tp trung ca ton b khu di tch vi quy m 5 ha  c th b tr cc cng trnh bo tng trng by cc di ch kho c, t chc cc hot ng l hi vn ho lm sng li cc phong tc tp qun ca ngi Vit... </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Khu vc cc di tch kin trc nh: nh, cha, m M Chu... c u t  tn to. <br /> Khu vc cc di ch kho c chnh ng Vng, Bi Mn v ng My s c xy dng thnh cc bo tng tng... </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Khu vc s pht trin mi  h tr khu di tch gm: Cng vin ti pha nam khu vc di tch vi quy m hn 74ha; khu vc trng hoa, cy cnh ti khu vc bc sng Hong v phc hi mt phn din tch mt nc to li mt phn din mo cnh quan xa... </span></p>', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2011-10-29 09:56:02', 62, '', '2012-04-10 07:38:13', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-29 09:56:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 12, 0, 7, '', '', 0, 186, 'robots=\nauthor='),
