(154, 'T Vn ngy y...By gi', 't-vn-ngay-ybay-gi', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 130%;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 130%; font-family: Arial;">Nm cnh con ng giao thng ni gia quc l 3 vi ng vnh ai bao quanh sng ung thuc a phn x ng Hi c mt ngi trng vi nhng to nh cao tng rt khang trang- Trng THPT C Loa. C l th h tr gio vin chng ti hm nay t ai tng tng c nhng nm 70 ca th k XX cc lp hc ca trng ch l nhng ngi nh tranh vch t do cc bc ph huynh, thy c gio v hc sinh t lm nn  hc. n nhng nm 80 nhng cn nh y  c thay th bng nhng ng nh xy lp ngi, c kh hn song vn l biu hin ca s ngho nn, n s, thiu thn. T lc c s vt cht cn kh khn th, by gi khi b mt ca trng  thay i hon ton theo hng hin i ho th thy v tr trng THPT C Loa ni chung, t vn ni ring vn lun c xem l mt i gia nh vi mi m tnh thng, vi s kht khao vn ln  chim lnh nhng nh cao ca tm hn, tri thc v cuc sng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 130%;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 130%; font-family: Arial;">Nm 2011 nh trng t chc k nim 45 nm ngy thnh lp. Mt nim vui, nim hn hoan phn khi n vi tt c th h thy v tr chng ti. 45 nm mt con s c th l khim tn nhng n  nh du mt b dy lch s m khng phi trng no cng c, 45 nm vi bit bao k nim kh qun ca mi gio vin  tng sng v cng tc ti trng. Ln theo nhng nm thng  qua c l chng ti hm nay khng th im ht c tn tui, nhng ng gp ca cc thy c tng l thnh vin trong t- nhng ngi  t nn mng cho s pht trin, thnh t ca t Ng vn hm nay. Cho n thi im ny nhiu k s tm hn ca t  hon thnh nhim v trng ngi, tr v an hng tui gi vui vy cng con chu, cng c nhng ng nghip, nhng bc cha ch chng ti  v vi ci vnh hng mang theo bao c nguyn...Nhng tn tui ca cc thy c vn c th h tr chng ti nhc n nh mt nim t ho, mt lng bit n trn trng. Chnh nhng th h gio vin i trc  gip chng ti tin bc mt cch vng vng hn, t tin hn. Chng ti khng th qun nhng tm gng v o c, v nng lc chuyn mn v tm lng yu ngh, mn tr ca c Nguyn Th Y, thy Ng B Dc, c Trn Th Tu, Nguyn Th Nhung, Hong Xun Trng, Hong Minh Thin v c nhng thy c cn rt tr hm nay nh: c Dng Th Cc, Nguyn Th T, inh Th Loan,V Thanh Thu, Trn Diu Thu...</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 130%;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 130%; font-family: Arial;"><img style="float: left;" src="data/giaoduc/Gioithieu/dsc_0610.jpg" alt="" height="219" width="329" />45 nm pht trin ca trng cng l 45 nm t vn ng gp khng t thnh tch to nn ting vang ca trng THPT C Loa. Nim vui, nim t ho c dng ln trong lng mi chng ti hm nay. Trong bc tin 45 nm ca trng t vn cng t ho bi khng t cc thnh vin ca t  phn u v tr thnh nhng ngi lnh o xut sc cho li a con thuyn THPT C Loa n nhng bn b vinh quang nh Nguyn Th Y hiu trng ca trng t 1976 - 1991, thy Ng B Dc hiu trng ca trng t 1992 - 2004, thy T B Cnh l hiu trng t 2005 - 2008, c Nguyn Th Nhung Ch tch Cng on t 2004 - 2007. Chng ti cng nh c mi nm hc phong tro thi ua ng k gio vin dy gii, gio vin ch nhim gii cc cp c pht ng cc thnh vin trong t tuy c i cht cn n o, do d song ai cng mun c khng nh mnh, dng mu vn chng vn m , thi thc ng vin chng ti  ri thnh tch ca t  c lp nn ngy mt nhiu, ngy mt cao hn. Cc c Nguyn Th ng, Trn Th Tu, Nguyn Th Nhung, Hon Xun Trng, Dng Th Cc, Nguyn Th T, inh Th Loan... khng t ln t cc danh hiu gio vin ch nhim gii, gio vin ging dy gii... Nhiu sng kin kinh nghim v cng tc ch nhim, chuyn mn t cc gii ca Thnh Ph mang n nhng ng gp khng nh  nng cao cht lng dy v hc gip  ng nghip bi dng tay ngh, vng vng hn trong gio dc, truyn th kin thc cho hc sinh. Vi s phn u khng ngng ca cc th h gio vin trong t rt nhiu hc sinh  ot nhng gii thng cao trong cc k thi hc sinh gii cp thnh ph, cp quc gia. Hc sinh Phm Thu An kho (1989-1992)  lm rng danh cho t vn v cho nh trng vi thnh tch nh cao: Gii nh (khng c gii nht) cp Quc gia  b mn vn nm hc (1991-1992)</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 130%;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 130%; font-family: Arial;">Nhng hc sinh  ot gii nh, ba thnh ph nh cc em: Nguyn Dip Lan, Thu Linh, Thu An....</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 130%;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 130%; font-family: Arial;">Khng bit t bao gi ci tn t ng vn trng THPT C Loa  tr nn gn b, thn thng vi mi thnh vin trong t n vy. Tht ra khng phi lc no cuc sng, sinh hot ca t cng xui cho mt mi. Sng gi cng c lc ni ln trong mt vi cuc hp, trong nhng bui nhn xt nh gi gi dy. Song tt c ch gip  cho mi ngi trong gia nh vn chng ny hiu nhau, yu thng nhau nhiu hn m thi.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 130%; font-family: Arial;">K nim 45 nm ngy thnh lp trng, y l dp th h gio vin, hc sinh c gp nhau, nhng gio vin t vn c hi t, chc chn chng ti s c rt nhiu, rt nhiu k nim  tm s. Ngh n iu  trong lng chng ti li trn ngp mt nim vui, nim t ho v s xc ng lng lng n kh t.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 130%; font-family: Arial;">T trng Dng Th Cc<br /></span></p>', '', 1, 1, 0, 6, '2011-10-29 04:00:27', 62, '', '2012-04-10 11:48:23', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-29 03:59:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 6, 0, 4, '', '', 0, 112, 'robots=\nauthor='),
