(151, 'K hoch cng tc thng 10/2011', 'k-hoch-cong-tac-thang-102011', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal"><strong>\r\n<table style="float: left;" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="logo truong" src="images/logo%20truong.jpg" height="194" width="167" /></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nI- Cng tc gio dc t tng - o c:</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Tuyn truyn v cc hot ng hng ti L k nim 45 nm ngy thnh lp trng THPT C Loa&nbsp;; pht ng thng hc tt, tun hc tt, gi hc tt trong hc sinh, gio vin. Hc sinh thc hin tt k cng n np, khng i hc mun, khng b tit, khng vi phm ni quy nh trng, thc hin tt an ton giao thng, thc hin hnh vi ng x, giao tip thn thin ca ngi hc sinh th  thanh lch.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Tuyn truyn kt qu i hi on trng nm hc 2011- 2012.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Trin khai ging dy ti liu Thanh lch, vn minh cho hc sinh 10, 11 vo cc gi sinh hot lp.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">- Tng cng vai tr ca gio vin ch nhim lp trong cc hot ng phong tro ca hc sinh do nh trng pht ng v giao nhim v; hng ngy kim tra, n c, pht hin v c bin php gio dc nhng hc sinh c biu hin vi phm quy ch ca trng, lp mt cch hiu qu.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- on thanh nin thng xuyn kim tra thc hin thi ua ca cc lp, ca hc sinh pht hin hc sinh vi phm n np, k cng v cc quy nh ca nh trng. Biu dng tm gng tp th, c nhn thc hin tt nhim v; thng bo kt qu thi ua ca hc sinh trn bng tin, ng thi thng bo danh sch hc sinh chm tin, hc sinh vi phm n np ca cc lp trong thng 9  gio dc.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Yu cu cc lc lng gio dc trong nh trng, bao gm cc cn b, gio vin, nhn vin thc hin ng b vic thc hin nhim v qun l, gio dc hc sinh khi cc em n trng tham gia cc hot ng gio dc, to bc chuyn bin mnh m v k cng n np trong dy v hc.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal"><strong>II- Cng tc chuyn mn:</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Tng cng cng tc kim tra thc hin quy ch chuyn mn ca gio vin.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Tip tc bi dng hc sinh gii khi 12, m bo thi gian, ni dung v cht lng n tp  c c kt qu thi tt nht vo ngy 18 thng 10 nm 2011.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Duy tr bi dng chuyn  cho cc lp u cao, bi dng, ph o cho hc sinh c nhu cu, t nguyn.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Trin khai k hoch d gi, kim tra chuyn mn trong trng, cc t chuyn mn, a hot ng ny i vo n np, cht lng, trnh hnh thc.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"> </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;"> </span>- Cc t chuyn mn tp trung d gi gio vin tham gia thi dy chuyn  gio dc t tng H Ch Minh trong mn GDCD; d gi gio vin tham gia thi mn Ngoi ng, Ng vn v a l d thi cp cm.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;"> </span>- Cc t chuyn mn hon thin ch tiu thc hin k hoch nm hc, ng k sng kin kinh nghim,  dng dy hc t lm.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"> </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal"><strong>III- Cng tc c s vt cht- LHN  Dy ngh: </strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- n c hc sinh hc khi 11 ngh ti trung tm s 6, t chc cho nhng hc sinh ngh hc ngh i lao ng ti trng.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Tng cng cng tc y t, v sinh phng dch, cc khu vc nh v sinh, khun vin nh trng;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- T chc lao ng sp xp h thng cc phng sinh hot t nhm b mn, phng th vin, phng thc hnh vt l, tin hc, phng hp hi ng, phng lm vic cho ph hp vi c s vt cht mi.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"> </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"> </span><strong>IV- Sinh hot tp th:</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Cng on kt hp vi Ban v s tin b ph n t chc hi tho cc chuyn  v gii vic trng- m vic nh, v c gio ti nng duyn dngT chc thi u mt s mn th thao trong cc t chuyn mn- giao cho cng on, nhm TD xy dng KH, trin khai.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- B phn<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"> </span>bo v, on thanh nin, gim th nh trng, gio vin ch nhim t chc kim tra vic thc hin mc ng phc, in thoi, v kh trong hc sinh khi n trng hc tp, rn luyn.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Trin khai hot ng sinh hot tp th trong gi cho c u tun, on thanh nin ch o st st ni dung, kim duyt ni dung chun b ca cc lp hc sinh trc khi trin khai, nng cht lng, hiu qu gi cho c u tun.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- on thanh nin, cc gio vin ch nhim la chn hc sinh ca lp, trin khai t chc thi hc sinh thanh lch cp nh trng, cho mng 45 nm .</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- on thanh nin phi hp vi nhm th dc, trin khai luyn tp th dc nhp iu<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"> </span> biu din nhn dp 45 nm, t chc hi khe ph ng, thi cc mn TDTT gia cc lp, khi lp</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Tip tc luyn tp mn ma ht truyn thng, cc tit mc vn ngh  biu din vo ngy l k nim 45 nm. Mi chuyn gia gin dng v luyn tp.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Chi on gio vin xy dng k hoch, luyn tp cc tit mc vn ngh ht v ngh , nh gio cho mng ngy thnh lp trng v ngy nh gio VN 20  11.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"> </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal"><strong>V- Cng tc qun l - t chc:</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Tip tc chun b cc ni dung cho L k nim 45 nm thnh lp trng. T chc cc hot ng phong tro, hot ng vn ha vn ngh cho GV, HS.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Kim tra cc khon thu ca cc lp, GVCN, GV b mn: qu lp, thu khc...</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Cht danh sch hc sinh cc lp tham gia mua bo him y t, bo him x hi, m bo quyn li hc sinh.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"> </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Xt ht thi gian th vic cho cc gio vin tuyn dng nm 2011.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Sp xp thi kho biu n nh, b tr cho gio vin, nhn vin ngh ch  thai sn ng thi gian, gio vin mi chuyn v trng cng tc.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Xt nng lng thng xuyn t 2 v trc thi hn nm 2011.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- Tip on thanh tra, kim tra cng tc thu u nm ca S Gio dc &amp; o to.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal">- B tr sp xp c s vt cht cc phng ban chuyn mn, trin khai trang website ca trng, ng dng cng ngh thng tin trong qun l.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- B sung trang thit b cho cc phng, ban, t chuyn mn phc v sinh hot chuyn mn, dy v hc.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- Tng cng cng tc An ninh trt t trong nh trng, ti thi im hc sinh n trng v khi tan trng.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Hiu trng</strong></p>', 1, 2, 0, 11, '2011-10-29 03:47:08', 62, '', '2012-04-10 07:34:08', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-29 03:44:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 6, 0, 24, '', '', 0, 188, 'robots=\nauthor=');
