(149, 'Cng on Trng THPT C Loa', 'cong-oan-trsng-thpt-c-loa', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;">Trng THPT C Loa ra i trong hon cnh t nc ng thi thc hin 2 nhim v xy dng CNXH  Min Bc v khng chin chng M thng nht t nc  min Nam. y l thi k t nc gp rt nhiu kh khn, c s vt cht phc v cho vic dy v hc thiu thn, trng lp phi i s tn  chung nh dn. Vic hc tp, sinh hot ca gio vin v hc sinh c thc hin trong cc cn phng tranh tre na l tm b, thiu sch, v, bt v nhiu vt dng cn thit khc.... Thc hin li dy ca Bc H: "D kh khn n u cng phi tip tc thi ua Dy tt v Hc tt", Cng on nh trng  lm tt vai tr ng vin gip , quan tm chm lo i sng ca cng on vin, gio dc lng yu nc, yu CNXH, tt c v min Nam thn yu; rn luyn np sng lm vic thi chin- trng hc ng thi l hm tr n-  va dy hc  kin thc, ng chng trnh, va m bo an ton cho gio vin v hc sinh; sn sng dy gip  ng nghip khi m au, bn vic gia nh khng  hc sinh b mt gi m khng cn bt c iu kin g.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal"><span> </span><img style="float: left;" src="data/giaoduc/Gioithieu/cimg2608.jpg" alt="" height="302" width="404" />Sau khi t nc thng nht, c dn tc phi gng mnh khc phc hu qu nng n ca chin tranh, nn kinh t vn hnh theo c ch bao cp, i sng ca thy c gio gp rt nhiu kh khn, thiu thn. Trc hon cnh , cng on cng nh trng  ch ng lin h vi a phng mn t t chc tng gia sn xut cy la, trng rau, chn nui, lm thm ngh ph...  tng thu nhp m bo cuc sng; gim st vic phn phi cc ch  cng khai, cng bng; tng cng cng tc quan h giao lu vi cc a phng, c quan, x nghip trn a bn  tranh th s gip  ng h nhm nng cao i sng cho cng on vin vo cc ngy l tt. Nhng vic lm   gp phn khng nh  duy tr cuc sng c n nh, ng vin tinh thn cc thy c gio vt qua nhng kh khn, bm trng, bm lp  dy tt, cng tc tt.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span> </span>Trong thi k t nc tin hnh cng nghip ha, hin i ha i hi gio dc trong cc nh trng phi i mi  ph hp, thch ng vi thi i, cng on nh trng  lun khng nh c v tr, vai tr, chc nng, nhim v v tm quan trng ca mnh vi t cch l mt t chc chnh tr, phi hp cht ch vi chnh quyn thc hin thng li nhim v gio dc ca ng, Nh nc giao cho v chm lo i sng, bo v quyn li chnh ng, hp php ca ngi lao ng. Trong sut chng ng 45 nm xy dng v trng thnh, ng hnh vi bc i ln ca nh trng n nay cng on  c 105 cng on vin sinh hot  7 t. Cng on khng ngng ln mnh c v s lng v cht lng, pht trin ton din v chnh tr, t tng, t chc, chuyn mn nghip v.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span> </span>Thi ua chnh l ng lc ca s pht trin. Nhn thc su sc c iu ny nn cng tc thi ua khen thng lun c nh trng v cng on quan tm i mi, m bo kp thi v cng bng, c tc dng thc y. Xc nh mt trong nhng nhim v quan trng ca t chc cng on l t chc cc hot ng, phong tro thi ua nhm c v cng on vin on kt, quyt tm phn u hon thnh cc mc tiu, ch tiu ca cc t chc trong nh trng  ra. Trong nhng nm qua, cc phong tro thi ua c s bin chuyn mnh m, nhiu khi sc v t c nhng kt qu ng k gp phn "Dy tt, hc tt: Hng nm, phong tro thi ua hi ging c ng o cng on vin tham gia nhit tnh, t gic, sng to, y l t sinh hot b ch nng cao chuyn mn nghip v. Phong tro vit Sng kin kinh nghim lun duy tr vi s lng v cht lng cao, c S gio dc &amp; o to ghi nhn v khen ngi. Mi phong tro u c cc tp th c nhn in hnh tiu biu nh: Tng kt 5 nm phong tro " Dn ch - K cng - Tnh thng - Trch nhim " giai on 2004  2009, Cng on nh trng c S gio dc &amp; o to tng giy khen; tiu biu phong tro 5 nm thc hin cuc vn ng: "Xy dng Nh trng vn ho - Nh gio mu mc - Hc sinh thanh lch" v "Mi thy c gio l tm gng o c, t hc v sng to" c c gio Nguyn Th Thuy; tiu biu phong tro "Gii vic nc m vic nh" l c gio  Th Phng. Cng on lun khuyn khch cng on vin t lm  dng dy hc nhm pht huy tnh sng to, nng cao cht lng dy hc. Nm hc 2009  2010, trng c 1 sn phm mn Ho hc t gii B, 1 sn phm mn Cng ngh t gii C cp Thnh Ph; tham gia Hi thi thit k gio n in t v phn mm dy hc cp thnh ph nm hc 2008- 2009, trng t 1 gii Nh mn Sinh hc, 1 gii Ba mn Gio dc cng dn. Nh trng- cng on ng vin khuyn khch to iu kin cho cn b- gio vin i hc Cao hc nng cao trnh , kt qu n nay  c 22 cng on vin c trnh  Thc s (c 4 thy c trong Ban Gim hiu). Quan tm u t gip  gio vin nng cao trnh  chuyn mn c th hin r trong cc hi thi gio vin dy gii, kt qu c 10 thy c t gio vin dy gii cp Thnh ph (c bit c thy Nguyn Ngc Hi t gii Nht Hi thi gio vin dy gii cp Thnh ph mn Ton).</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span> </span>Cng on lm tt cng tc nhn o t thin, hng nm u hng ng ng gp nhn o gip  ng bo gp kh khn, hon nn do cc t chc cng on, Hi ch thp  huyn pht ng. c bit phong tro "Nh gio H Ni  u cho hc sinh ngho, c hon cnh kh khn" c cc thy c gio quan tm ng h mang  ngha nhn o cao c, ngha c cao p, nhiu khi m thm lng l. Tiu biu nm hc 2010 -2011, c 38 hc sinh trng THPT C Loa c cc thy c gio  u vi s tin 11.600.000. Hot ng ny ca cng on nh trng  c Hi ch thp  huyn ng Anh v Cng on ngnh gio dc H Ni nh gi cao.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span> </span>Vi phng chm on kt l sc mnh, l yu t quyt nh s pht trin ca nh trng, cng on lun ch trng vic xy dng khi on kt, y cng l thnh tch ni tri v tr thnh truyn thng tt p. Ban chp hnh cng on lun tn trng, lng nghe tm t nguyn vng ca cng on vin, to c bu khng kh thc s phn khi, thn thin trong nh trng, ng vin mi ngi lm vic t gic, nng cao  thc, danh d ngh nghip. Mi thnh vin trong c quan sng vui v chn tnh, chia s, cm thng, thm hi gip  nhau khi gp kh khn...c bit, lun c tinh thn tng tr gip  nhau  cng nhau hon thnh nhim v. Cng on thc s l mi m, l gia nh ln em li nim tin, l ni chia<span> </span>ngt x bi ca mi cng on vin. C quan c np sng vn ho tt, tp th cng on l tp th m phm, khng c hin tng vi phm k lut, quy ch chuyn mn, k hoch ha gia nh, vi phm php lut.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span> </span>Nhng thnh tch  t c ca cng on trng THPT C Loa c cng on cp trn ghi nhn v nh gi cao, nhiu nm t danh hiu cng on vng mnh v vng mnh xut sc. c bit nm hc 2010  2011, cng on nh trng rt vinh d c Cng on gio dc Vit Nam tng bng khen " t thnh tch xut sc". y l b hoa ti thm, thit thc v nhiu  ngha hng ti k nim 45 nm ngy thnh lp trng. C c kt qu nh vy do Cng on lun nhn c s ch o su st ca Chi b, s phi hp cht ch, nhp nhng gia Ban chp hnh Cng on v Ban Gim hiu trong cc hot ng, ng thi nhn c s ng h ca cc t chc on th v s ng thun trong tp th cng on vin.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span> </span>Trong nim vui k nim ngy thnh lp trng, vi b dy truyn thng 45 nm xy dng v trng thnh, vi nim t ho l trng hc t chun Quc gia, t tiu chun cht lng gio dc cao, cn b- gio vin- nhn vin trng THPT C Loa tip tc on kt, st cnh bn nhau, thi ua lao ng sng to, phn u gi vng cc danh hiu  t c v tip tc xy dng nh trng ngy cng pht trin vng mnh ton din, l a ch  gio dc ca Huyn v Th .</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal"><span> </span>CH TCH CNG ON QUA CC THI K</p>\r\n<table class="MsoNormalTable" style="margin-left: 5.4pt; border-collapse: collapse; height: 161px; width: 521px;" border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 0; mso-yfti-firstrow: yes;">\r\n<td style="width: 81pt; border: 1pt solid black; background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #e0e0e0; padding: 0in 5.4pt;" width="108">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;" align="center"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">THI K</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 89.05pt; background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #e0e0e0; padding: 0in 5.4pt;" width="119">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;" align="center"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">CH TCH CNG ON</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 173.05pt; background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #e0e0e0; padding: 0in 5.4pt;" width="231">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;" align="center"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">THNH TCH</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 1;">\r\n<td style="width: 81pt; border-right: 1pt solid black; padding: 0in 5.4pt;" width="108">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;" align="center">....... --&gt; 1977</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 89.05pt;