(147, 'Chi u chi b nhim k 2010- 2015', 'chi-u-chi-b-nhim-k-2010-2015', '', '<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n<table style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><img src="data/giaoduc/Gioithieu/dsc_8123.jpg" alt="" height="340" width="511" /></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong><span style="color: #0000ff;">1- Bi th chi b: ng chi Ng c Nm ( gia) </span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="color: #0000ff;">2- Pho bi th chi b: ng chi L Thanh Tung</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="color: #0000ff;">3- Chi uy vin: ng chi  Thi inh</span></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="padding-left: 60px;">&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 0, 2, '2011-10-29 03:38:16', 62, '', '2012-04-10 11:42:24', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-29 03:37:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 19, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 293, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(146, 'Chi b ng  thc hin tt vai tr ht nhn lnh o nh trng t 1966 n nay', 'chi-b-ng-a-thc-hin-tt-vai-tro-ht-nhan-lanh-o-nha-trng-t-1966-n-nay', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: windowtext;">Chi b ng trng trung hc ph thng C Loa c thnh lp nm 1966 cng vi s ra i ca trng trung hc ph thng C Loa ( tin thn l trng cp 3 ng Anh A). Lch s 45 nm ca chi b gn b cht ch vi qu trnh xy dng v pht trin ca nh trng. Trong sut 45 nm qua, chi b ng thc s l ht nhn chnh tr, trc tip lnh o cc hot ng trong nh trng thc hin nhim v gio dc ton din, bi dng cc th h hc sinh trng thnh.</span></p>\r\n<p><img style="float: left;" src="data/giaoduc/Lanhdaotruong/thaynam.jpg" alt="" height="205" width="309" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: windowtext;">Nhng nm u thnh lp trng l khi c nc ang chm trong khi la bi cuc chin tranh ph hoi c lit ca gic M. S lng ng vin lc  khng nhiu, ch c 3 ng ch trn tng s 21 cn b, gio vin, nhn vin nh trng; nhim v ca chi b rt nng n,  l lnh o cng tc trng tm dy v hc trong iu kin c s vt cht v cng kh khn, thiu thn.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Trng ch c 7 lp hc, chia lm 3 ni: Xm Mt, Bi Miu, Mch Trng, phng hc tranh tre, l naTrong gian kh nhiu b ca chin tranh, chi b ng nh trng giai on 1966-1970 do ng ch Phan Th, sau  l ng ch Trn nh Duyt lm b th,  lun th hin ng vai tr lnh o trc tip, on kt, xy dng nh trng vt qua nhng kh khn, th thch ban u, n lc thi ua dy tt, hc tt.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: windowtext;">Giai on 1971-1975, giai on phi hc s tn do  quc M nm bom tr li min Bc vo gia nm 1972, chin tranh v cng khc lit; min Bc dc sc ngi v ca cho cuc khng chin chng M cu nc  min Nam. Thi k ny, di s lnh o ca chi b ng do cc ng ch Trng Kim Huy (1971-1972), Phan Thc Ti (1972-1973), Nguyn Th Y (1974-1975) lm b th,  gio dc, ng vin rt nhiu cn b, gio vin, hc sinh tham gia lc lng v trang, thanh nin xung phong chng M cu nc. Trong s nghip bo v t quc, nhiu th h thy tr ca trng  ln ng chin u: C nhiu ngi anh dng lp cng, c ngi hi sinh oanh lit v c ngi  li mt phn thn th ca mnh  chin trng; nhng con ngi dng cm y, gp phn mang n s bnh yn ca t nc. Danh hiu Trng tin tin chng M cu nc ( t 1966- 1975)  ghi nhn nhng ng gp ca nh trng trong cng cuc chng M cu nc.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: windowtext;">Giai on 1976-1991, t nc hon ton thng nht i ln xy dng ch ngha x hi. Chi b ng nh trng do cc ng ch Nguyn Th Y (1976-1977 v 1982-1988), ng ch Hong Cng K (1978-1981), ng ch Trn Ngc Kh (1989-1991) lm b th,  lnh o nh trng pht huy truyn thng cch mng, khc phc mi kh khn, y mnh phong tro thi ua: Thy n lc dy tt- Tr hng hi hc tt. Chi b  pht trin hn vi s lng ng vin l 11 ng ch.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: windowtext;">Giai on 1992-2004, t nc i vo thi k i mi cng nghip ho, hin i ho. Chi b ng trng trung hc ph thng C Loa cng tng bc i mi v pht trin. B th chi b l ng ch Ng B Dc,  lnh o cc hot ng ca nh trng: cng tc chuyn mn dy v hc, cng tc xy dng c s vt cht, cng tc pht tin cc t chc on th a trng tng bc i ln t trng tin tin nhiu nm.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: windowtext;">Giai on 2004 n nay, ngnh Gio dc nc nh trong thi k i mi chng trnh, sch gio khoa phn ban, i mi phng php ging dy, ng dng cng ngh thng tin trong qun l v dy hc. Chi b ng nh trng do cc ng ch T B Cnh (2004-2007, ng ch Nguyn Hu ng (2007-2008), ng ch Ng c Nm lm b th, lnh o nh trng thc hin ng li i mi Gio dc, ng thi tp trung lnh o nhim v trng tm c bn xuyn sut dy v hc; khng ngng nng cao cht lng gio dc ton din; gio dc chnh tr t tng cho cn b gio vin v hc sinh; thc hin tt cc cuc vn ng v cc phong tro ca ng, ca ngnh gio dc. Chi b i u trong vic trin khai cuc vn ng Hc tp v lm theo tm gng o c H Ch Minh, pht trin mnh phong tro thi ua Hai tt trn tinh thn Dy thc cht, hc thc cht, kim tra thc cht v cht lng thc cht, trin khai phong tro Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc. Thm nhun t tng H Ch Minh v chm lo bi dng th h cch mng cho i sau, chi b  lm tt cng tc to ngun v kt np ng vin, t nm 2004 n nm 2010, chi y phn cng cc ng vin bi dng du dt qun chng u t v  kt np thm ng vin mi. Tnh n nay, chi b c 23 ng vin, chim t l 23%; cc t chuyn mn u c ng vin nn pht huy c vai tr, trch nhim tng ng vin trong vic nng cao cht lng dy hc ca nh trng.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: windowtext;">Chi b ng nh trng ngy cng pht trin vng mnh, xng ng l ht nhn on kt, lnh o nh trng thc hin tt cc ch trng chnh sch ca ng, php lut ca nh nc, hon thnh xut sc nhim v chnh tr, t nhiu thnh tch ni bt. Nh trng lin tc t danh hiu trng tin tin v tin tin xut sc, nm hc 2007-2008 c cng nhn l n v l c u thi ua thnh ph H Ni; nm 2009, trng vinh d c UBND thnh ph H Ni trao <strong><em>Bng cng nhn trng THPT t chun quc gia</em></strong> giai on 2001-2010. Trong nhiu nm, chi b t danh hiu Chi b trong sch vng mnh; cc on th, t chc x hi trong trng di s lnh o ca chi b tr thnh nhng on th xut sc c cc cp qun l huyn v thnh ph khen thng.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: windowtext;">Chi b ng trng trung hc ph thng C Loa  tri qua khng t nhng gian nan, th thch nhng cng y thnh tch ng trn trng v t ho. Pht huy truyn thng tt p v nhng thnh qu t c ca 45 nm qua, ton th cn b ng vin trong chi b on kt mt lng, quyt tm thc hin thng li ngh quyt i hi chi b nhim k 2010-2015; khng ngng nng cao cht lng dy v hc, p ng yu cu o to nhn lc cho s nghip cng nghip ho, hin i ho t nc v hi nhp quc t; c gng, quyt tm gi vng nhng danh hiu cao qu; ra sc phn u a nh trng tip tc pht trin v nhn c phn thng cao qu ca ng v Nh nc.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: justify;" align="right"><span style="color: windowtext;">B th chi b&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br /> Ths.<strong>Ng c Nm</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal" align="right">&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 0, 2, '2011-10-29 03:22:20', 62, '', '2012-04-10 12:29:03', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-29 03:20:32', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 10, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 202, 'robots=\nauthor='),
