(137, 'N r lp h  nng im cho sinh vin', 'n-r-lp-he--nang-im-cho-sinh-vien', '', '<p><strong>(GDVN) - Hc ci thin trong h  th thy gio s d hn, s khng im danh nhiu nh hc trong nm v  quan trng l im cng c phn thong hn. Kiu Trang - sinh vin i  hc Khoa hc T nhin, H Ni chia s vi chng ti.<br /> </strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em>LTS: Thay v c mt k ngh h vui  v, thoi mi, nhiu sinh vin ca mt s trng i hc  chn cch  ngh h cng nhng lp hc ci thin vi tin hc ph cao ngt tri.  Liu nhng lp hc ny c ci thin v bi p thm kin thc ca cc  sinh vin hay khng? Hay ch n gin l ci thin im? Cht lng ca  nhng lp hc ny n u?</em><br /> <br /> <strong>Lp hc ng gp 2  3 ln lp trong nm</strong><br /> <br /> Vo nhng ngy h ny, gh thm cc lp hc ci thin ca mt s trng  i hc c t chc, mi thy c khng kh hc ci thin im trong t  h ca cc sinh vin si ni khng km g trong k hc chnh kha.</p>\r\n<table class="MsoNormalTable" style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #fde9d9; border-collapse: collapse; border: medium none; margin-left: 6.75pt; margin-right: 6.75pt;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style="height: 134.2pt;">\r\n<td style="width: 168.35pt; border: 1pt solid #0070c0; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 134.2pt; text-align: justify;" width="224" valign="top">\r\n<p>Hnh thc ci thin im l sn phm ca h o to tn  ch - mt  hnh thc o to mi m ang c nhiu trng i hc p  dng trong  nhng nm gn y.</p>\r\n<p>Lp hc ci thin im (hay cn gi l lp nng im)   c m ra cho nhng sinh vin c im tng kt mn hc no im D (va    im qua mn hc) trong k hc chnh kha, mun hc  ci thin con   im  ca mnh.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"> c mt sut hc ci  thin v mn hc no , sinh vin phi mn mi  ch nh trng m  lp, ri phi nhanh chn ln tn phng o to ca  nh trng  ng  k. <br /> <br /> Thu Trang  sinh vin K54 khoa Ton, trng H Khoa hc T nhin n n   ci vui sng cho bit, c  hon thnh xong th tc ng k lp hc   ci thin. Mn ny k trc em b im D ln ny may m ng k c   vo lp ny, hi vng s c im B  g gc li, nu khng nhanh chn   l li phi ch n h nm sau mi hc c. <br /> <br /> Bn Q.Ch, hc cng lp vi Trang cho hay, mn tin hc ny, gn nh c   lp em i hc ci thin im. Trng c 2 lp Ton, gn nh sinh vin   c 2 lp u i hc ci thin mn tin, m lp tin th trong h ch t   chc c 1 lp, thnh th, hai lp ghp mt nn rt ng.<br /> <br /> Theo tm hiu, phng vin c bit, kt qu hc ci thin mn s c   thay vo kt qu ca mn  trong hc k chnh thc trc . V th,   cn phi xem mt gi vng, nu thy gio ca mn ny kh th hc ci   thin ch tn tin, ch c tc dng g.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;">K ngh h ny, Tun   sinh vin nm 4 i hc Kin trc (H Ni)   li ngh h cng 3  mn hc ci thin vi tng s tn ch l 8. Tun chia s vi ti: Sinh  vin trng em chc khng c khi nim ngh h na, chng n hc h m  ng vui, nhn nhp chng km g hc chnh c. Lp Vt L em ang theo  hc y cht cng,  cc la sinh vin t nm th 2 cho ti nm th 4.  <br /> <br /> Khi c hi v mc ch ca vic hc ci thin, Tun  chng ngi ngn  g m tuyn b: Quan trng l mnh ra trng c tm bng p mt cht  th ngi ta mi nhn vo lm ch nu khng th em cng chng i hc  lm g cho mt ngi.  trn H Ni ny ngt ngi, kh chu lm, v qu  c ngh ngi c phi l thch hn khng.<strong><br /> </strong></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<table border="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://giaoduc.net.vn/images/stories/2011/07/27/cai%20thien%202.jpg" border="0" alt="Mt lp hc ci thin im cht cng. nh chp ti trng i hc Khoa hc T nhin sng th 2 ngy 18/7." width="470" align="middle" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: center;">Mt lp hc ci thin im cht cng. nh chp ti <br /> trng i hc Khoa hc T nhin sng th 2 ngy 18/7</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Thy cha nhn lp v bn i du lch </strong><br /> <br /> Mc d c nhiu trng m lp hc ci thin song song vi k hc chnh   trong nm nhng a phn sinh vin khng thch ng k nhng lp c t   chc nh th. Bi l hc trong h th thy gio s d hn, s khng   im danh nhiu nh hc trong nm v quan trng l im cng c phn   thong hn i cht. Xun T.  sinh vin khoa Ton trng i hc Khoa   hc T nhin xi li chia s vi ti. <br /> <br /> Phng vin  tham gia mt bui hc cng T. vo mt bui sng th 2 mi.   8 gi vo hc m c nng cng vi bn mnh lang thang n sng, ung   nc v ngi tn pht vi nhau ti gn 9 gi mi vo. <br /> <br /> Mn ny hc 4 tit, phng hc li b na nn vo sm th ch c ngi m   th thi anh . T. gii p thc mc ca ti vi v bnh thn. <br /> <br /> Ngang nhin vo cng trc ca lp hc (v cng sau ngi ta khng m),   sau mt ting cho cho c l l T. v bn ca mnh  kim c mt  v  tr  cui lp. Trn bc, thy c ging.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;">Nhng tng T. v bn  mnh  l nhng ngi vo mun nht ri nhng sau  , c khong vi  pht li c ting xin php thy cho vo lp. Khng  nhng th, nhiu  sinh vin chm ch ti sm t u bui, ngi ti gi   khng chu c  nhit na nh xch cp ra v. <br /> <br /> Lp hc c v nhn nhp v bt nhm chn hn. Trn bc, thy vn c ging. <br /> <br /> Tham gia mt lp hc khc ca trng i hc Kin Trc H Ni vo bui   sng th 4, bn cht ca s vic cng khng c cht thay i. <br /> <br /> Lch 7 gi vo hc, 7 gi 30 vn cha thy c gio ti. Sinh vin ht   ln ra hnh lang li ln vo lp. Nhiu ting bn tn v s chm tr   ca c gio  vang ln v tr thnh  ti si ni cho sinh vin lp   hc ny.</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<table border="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://giaoduc.net.vn/images/stories/2011/07/27/cai%20thien%201.jpg" border="0" alt="Tranh th chp mt  trong thi gian ch ging vin ti. nh chp ti i hc Kin trc H Ni sng th 4 ngy 20/7." width="470" align="middle" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: center;">Tranh th chp mt  trong thi gian ch ging vin ti. nh chp ti<br /> i hc Kin trc HN sng th 4 ngy 20/7.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Lp hc bn cnh cng  khng km phn hp dn. Nhiu sinh vin trong khi ch ging vin ti   tranh th chp mt mt cht v m qua tao vi thng bn chm dn  (game  ch) ti mi 3 gi sng mi ng. <br /> <br /> Vi pht sau, ting thng bo c gio n dng nh  khuy ng tt  c. Bc vo lp hc, khng mt li gii thch, thn nhin t cp sch  ln bn, ging vin ni: chng ta tip tc chng trnh hm trc,   ri pha di lp c ting lm bm: Sao c li ti vo lc ny, ph c  gic m p ca em.<br /> <br /> Lp hc cht cng vi gn 100 sinh vin, chc chc li thu np thm  mt vi ngi ti tr. Trn bc c vn ging bi, ting c ha ln vi  ting qut trn v v trn u v ting cht cha ca khoan, ct, c,  o ca ta nh m nh trng ang xy d bn cnh. <br /> <br /> C gio ti dy l may cho mnh ri nn phi c cng tai ra m nghe  thi anh .  lp Ton cao cp, l ra bn em phi hc c 3 bui ri  nhng thy gio cha ti nhn lp na kia. Nghe bo thy gio i du lch  th phi. <br /><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>(GDVN)</strong></p>', '', -2, 17, 0, 222, '2011-10-22 10:46:23', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 10:44:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 1, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 16, '');
