hi gian. Las Vegas thu ht 35 triu khch du lch  mi nm ti tham quan, mua sm ti cc khu gii tr hng sang, nh hng,  siu th ln, vi hn 125.000 phng khch sn cao cp.</p>\r\n<p> l nhng l do gip Las Vegas ng u nc M v tc  pht trin ngh nghip c bit l du lch v qun l khch sn.<br /><br />CSN  hin c hn 43.000 sinh vin, trong  c hn 700 sinh vin quc t n  t hn 60 quc gia. C s vt cht ca trng hin i v tin li bao  gm phng hc, phng th nghim, th vin, hn 50 cu lc b v t chc  sinh vin ti 3 khu hc x v 11 trung tm o to.</p>\r\n<p>Chng trnh o to ca trng phong ph v a dng vi hn 200  chng trnh o to ngh v hn 80 chng trnh cp bng Cao ng v  Chuyn tip i hc, hc 2 nm cui ti cc trng i hc trn ton  nc M. Hc ph: 9.000$/nm<br /><br />Sinh vin sau khi tt nghip c c  hi thc tp hng lng trong thi gian hc v sau khi tt nghip. Las  Vegas l a im du lch ni ting th gii, sinh vin c th tn dng  c hi ng dng Bng cp v kh nng song ng ca mnh.</p>\r\n<p>Lin h: Ti H Ni: 230 Kim M, Qun Ba nh. T: 04 3726 1938; <br />E-mail: viscohanoi@visco.edu.vn <br /><br />Tp. HCM: 239 Cch Mng Thng 8, Nh A02 Chung c Vn ha P.4, Q.3. <br />T: 08 3832 8416; E-mail: viscohcm@visco.edu.vn <br /><br />Ti  Nng: 433 Phan Chu Trinh, Q.Hi Chu. T: 0511 3552596/97; E-mail: viscodn@visco.edu.vn <br /><br />Ti Hi Phng: 309 Hai B Trng, Ct di, Q. L Chn. T: 031 3950215; Email: viscohp@visco.edu.vn</p>\r\n<p>(GDVN)</p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>{tab=Tiu  2 - Alo alo alo}</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>Hc bng 1.000$ cho sinh vin np h s ng k nhp hc.</p>\r\n<p>Gim c tuyn sinh quc t ca Trng ph thng ni tr Southwestern  Academy (bang California v Arizona) v Trng Cao ng Southern Nevada  (Las Vegas) - b Lynn Yekiazarian v ng Naus Scott s c chui hi  tho phng vn tuyn sinh ti H Ni, Tp. H Ch Minh v  Nng. Hc  bng 1.000$ cho sinh vin np h s ng k nhp hc.</p>\r\n<hr id="system-readmore" />\r\n<p>Thi gian v a im nh sau:</p>\r\n<p>H Ni: 17h00 Ch Nht ngy 18/9/2011<br />Hotel de l''Opera Hanoi, 29 Trng Tin<br /><br />HCM: 17h30 Th Hai ngy 19/9/2011<br />Khc