(127, '''Bi lun ca HS Vit Nam thng c cht lng cao''', 'bai-lun-ca-hs-vit-nam-thng-co-cht-lng-cao', '', '<p>"TP tuyt vi c xy dng trn nhiu yu t. Ln  k hoch  TP c th sng c cho gia nh v c nhn phi i  mt vi nhiu thch thc mi".</p>\r\n<div class="body">\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">- i din Trinity College chia s vi ''Nh lnh o tr 2011''.</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">IDP Education Vit Nam  nhn c  rt nhiu bi vit tham d cuc thi Hc bng Nh Lnh o tr 2011.  Hc sinh rt quan tm n cch nh gi cht lng ca bi lun v  nhng tiu chun c th m ban gim kho ch  khi chm im.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Sau y l cuc tr chuyn vi hai i din Trinity College/ the University of Melbourne:</p>\r\n<table style="height: 359px;" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" width="309" align="left">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="background-color: #cccccc;">\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Tin s Tamar n TCFC vo nm 1992 sau khi hon thnh  hc v tin s ti trng i hc London v c thi gian ging dy mn  lch s  i hc Melbourne.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Nghin cu ca b tp trung  vo s thay i kinh t v vn ha, c gii thiu trong quyn  sch Bit th, nng tri, v nn kinh t nng thn Roman (t th k  th 3 n th k th 5 Sau Cng Nguyn) (Oxford 1991/2004). Quyn  sch ny  nhn c s cng nhn ca quc t v c trch dn  trong hn 100 n phm hc thut trn ton th gii. Cc n phm  khc ca b bao gm Gio dc trong mt ngi lng ton cu: Thch  thc a vn ha B-HERT Tp ch Bn trn Kinh Doanh/Gio dc thng  11/2003.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Nm 2009, b c bnh chn  l Nghin cu sinh th 50 ca c trong Hi Kho c hc London  Hip  hi v kho c v lch s c thnh lp vo nm 1707 vi gn 2500  hi vin quc t. B cng l Nghin cu sinh Danh d ca Khoa Lch s  thuc i Hc Melbourne.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Hin ti, b cng vi nhm  cc ng nghip n t trng i hc Quc Gia c tham gia mt d  n quc t v  vinh d nhn c mt trong 150 Gii thng do Hi  ng Nghin Cu Khm ph c trao tng trong lnh vc Khoa hc Nhn vn  v Sng to Ngh thut nm 2010.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Ngoi cng vic nghin cu,  b Tamar rt thch c tiu thuyt trinh thm v i du lch n cc  b bin Chu u v chu  vo nhng ngy ngh  c cng vi gia nh  (chng b Tamar hin ang lm vic ti trng i hc Monash)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Tin s Tamar LEWIT - Trng  b mn Lch s cc  tng v l Gim c d n hc thut chuyn  ngnh ca Trinity College:- Tin s Tamar LEWIT - Trng b mn Lch  s cc  tng v l Gim c d n hc thut chuyn ngnh ca Trinity  College:</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em>- Ch  nm nay l v mt thnh ph l tng, b c th gii thch l do ti sao li chn ch  ny?</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">- Mt thnh ph tuyt vi c xy  dng trn nhiu yu t. Thnh ph  th k 21 m chng ta ang  sng c s thay i so vi 100 hoc thm ch 50 nm trc, do vy,  vic ln k hoch  thnh ph tr thnh mt ni c th sng  c cho gia nh v c nhn ang phi i mt vi nhiu thch thc  mi.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Hc sinh, sinh vin sp tt nghip  Trung hc v i hc trong nhng nm ti s lm vic trn nhiu lnh  vc v h l ngi c nh hng trc tip n din mo ca cc thnh  ph m chng ta sng trong tng lai.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em>- B mong i iu g t bi vit ca cc hc sinh Vit Nam?</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">- Theo kinh nghim t chc cc cuc  thi vit lun  Vit Nam (cng nh nhng quc gia khc) trc y,  cht lng bi vit ca hc sinh Vit Nam thng t tiu chun rt  cao. Nhng bi vit ca th sinh ot gii trong cc k thi trc c  trau chut rt k lng vi  kin c o v c din t r  rng. C nhiu bi vit rt n tng.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">-<em> Theo  kin ca b, tiu chun cho mt bi vit c cht lng l g?</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">-  quyt nh bi vit thng cuc,  chng ti thng cn c vo nhng yu t sau y: s c o trong  suy ngh hoc  tng, s dng tt Ting Anh, bao gm chnh t v ng  php, kh nng lp lun, pht trin cc  chnh hoc ch  ca bi  lun, b cc bi vit cht ch. Chng ti tm kim nhng th sinh  c th hon thnh nhim v l i din xut sc ca Vit Nam ti  Chng trnh Du hc H Nh Lnh o tr  Trng Cao ng Trinity.</p>\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" width="200" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://giaoduc.net.vn/Uploaded/haiyen/2011_10_11/t682345.jpg" border="0" alt="Bi lun ca HS Vit Nam thng c cht lng cao" width="400" height="513" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid;" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<p><strong>Tin s Tamar LEWIT</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em>- Khi chm im cho cc bi vit ca sinh vin, b ch  vo nhng yu t no?</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">-  tng c o v lp lun vng  chc lm nn mt bi lun thng gii. Tt nhin vi iu kin tip  cn Internet d dng nh hin nay, c th mt s bn cho rng sao  chp ti liu t nhiu website khc nhau s khin cho bi vit tr  nn li cun hn. Tuy nhin, khng kh  cc gio s dy dn kinh  nghim ca chng ti pht hin bi lun o vn. Bi lun thng gii  t nhng nm trc y u th hin c gc nhn c nhn ni bt  chim s ch  t ban gim kho ngay t phn gii thiu. Bi lun  rt cn c mt cu trc tt.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em>- S sng to v tm nhn l 2 k  nng quan trng ca mt nh lnh o, vy nhng yu t ny c c  th hin r trong bi lun ca cc th sinh?</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">- Chc chn ri, r rng l c mt s  nh lnh o thin bm v nhng nh t tng sng to  cc trng hc  trn khp Vit Nam.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em>- Nhng cu tr li ca th sinh c  p ng c mong i ca b khng v b c bao gi ngc nhin trc s  sng to trong bi vit ca cc th sinh?</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">- Vng, iu ny l chc chn, ti ngh  nm nay cc bi lun u rt tt, v cng vic nh gi tht s  kh cho cc hc gi ca chng ti. T nhng  tng biu l c xt  on v d nh c phng tin giao thng cng cng tt v cn nhc  cc yu t mi trng, cho ti nhng  tng c o nh s dng tu  ln siu tc lm phng tin i li cho thnh ph hin i trong  tng lai.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>ng Ben Waymire  Gim c tuyn sinh cao cp Trinity College:</strong></p>\r\n<table style="width: 300px;" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" align="left">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="background-color: #cccccc;">\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">ng Ben Waymire tt nghip  chuyn ngnh Tm l hc v c mi nm kinh nghim lm vic v cc vn   tr em trc khi gia nhp Trinity College vo nm 2005.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">T  n nay, ng  tham  gia pht trin cc chin lc tuyn sinh cho mt lot cc quc gia  khc nhau bao gm: Indonesia, Hn Quc, Nga, Chu Phi, Trung ng,  Thi Lan va Vit Nam.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">ng c mt cuc sng th  v v bn rn vi hai con nh  thnh ph Melbourne. Ben cng rt  hng th vi vic du lch n nhng quc gia khc nhau, v c bit  thch tham quan v nghin cu v Vit nam. ng yu thch m thc Vit  Nam v cc k thch mn Bn B Hu.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">-<em> Hc bng Nh lnh o tr l  chng trnh thng nin Trinity, The Univeiisty of Melbourne v IDP  Education Vit Nam t chc cho cc hc sinh Vit Nam. ng c th cho  bit mc ch ca vic t chc hnh thc hc bng ny l g?</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">- The University of Melbourne l trng  i hc S 1 ti c (Theo xp hng ca Shanghai Jiao Tong 2011 v the  Times Higher Education 2011) v xp th 4 trn th gii v cht  lng u ra ca trng (Theo xp hng ca the Times Higher Education  v Bc o to Sau Trung hc 2011). c cng nhn l mt trong  nhng im n l tng nht th gii  hc tp, tuy nhin khng  phi ai cng c th c nhn vo hc ti y. <br /> <br /> Do , mt trong nhng l cho chnh cho vic t chc cuc thi vit  lun l em n mt c hi cho cc sinh vin t thnh tch cao  (nhng bn khng th hoc khng c c hi theo hc ti trng chng  ti) c th tham d mt kha hc hng th v th thch trong thi gian  2 tun ti khu hc x ca Trinity College v the University of  Melbourne. Chng trnh Nh Lnh o Tr mang cc sinh vin xut sc  trn ton th gii li vi nhau  cc bn chia s cc  kin, suy  ngh v tnh hu ngh ti khu hc x xinh p ny.</p>\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" width="200" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://giaoduc.net.vn/Uploaded/haiyen/2011_10_11/t682350.jpg" border="0" alt="Bi lun ca HS Vit Nam thng c cht lng cao" width="400" height="301" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid;" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>ng Ben Waymire</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em>- Kha hc Nh Lnh o Tr cung cp nhng kin thc, k nng v kinh nghim g cho hc sinh, tha ng?</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">- Chng trnh Nh Lnh o Tr hng  ti mc tiu truyn t cm hng cho cc hc sinh c thnh tch cao  thng qua cc chng trnh hi tho gip khi dy tinh thn hc tp.  Cc th sinh tham d chng trnh s c c hi tng tc vi nhng  ngi c ti tr hng u trn nhiu lnh vc khc nhau bao gm Khoa  hc, Tm l hc, cc lut s hng u, cc nh hot ng nhn quyn  v nhng ngi ot gii Nobel. <br /> <br /> Chng ti c mc tiu pht trin t duy phn bin trong hc tp bng  cch truyn cm hng cho cc em tip tc pht trin v lm nn nhng  iu v i sau nhng nm hc Ph thng. Chng ti nhn thy cc th  sinh sau khi hc xong chng trnh ny trong nhiu nm qua c tm  nhn mi v ngun nng lng khi h chuyn ln cc bc o to Sau  Trung hc.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em>- ng  pht hin ra hc sinh no n t Vit Nam c y  phm cht ca mt nh lnh o cha?</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">- Vng, tt nhin l c rt nhiu!  Ti Trng Cao ng Trinity v i hc Melbourne, c l iu kh khn  nht cho chng ti l xc nh th sinh thng cuc bi v chng ti c  th d dng chn ra hng trm ng vin sng gi hoc thm ch nhiu  hn na  tuy nhin, rt tic s lng gii trong nm nay li c  hn.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>(GDVN)</strong></p>\r\n</div>', '', -2, 14, 0, 155, '2011-10-22 08:46:28', 62, '', '2011-10-24 16:56:16', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 08:46:28', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 6, 0, 4, '', '', 0, 8, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(125, 'Hc bng 100% ca trng H Queen''s Belfast (Anh)', 'hc-bng-100-ca-trng-h-queens-belfast-anh', '', '<p>(GDVN) -Trng INTO QUEEN''S BELFAST V H QUEEN''S BELFAST ang ginh cc sut hc bng hp dn t 10-100 % hc ph.<br /><br />Chng trnh D b i hc: Hc bng 10-100% hc ph . Chng trnh d b i hc chun b cho sinh vin vo nm th nht vi nhiu chuyn ngnh ti i hc Queens Belfast.<br /><br />Trong lnh vc Kinh doanh, Qun tr c:<br /><br />Ngnh K ton: Khi tt nghip chuyn ngnh k ton ti i hc Queens Belfast, sinh vin s c min thi 9 mn trong k thi ly chng ch ACCA. Trng ng th 20  UK v ngnh K Ton (Theo t the Times and University Guide 2010 v 2011).<br />Nghin cu Ri ro, thng k: Sinh vin hc chuyn ngnh ny ti Queens Belfast s c min thi 8 trn 9 mn  s mn thi ti a trong k thi chuyn mn CT ti bt c trng i hc no ti UK.<br />Ti chnh: Sinh vin hc chuyn ngnh ny s c 1 nm thc tp . Trng ng th 20 ti UK v ngnh Ti chnh.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>Trong lnh vc Khoa hc v K s c cc chuyn ngnh sau:<br /><br />Kin trc: tng ng RIBA phn 1 v xp hng th 10 trn ton vng quc Anh.<br /><br />Khoa hc my tnh: Sinh vin hc chuyn ngnh ny s c 1 nm thc tp<br /><br />K s: hng khng, ha, dn dng, in, v c<br /><br />iu kin t hc bng:<br /><br />in n nhp hc, n xin hc bng, np bng im v chng ch ting Anh<br /><br />Bi lun ti a 400 t<br /><br />Chng trnh Diploma: hc bng 10-30% hc ph.<br /><br />Chng trnh Diploma tng ng nm th nht i hc sau khi hon thnh s vo thng nm th hai.<br /><br />Trong lnh vc Kinh doanh, qun tr:<br /><br />Ngnh ti chnh: Sinh vin hc chuyn ngnh ny s c 1 nm thc tp. Trng ng th 20 ti UK v ngnh ti chnh..<br /><br />Ngnh kinh t: Sinh vin hc chuyn ngnh ny s c 1 nm thc tp.<br /><br />Trong lnh vc K s c cc chuyn ngnh sau:<br /><br />K s hng khng: Sinh vin hc chuyn ngnh ny s c 1 nm thc tp. Trng ng th 15 ti UK.<br /><br />K s in: Sinh vin hc chuyn ngnh ny s c 1 nm thc tp. Trng ng th 10 ti UK chuyn ngnh ny.<br /><br />K s c kh: Sinh vin hc chuyn ngnh ny s c 1 nm thc tp. Trng ng th 15 ti UK.<br /><br />Yu cu xin hc bng:<br /><br />in n nhp hc, on xin hc bng, np bng im v chng ch ting Anh<br /><br />Bi lun ti a 400 t<br /><br />Chng trnh D b thc s:<br /><br />Chng trnh d b thc s trao 5 hc bng 100% tr gi 11,490 bng cho chuyn ngnh Qun tr v Ti chnh, khai ging thng 01/2012 c yu cu nh sau:<br /><br />IELTS ti thiu 5.5 (khng k nng no di 5.0)<br /><br />in n nhp hc, np bng im v chng ch ting Anh<br /><br />n xin hc bng v bi lun (ti thiu 200 t v ti a l 500 t)<br /><br />Hc bng s c trao thnh hai t: 5, 745 bng cho kha kha d b thc s v 5, 745 bng khi vo hc kha thc s ti trng Queens Belfast.<br /><br />Hn cht ng k h s xin hc bng cho c 3 chng trnh: ngy 18/11/2011<br /><br />Lin h: Cng ty t vn gio dc TEC.<br /><br />T: (04) 37664523 / 53. Fax: (04) 37622481 Email: info@tec.edu.vn<br />( GLN Center)</p>\r\n<p></p>', -2, 13, 0, 227, '2011-10-22 08:40:49', 62, '', '2011-10-25 02:35:50', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 08:40:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 26, 0, 15, '', '', 0, 58, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(124, 'Hi tho hc bng ti i hc Queen''s, Belfast, Anh', 'hi-tho-hc-bng-ti-i-hc-queens-belfast-anh', '', '<div style="text-align: justify;">(GDVN) - i hc  Queens Belfast l mt trong 20 trng i hc hng u trong lnh vc  o to v nghin cu ca Vng Quc Anh.</div>\r\n<div id="ctl00_PrimaryContent_ctl00_divRelatedContents">\r\n<ul class="article-link">\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Trng ang c chng trnh hc bng  tr gi ti 100% hc ph cho kha D b i hc, D b Thc s, 30% hc  ph cho kha International Diploma (tng ng nm I i hc) v nhiu  sut hc bng t 2.000  4.000 cho kha Thc s chuyn ngnh Kinh  doanh, Khoa hc x hi v K thut khai ging thng 1 v 9/2012.<br /> <br /> i vi nhng sinh vin mong mun nng cao trnh  ting Anh trc khi  vo hc C nhn, Thc s, i hc Queens Belfast phi hp cng trung  tm INTO cung cp cc kha hc ting Anh, D b i hc, Nm I i hc,  D b Thc s vi thi gian khai ging linh hot, hc bng hp dn. <br /> <br /> ng Simon Illey, i din tuyn sinh ca i hc Queens Belfast s c  bui ni chuyn gii thiu v trng, chng trnh hc, c hi hc bng  ca trng theo lch c th:<br /> <br /> TP. H CH MINH. Thi gian: 17h30 th Hai, 24/10/2011. a im: VISCO,  239 Cch mng thng 8, nh A2, chung c Vn ha, P.4, Q.3 <br /> <br /> H NI. Thi gian: 17h30 th T, 26/10/2011. a im: VISCO, 230 Kim M, Ba nh<br /> <br /> * n d hi tho, sinh vin em theo bn photo kt qu hc tp mi nht  c t vn c th.<br /> <br /> c thnh lp nm 1845, n nay Queens Belfast c hn 17.000 sinh vin  n t 80 quc gia trn th gii. i hc Queens Belfast l thnh vin  ca t chc danh ting Russell Group gm 20 trng i hc hng u  trong lnh vc o to v nghin cu, trong  c i hc Cambridge v  Oxford.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<table class="picBox" border="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://giaoduc.net.vn/Uploaded/haiyen/2011_10_20/QUB.jpg" border="0" width="475" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Trng c trang b hin i vi h thng thng tin th vin c u  t hn 45 triu bng Anh, h thng my tnh kt ni Internet phc v cho  vic hc tp ca sinh vin. Hng nm, trng u c ngn sch  u t  tu b li cc trang thit b phc v hot ng th thao, gii tr, vn  ha cho sinh vin.<br /> <br /> c bnh chn l 1 trong nhng trng i hc hng u th gii trong  lnh vc nghin cu theo nh gi ca UK Research Assessment Exercise  2008, Queens Belfast em n cho sinh vin mi trng hc tp hon ho,  pht huy ti a kh nng sng to, nghin cu ca sinh vin. <br /> <br /> Theo bnh chn ca Times Good University Guide 2011, i hc Queens  Belfast nm trong nhm 20 trng i hc hng u Vng quc Anh c th  mnh  19 chuyn ngnh, trong  chuyn ngnh Dc, Nha khoa, Ti chnh,  in & in t ca trng xp trong nhm 10 trng hng u ton  Vng quc Anh. Chng trnh o to ca trng rt a dng vi nhiu  chuyn ngnh o to th mnh: Y, Dc, Kinh doanh, Ti chnh, K ton,  Lut, Gio dc, Nng nghipv mc hc ph va phi. <br /> <br /> Hc bng: i hc Queens Belfast trao tng cc sut hc bng tr gi  ti 100% hc ph cho kha D b i hc, D b Thc s, 30% hc ph cho  kha International Diploma (tng ng nm I i hc) v nhiu sut hc  bng 2.000 - 4.000 cho kha Thc s chuyn ngnh Kinh doanh, Khoa hc  x hi v K thut khai ging thng 1 v 9/2012.<br /> <br /> Chi tit xin vui lng lin h VISCO<br /> <br /> Ti H Ni: 230 Kim M, Ba nh<br /> <br /> T: 04.3726 1938; Fax: 04.3726 1936; E-mail: viscohanoi@visco.edu.vn<br /> <br /> Ti TP H Ch Minh: 239 Cch Mng Thng 8, Nh A2, Chung c vn ho, P.4, Q.3 <br /> <br /> T: 08 3832 8416; Fax: 08 3832 8417; E-mail: viscohcm@visco.edu.vn<br /> <br /> Ti  Nng: 433 Phan Chu Trinh, Hi Chu<br /> <br /> T: 0511.3552 596/97; Fax: 0511.3552 597; Email: viscodn@visco.edu.vn<br /> <br /> Ti Hi phng: 309 Hai B Trng, Phng Ct di, L Chn<br /> <br /> T: 0313 950 748; Fax: 0313 950 215; Email: viscohp@visco.edu.vn</p>', '', -2, 13, 0, 227, '2011-10-22 08:39:56', 62, '', '2011-10-24 17:02:38', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 08:39:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 4, 