(123, 'Hc bng 100% hc ph ti Into Uea', 'hc-bng-100-hc-phi-ti-into-uea', '', '<div style="text-align: right;">(GDVN) - NTO UEA  thng bo dnh 2 sut hc bng 100% Hc ph, tr gi 11,490 Bng/ sut.  Hc bng c p dng cho kha hc thng 02/2012.</div>\r\n<div class="body">\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">Hc bng c p dng cho cc chng trnh sau:<br /> <br /> 1. Hc bng Kha hc D b Ngnh Ngh Thut v Nhn vn: p dng  cho hc sinh ng k nhp hc vo cc chng trnh d b sau ti trng  i hc East Anglia <br /> <br /> - Chuyn ngnh Kinh doanh v Kinh t vi X hi v Vn ha, <br /> <br /> - Chuyn ngnh Nhn Vn v Lut <br /> <br /> 2. Hc bng D b Khoa hc: p dng cho hc sinh ng k nhp hc vo nhng kha hc sau ti trng i hc East Anglia: <br /> <br />  D b chuyn ngnh Khoa hc tng qut <br /> <br />  D b chuyn ngnh Dc, Sinh ha v Y t <br /> <br />  D b chuyn ngnn Vt l v Ton hc <br /> <br />  D b chuyn ngnh Ton hc v Thm nh gi <br />\r\n<p></p>\r\n<table class="picBox" border="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://giaoduc.net.vn/Uploaded/haiyen/2011_10_19/Nhom%201_2.JPG" border="0" width="475" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\niu kin d thi hc bng: <br /> <br /> - Tt nghip lp 12 loi Kh/Gii <br /> <br /> - IELTS tng ng 6.0, ti thiu 5.5 tng k nng. <br /> <br /> - n ng k nhp hc ca INTO UEA. <br /> <br /> - n ng k d thi hc bng ca UEA. <br /> <br /> - Bi vit ti a 200 t th hin bn thn v l do chn UEA cng nh li ch ca kha hc s mang li. <br /> <br /> Hn cht np n xin hc bng l ngy 18/11/2011 <br /> <br /> LIN H: CNG TY T VN GIO DC TEC<br /> <br /> T: (04) 37664523 / 53. Fax: (04) 37622481. Email: info@tec.edu.vn</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="author">( GLN Center)</div>', '', -2, 13, 0, 227, '2011-10-22 08:37:20', 62, '', '2011-10-24 16:57:45', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-24 08:37:00', '2011-10-24 16:37:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_pr