(122, 'Khng tuyn sinh ba nm s b nh ch', 'khong-tuyn-sinh-ba-nm-s-b-inh-ch', '', '<div class="sapo">\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">Trng cng s phi gii th nu ht thi hn nh ch hot ng o to vn khng khc phc c nguyn nhn b nh ch.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="body">\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"> l quy nh mi ti thng t sa  i, b sung mt s iu ca thng t 14 (ban hnh iu l trng cao  ng) v quyt nh 06 (quy nh o to lin thng trnh  cao ng,  i hc) va c B GD-T ban hnh.<br /> <br /> Theo , trng cao ng s b nh ch hot ng o to nu sau ba nm  k t khi c cho php hot ng o to, nh trng khng tuyn sinh  v t chc o to; c hnh vi gian ln  c cho php hot ng o  to; ngi cho php hot ng o to khng ng thm quyn; vi phm quy  nh ca php lut v gio dc, b x pht vi phm hnh chnh  mc   nh ch.<br />\r\n<p></p>\r\n<table class="picBox" border="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://giaoduc.net.vn/Uploaded/haiyen/2011_10_09/pho%20thong%20chuyen%20ngu%20by%20buituan.jpg" border="0" width="475" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nTrng cng s phi gii th nu ht thi hn nh ch hot ng o to vn khng khc phc c nguyn nhn b nh ch.<br /> <br /> B GD-T cng quyt nh bt u t ngy 20-11-2011, cc trng cao ng  mun ng k hot ng phi t c cc tiu chun c th v ging  vin v din tch phng hc nh: i ng ging vin c hu, cn b qun  l  nng lc xy dng v thc hin chng trnh o to, m bo t l  khng qu 25 sinh vin/ging vin mi khi kin thc ca tt c cc  ngnh o to, trong  t nht 15% ging vin c trnh  thc s tr  ln.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="author" style="text-align: right;"><strong>Theo Tui Tr</strong></div>', '', -2, 13, 0, 227, '2011-10-22 08:36:50', 62, '', '2011-10-24 17:03:25', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 08:36:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 18, '', '', 0, 11, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(121, 'Hin k cho B Gio dc: Ko di tuyn sinh n thng 12!', 'hin-k-cho-b-giao-dc-keo-dai-tuyn-sinh-n-thang-12', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Nhng vn  bt cp trong tuyn sinh  va qua c GS Trn Hng Qun vch ra vi mong mun a nn gio dc  Vit Nam pht trin.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Theo GS Trn Hng Qun, Ch tch Hip  hi cc trng H, C ngoi cng lp Vit Nam, k thi tuyn sinh H, C  theo hnh thc ba chung  tin hnh c 10 nm, tuy c nhng mt  tch cc trong my nm u trin khai, nhng n nay  khng cn thch  hp, cn sm thay th bng hnh thc khc.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"></p>\r\n<table class="picBox" style="text-align: justify;" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://giaoduc.net.vn/Uploaded/xuantrung/2011_10_18/DSC06557.JPG" border="0" width="475" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="desc"><span style="font-size: 14px;">nh minh ha Xun Trung</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Chng ta nn thc hin nghim tc ngh quyt ca i hi XI ca ng:  i mi mt cch cn bn v ton din nn gio dc. i mi t duy,  trc ht l i mi c ch qun l gio dc, mnh dn chm dt hnh  thc thi tuyn sinh ba chung, giao quyn t ch v tuyn sinh cho cc  trng H, C, TCCN. B khng nn m m lm cc vic ca nh trng,  ca a phng, m cn tp trung vo cng vic qun l nh nc - GS  Trn Hng Qun cho bit.<br /> <br /> C th,  gii quyt nhng kh khn trc mt, GS Trn Hng Qun thay mt cc trng NCL kin ngh:<br /> <br /> <em>Th nht</em>: Ko di thi gian tuyn sinh cho n khi tuyn  ch  tiu B giao, c th ht thng 12/2011, v cc trng i hc khng  nht thit khai ging vo thi gian c nh. Cho php cc trng H, C  kh khn v ngun tuyn, c xt tuyn c khi B cho ngnh Kinh t v  cc ngnh khc chp nhn kt qu thi khi B (hin nay s di d ngun  tuyn ca khi B cn nhiu, khi A li cn kit).<br /> <br /> <em>Th hai:</em> Vi nhng trng c nguy c ng ca, B nn c on  cng tc i th st nm tnh hnh, c gii php tnh th, hoc gii  php c bit gip cc trng tho g kh khn. Trnh tnh trng ch do  khng cn ngun tuyn m mt s trng b tc trong duy tr hot ng  ca nh trng, c hi cho cng cuc x hi ha gio dc. Trong tt c  thnh cng hay tht bi ca nh trng, cng u c phn ca B  GD&T.<br /> <br /> "Ngay t nm nay, B nn tp trung nghin cu ci cch khu thi tuyn  sinh. Hip hi chng ti sn sng tham gia cng B. B nn xem xt tham  kho phng n thi tuyn sinh mi m Hip Hi   xut hn na nm  trc" - GS Qun nhn mnh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>(GDVN)</strong></p>', '', -2, 13, 0, 227, '2011-10-22 08:35:30', 62, '', '2011-10-22 10:52:06', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 08:35:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 4, 0, 19, '', '', 0, 13, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(120, 'Sinh vin hc hiu qu nht vo gi no trong ngy? ', 'sinh-vien-hc-hiu-qu-nht-vao-gi-nao-trong-ngay-', '', '<div style="text-align: justify;">(GDVN) - Mt nghin cu mi y cho thy rng nhng sinh vin i hc vo bui sng c kt qu hc tp tt hn.</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>(GDVN) - Phn ln sinh vin i hc u thch ln ging ng vo bui chiu thay v vo bui sng v c th ng nhiu hn. Tuy nhin, mt nghin cu mi y cho thy rng nhng sinh vin i hc vo bui sng c kt qu hc tp tt hn.</strong><br /> <br /> Nghin cu ca hai nh tm l hc Pamela Thacher v Serge Onyper, thuc trng i hc St Lawrence (M), cho thy rng nhng sinh vin tham d cc lp hc bui chiu c nhiu thi gian  ng hn, nhng h cng d lm dng bia ru hn so vi cc sinh vin hc vo bui sng.<br /> <br /> Thc t, chng ti  pht hin thy rng nhng ngi ng dy mun thng ung nhiu bia ru hn nhng ngi dy sm. Sinh vin khng ung ru s khng lm nh hng ti vic hc ca h, trong khi, ng nhiu khng h gip sinh vin hc tt hn, tin s Pamela Thacher cho bit.<br /> <br /> <img src="http://giaoduc.net.vn/Uploaded/nguyenlap/2011_10_12/anh.jpg" style="vertical-align: middle;" border="0" /><br /> <br /> Nhm nghin cu  tin hnh theo di thi quen dy sm ca cc sinh vin i hc, da trn mt bng thng tin v thi gian ng, lch hc hng ngy, lng bia ru tiu th v tinh thn do nhng sinh vin t cung cp cho nhm nghin cu.<br /> <br /> Kt qu, cc nh khoa hc nhn thy rng nhng sinh vin hc trn lp vo bui chiu c im s trung bnh thp hn so vi sinh vin hc vo bui sng. <br /> <br /> Ti c th khng nh rng lp hc bui sng nn bt u t 8h hay 8h30 bi v y l qung thi gii gip sinh vin tip thu bi ging hiu qu nht, tin s Pamela Thacher cho bit.<br /> <br /> <strong>H Anh </strong><em>(Edvantage)</em></p>', '', 1, 4, 0, 28, '2011-10-22 08:34:13', 62, '', '2012-04-10 12:25:51', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 08:34:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 4, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 92, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(119, 'Kt thc tuyn sinh 2011: Nhiu trng ng ca ngnh ', 'kt-thuc-tuyn-sinh-2011-nhiu-trng-ong-ca-nganh-', '', '<div class="sapo">V khng tuyn  th sinh (TS) nn trong nm hc mi  ny, nhiu trng H hoc tm ngng hoc chnh thc khng o to mt s  ngnh.</div>\r\n<div class="body">\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Cng lp cng cht vt</strong></div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Hai ngnh ting Php v song ng Php -  Anh c th s ngng o to ti trng H Nng Lm TP.HCM. PGS-TS Hunh  Thanh Hng - Ph hiu trng trng H Nng Lm TP.HCM, cho bit: Cc  nm qua, hai ngnh ny tuyn khng c TS. Nm nay tnh hnh cng bi  t nh vy, TS u vo s c chuyn sang ngnh khc hc. Khng nhng  th, bn ngnh hc ti Phn hiu Ninh Thun ca trng l nng hc,  cng ngh thng tin, qun l mi trng, kinh t nng lm cng phi  ngng o to.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Tin t Ban o to H  Nng cho bit  s ng ca 2 ngnh s phm gio dc chnh tr v vn ha hc ca trng  H S phm. Ngnh s phm gio dc c bit ch tuyn c 12 TS cho 3  t tuyn, trong khi ch tiu l 41; ngnh vn ha hc ch tuyn c 8  TS trong khi ch tiu l 42. Nhng TS trng tuyn ca 2 ngnh hc ny s  c php chuyn ngnh, vo hc nhng ngnh c im chun tng ng,  hoc c bo lu kt qu trng tuyn cho nm hc sau.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Kt thc thi hn np h s xt tuyn  nguyn vng 3, lnh o nhiu trng H ti ng bng sng Cu Long gn  nh trnh tr li khi bo ch  cp v nhng thng tin lin quan n h  s xt tuyn. Tin s Nguyn Vn  - Hiu trng trng H ng Thp,  cho bit h s xin xt tuyn nguyn vng 3 khng nhiu. <br /> <br /> Nm nay trng ch tuyn c khong 70% so vi tng ch tiu B GD-T  giao. Theo ng , do lng h s qu t nn H ng Thp quyt nh  dng tuyn sinh 4 ngnh: s phm k thut cng nghip, s phm k thut  nng nghip, khoa hc th vin, cng ngh thit b trng hc.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nm 2011 trng H An Giang cng lm vo  th nhiu ngnh tuyn khng  TS  m lp. Thc s Hong Xun Qung,  Ph hiu trng, chua xt  cp nhng ngnh H phi ng ca. C th l  ngnh s phm vt l, s phm ha hc, s phm a l, chn nui th y.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<table class="picBox" border="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://giaoduc.net.vn/Uploaded/haiyen/2011_10_15/tuyensinh45096821.jpg" border="0" width="475" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="desc">TS np h s vo trng H Vn Hin, trng ny nm nay ng ca 2 ngnh - nh: o Ngc Thch</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Nm nay trng ch tuyn c trn 85% so tng ch tiu cc ngnh o  to H, C. Trng rt c gng nhng ngun TS t im sn tr ln li  khng di do, ng Qung ni.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Kh khn cho ngnh khoa hc c bn</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">D phng s TS o, H Hu  quyt nh  gi thm gn 1.500 ch tiu cho nguyn vng 3, th nhng ch c 421 h  s ng k. PGS-TS Nguyn Vn Tn - Hiu trng trng H Khoa hc, cho  bit: V phn ln cc ngnh o to ca trng l c bn nn rt kh  thu ht TS. Hin nay cc em ch chung cc ngnh thuc lnh vc kinh t,  ra trng d xin vic, d kim tin. <br /> <br /> Do , cng khng nn ngc nhin khi cc hc sinh gii ton chn thi vo  cc trng Kinh t, Ngoi thng; hc sinh gii vn thi vo bo ch...  Cc ngnh c bn v vy m ngy cng thiu vng sinh vin.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cn PGS-TS Nguyn c Hng - Ph gim  c H Hu, cho rng vic cc ngnh c bn khng tuyn c TS l tnh  trng chung ca cc trng H trn c nc, ch khng ring g Hu. y  l mt vn  v m cn c nh hng v chin lc ca Chnh ph, bn  thn cc trng H khng th mt mnh gii quyt. Chng hn ngnh trit  hc c chnh sch u i sinh vin theo hc khng phi ng hc ph song  vn khng c ngi hc, bi cc em nhn thy khng c tng lai cho u  ra, ng Hng nhn mnh. <br /> <br /> Theo ng Hng, mt s ngnh nu t TS, s vn ng sang hc cc ngnh  khc tng ng trong cng khi. Nu TS vn quyt nh theo hc ngnh  mnh  ng k, theo quy ch o to tn ch, trng vn to iu kin  cho sinh vin theo hc. Tuy nhin, ng Hng vn khng nh: Mt s  ngnh khng c TS n nhp hc, chng ti s tm ngng o to mt nm  ch khng c chuyn ng ca cc ngnh ny. <br /> <br /> ng thi, ng Hng thng tin thm, sp ti, H Hu s t chc cc cuc  hp nhm r sot, cu trc li cc ngnh ngh o to hin nay  c s  thay i cho ph hp hn, v d nhng ngnh qu hp s c ghp li vi  mt ngnh ln hn chung lnh vc.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Ngoi cng lp ht hi</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cng ngh thng tin v ting Anh l th  mnh ca trng H Cng ngh thng tin Gia nh m n nay trng vn  cha chc chn s lng TS n nhp hc c   m lp khng. Nu iu  ny xy ra, trng s phi ng vin cc TS chuyn qua cc ngnh hc  khi kinh t. Tng t, trng H Vn Hin quyt nh s khng o to  hai ngnh x hi hc v vn ha hc do tuyn c qu t TS. Cc TS  trng tuyn vo hai ngnh ny s c ng vin chuyn qua hc cc ngnh  khc trong trng.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">ng L Cng C - Ch tch HQT trng H  Duy Tn cho hay: 3 ngnh quan h quc t, vn hc, VN hc c kh nng  ng ca vnh vin v vi  ny chc chn nhng nm tip theo vn khng  tuyn c TS. Ban o to trng H Kin trc  Nng cng thng tin  nm nay quyt nh ng ca ngnh ting Anh v sau 3 t tuyn, khng c  TS no ng k.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Ming bnh nh</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nm nay, khng ch cc trng ngoi cng  lp a ra nhng cch thc thu ht TS nh tng tin, hc bng m ngay  c nhng trng cng lp ln,  mt kha cnh no , cng li ko ngi  hc.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Gn nh tt c cc trng H thnh vin  ca H Quc gia TP.HCM u p dng nguyn vng 1B. Mt vi trng khc,  nh trng H Ngn hng TP.HCM, xt tuyn nguyn vng 2 cho TS im cao  ca trng mnh. Nhng trng khc li c chng trnh o to cht  lng cao, chng trnh c bit hoc chng trnh o to ngoi ngn  sch Hu qu l khng cn bao nhiu TS c im thi bng im sn bc  vo sn chi nguyn vng 3 ca nhng trng H ngoi cng lp. Chnh  v vy, nhng chiu li ko, thng tin cho TS bt ngun t chuyn  ming bnh nh nhiu ngi ginh git ny.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="author">Theo Thanh Nin</div>', '', -2, 13, 0, 227, '2011-10-22 08:33:16', 62, '', '2011-10-22 09:24:44', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 08:33:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 21, '', '', 0, 1, 'robots=\nauthor=');
