(118, 'Bc tm th gi B trng B Gio dc nhn dp nm hc mi', 'bc-tam-th-gi-b-trng-b-giao-dc-nhan-dp-nm-hc-mi', '', '<div class="body">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Nm hc mi  bt u c vi ngy, l mt ngi dn Vit Nam,  tng cp sch n trng, ti xin c vi li gi n ng.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Knh gi B trng B Gio dc - o to!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nm hc mi  bt u c vi ngy, l mt ngi dn Vit Nam,  tng cp sch n trng, ti xin c vi li gi n ng.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Tha ng, mi y thi, trong mt bi pht biu trn bo ch, ng  tng cho rng "Hng ngn im 0 mn Lch s thi H va qua l chuyn bnh thng!".  tng tri qua ci thi hc sinh, ngi hc tng trang sch tri di theo lch s dn tc, ti khng chp nhn cch B trng tr li nh vy. B trng tr li l i din cho c b GD&amp;T m li em so snh vic hc ca hc sinh VN v hc sinh nc khc - s VN v s nc khc. Liu nh vy c phi l phin din?</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Phng php dy v hc ca VN lun i sau th gii. Cc chuyn vin trong B cng u l gio s - tin s - du hc nc ngoi v vy m cch gio dc ca VN hng bao nhiu nm qua vn khng khc g nh hi sau gii phng?</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nu c chng ch khc l sch by gi t hn - v p hn (kin thc th vn th). Hc ph by gi t hn v c nhiu ph ph hn (ch khng phi cht lng tt hn). Hc sinh by gi i hc kh hn khng phi v kin thc nhiu hn m l v c qu nhiu th nhi vo u m chng bit ci no l kin thc.<br /> <br /> Vn hc c gi l b mn Quc ng - ngn ng Quc gia. Nu B trng c c nhng bi vn bt h ca hc sinh th B trng s cm thy th no?</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nh em c nui mt b ni. u b to nh qu bng nha 5000, hai mt b to nh hai hn bi ve. Hng ngy b chng lm g ch ngi mt ch nhai tru v nh nc bt khng ng ni quy nh".</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Hay tng tng tng, ba ting trng vang ln bo hiu gi hc  n, cc bn chen ln x y nhau vo lp. Khi mi ngi n nh ch ngi, c gio mi chy t cng vo, do c dy mun nn phi tranh th cho con b. Khi c vo th c lp ng ln cho. C bo cc em ngi xung ri hi hm nay lp mnh c ai ng tin khng?..."</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">S hc cn gi l truyn thng ca dn tc. Liu B trng c tin l nhng hc sinh cp 3 vn cn nhm tng l L Lai v L Li l hai anh em rut khng.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Th h chng ti, v c th h ang ngi trn gh nh trng by gi na, h c ai hi ci g l chng ti li ni: " em tm trong sch".</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nu hc tr ch bit nghe c gio c sch gio khoa cho chp th liu cc em c thot ra khi ci suy ngh: Nghe lm g v trong sch c ht, c ni y nh trong sch c khc g u.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Hay cc c gio cng ch bit dy nh mt thi quen i vi cc bi ging do dy nhiu m nh, nn cng chng cn o su t duy  a ra cch ging mi hoc mt kha cnh khc. Liu by gi c cn nhng ting ci trong lp S - liu c nhng nh mt m mng trong lp Vn v say m vi mn hc? Hay chuyn  c nhc li nh mt qu kh?</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<table align="center" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://giaoduc.net.vn/images/stories/2011/08/18/1735166189-1-CoGiao.jpeg" alt="n trng trc tin l phi " align="middle" border="0" width="470" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: center;"><strong>n trng trc tin l phi "Tin hc l, hu hc vn"</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ti thit ngh: nu thc s cn ci cch th hy ci cch t duy  tm nhn  phng php ging dy ca cc thy c gio trc. T khi b GD&amp;T c thnh lp n nay l bao nhiu nm? C bao nhiu ln t chc tng kim tra kin thc ca chnh cc nh gio? Liu cc nh gio c p ng  kin thc v t duy  ging dy hay ch l mt ngi ln c sch nhiu hn, thuc nhiu hn, bit nhiu hn dy li cho a cha bit g theo cch: "Cc con gi sch ra trang x bi y phn z. Mt bn ng dy c cho c t x n y. c xong th bt u im vi gch u dng ri cho v nh hc thuc lng v mai c kim tra".<br /> <br /> Vy th cc phng php gio dc trc quan, phng php ging dy thng qua phn bin thc t nh B  tng ni, vic ci cch sch gio khoa vi 70.000 t nh B kin ngh, liu c thc t khi m i ng ging dy vn gi nguyn l thi lm vic?</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Hay c chng li s ci cch sch theo kiu: Trong bng ch ci, ch E gn m nn a ln u. Nu vy th ch B phi ln trc v B l ch u tin ca  B - b sinh ra m th b ng trc ch? B ri n B, ri mi n M. Nhng vn cn thiu ng. Vy th bng ch ci s bt u t u?<br /> <br /> Xin cc nh gio hy dy cho hc sinh nhng g t ngn ngun tnh yu thng vi t nc, lch s dn tc v nim t ho ca nc Vit. Nu lm c nh vy, ti ngh s khng bao gi cn tn ti cc lp hc thm v dy thm. V hc sinh Vit Nam s thc s hiu c mnh l ai, ang  v tr no trn th gii, cn phi lm g v nh th no  a Vit Nam i ln.<br /> <br /> Chc B trng v cc thy c gio nm hc mi di do sc khe, dy tt  hc sinh v con ti c hc tt.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><em>c gi o Hong Ngc </em><strong>(GDVN)</strong></p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 3, 0, 22, '2011-10-22 08:31:34', 62, '', '2012-04-10 12:16:02', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 08:31:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 5, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 204, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(117, 'CTN Trng Tn Sang: Phi y mnh Lch s trong nm hc mi', 'ctn-trng-tn-sang-phi-y-mnh-lch-s-trong-nm-hc-mi', '', '<div class="sapo" style="text-align: center;"><em><img src="http://giaoduc.net.vn/Uploaded/haiyen/2011_08_30/truong%20tan%20sang.jpg" border="0" height="305" width="397" /></em></div>\r\n<div class="sapo">(GDVN) - Nhn dp nm hc mi, Ch tch nc Trng Tn Sang  vit th gi n ton th ng bo. <em> </em></div>\r\n<div class="body">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cc thy gio, c gio, cn b, cng chc, vin chc ngnh gio dc, cc bc ph huynh v cc em hc sinh, sinh vin thn mn!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nhn dp khai ging nm hc mi 2011  2012 v ngy ton dn a tr n trng, ti thn i gi ti cc th h nh gio, cn b, cng chc, vin chc ngnh gio dc, cc bc ph huynh v cc em hc sinh, sinh vin trong c nc li chc mng tt p nht.<br /><br /> Nm hc 2010  2011, ngnh gio dc  c nhiu c gng, tin b. Quy m v mng li gio dc tip tc c m rng; cht lng gio dc  cc cp hc c nng ln; gio dc o c, php lut, l tng sng cho hc sinh, sinh vin c ch trng; cng tc x hi ho gio dc, huy ng cc ngun lc u t cho gio dc t kt qu tt; c s vt cht ca nh trng c tng cng. <br /><br /> Ti nhit lit biu dng s n lc c gng v nhng kt qu ca ngnh gio dc, nht l cc tp th, c nhn in hnh tin tin, cc thy gio, c gio tm huyt, tn tu vi cng vic, cc em hc sinh ngho,  vng su, vng xa, bin gii, hi o  vt kh vn ln trong hc tp.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nm hc 2011  2012 c  ngha rt quan trng, l nm hc u tin thc hin Ngh quyt i hi ng ton quc ln XI.  thc hin tt s mnh nng cao dn tr, pht trin ngun nhn lc, bi dng nhn ti, gp phn quan trng pht trin t nc, xy dng nn vn ho v con ngi Vit Nam, cng vi s gp sc ca ton x hi, ngnh gio dc cn i mi cn bn, ton din, xy dng, nng cao cht lng i ng gio vin, cn b qun l gio dc; <br /> <br /> i mi mnh m ni dung, chng trnh, phng php dy v hc  tt c cc cp hc, bc hc; y mnh thi ua dy tt, hc tt; nng cao cht lng gio dc ton din, c bit coi trng gio dc truyn thng lch s, o c, li sng,  thc trch nhim x hi, nng lc sng to, k nng thc hnh, tc phong cng nghip; <br /> <br /> xy dng mi trng gio dc lnh mnh, kt hp cht ch gia nh trng vi gia nh v x hi; huy ng cc ngun lc tng cng u t pht trin gio dc, nht l  vng su, vng xa, bin gii, hi o, vng ng bo dn tc thiu s; <br /> <br /> thc hin tt chnh sch u i, h tr i vi hc sinh, sinh vin gii, ngho, khuyt tt, con em gia nh c cng vi cch mng, dn tc thiu s, gio vin cng tc  nhng vng kh khn.<br /> <br /> Ti mong mun v tin tng cc em hc sinh, sinh vin pht huy truyn thng hiu hc ca dn tc ta, n lc phn u vn ln, rn luyn tt, t nhiu thnh tch cao trong hc tp, nghin cu khoa hc.<br /> <br /> Ti  ngh cc cp u ng, chnh quyn, cc t chc, on th v ton x hi tip tc quan tm, chm lo nhiu hn na cho s nghip trng ngi, to mi iu kin thun li  con em chng ta c hc tp, rn luyn t kt qa tt.<br /> <br /> Chc cc thy gio, c gio, cn b, cng chc, vin chc ngnh gio dc v ton th cc em hc sinh, sinh vin t c nhiu thnh tch xut sc trong nm hc mi. Chc s nghip gio dc ngnh cng pht trin, gp phn tch cc vo s nghip xy dng v bo v T quc Vit Nam x hi ch ngha.<em><br /> </em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><em>Thn i</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><em>Ch tch nc CHXHCN Vit Nam</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><em>Trng Tn Sang</em></p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 3, 0, 20, '2011-10-22 08:30:15', 62, '', '2012-04-10 12:23:41', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 08:30:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 7, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 107, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(116, 'Nhn khai ging, GS Ng Bo Chu k chuyn... chic qun cc ', 'nhan-khai-ging-gs-ngo-bo-chau-k-chuyn-chic-qun-cc-', '', '<div class="sapo">\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">(GDVN) - GS Ng Bo Chu  v trng c, Trng THPT Chuyn H Khoa hc T nhin, H QGHN hm 4/9  d khai ging.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="body">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Trong s nhng v khch c mi d l  khai ging nm nay ca trng c B trng B GD-T Phm V Lun, i  din ph huynh hc sinh cc th h.<br /> <br /> Hc sinh c ca trng, ngoi GS Ng Bo Chu cn c GS Trn Vn Nhung,  Tng th k Hi ng Chc danh Gio s Nh nc (nguyn hc sinh kho 1  khi chuyn ton A0).</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<table class="picBox" border="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://giaoduc.net.vn/Uploaded/haiyen/2011_09_05/NBC%20ve%20truong%20cu.jpg" border="0" width="475/" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="desc">Gio s Ng Bo Chu chp nh vi cc thy c gio v HS trong trng</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Pht biu ti l khai ging, GS Ng Bo  Chu nhc li k nim cch y 25 nm, anh cng cc bn cng lp ln u  tin n M Tr lm th tc nhp hc vi cm xc hi hp xen ln b  ng. <br /> <br /> Sau khi nhc tn mt s bn c, ngi hc tr c Ng Bo Chu nh li:  Ti cn nh khi  bn th mc qun o v, bn th mc qun cc bi  ang  tui ln m tiu chun mua vi ca b m  ht. Bn mi cng  thnh bn quen rt nhanh, ch sau mt trn  bng ny la ngay bn tri  hi trng chng ta ang ngi y.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ba nm  tri qua rt nhanh trn nhng  chic bn gh xiu vo, nhng gian phng nh ca khi ph thng chuyn  ton... Ba nm A0 l ba nm m chng ti trng thnh t bao nim vui  ni bun. Ba nm A0 lun lun lu li trong tm khm ca chng ti -  nhng chng trai, c gi tr trng thnh t nhng c cu qun cc.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<table class="picBox" border="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://giaoduc.net.vn/Uploaded/haiyen/2011_09_05/gsngobaochau_1.jpg" border="0" width="475/" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="desc">GS Ng Bo Chu lun l thn tng ca gii tr</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nh li lch s thnh lp khi chuyn ton trng H Tng hp H Ni  trc y, ng Ng Bo Chu by t tnh cm tri n ti nhng nh lnh  o, nhng nh khoa hc c cng thnh lp khi chuyn ton, c Th  tng Phm Vn ng v c gio s T Quang Bu.</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">GS Ng Bo Chu chia s: Cch y mt nm, khi ti c Th tng  Nguyn Tn Dng tip, ng c ni vi ti, khi ng c nhn tin v gii  thng Fields ca ti, iu u tin ng lm l n mt gc to nh ca  Chnh ph thp nn hng cho c Th tng Phm Vn ng. iu  vi ti  rt cm ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="author" style="text-align: right;">Bo Gio Dc</div>', '', -2, 14, 0, 156, '2011-10-22 08:29:14', 62, '', '2011-10-22 09:25:40', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 08:29:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 5, '', '', 0, 8, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(115, 'Chn trn, bng i, vc qun trn vai vt sui tm con ch', 'chan-trn-bng-oi-vac-qun-tren-vai-vt-sui-tim-con-ch', '', '<p>(GDVN) -  nhiu ni trn t nc ny, c cp sch  n trng  l mt nim vui v tn ca cc em nh, no c dm ngh n  ci o mi.</p>\r\n<div id="ctl00_PrimaryContent_ctl00_divRelatedContents">\r\n<ul class="article-link">\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>ng n trng ca hc sinh vng cao Cao nguyn Do San (Lai Chu). "Vt qun ln vai th ny cho khi t!"</p>\r\n<div class="slideview" style="height: 347px;"><img src="http://giaoduc.net.vn/Uploaded/haiyen/2011_09_05/ap_20101111014949376.jpg" border="0" style="border-width: 0px;" /></div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<div class="author" style="text-align: right;">Nhm PV Gio dc</div>', '', -2, 18, 0, 163, '2011-10-22 08:27:36', 62, '', '2011-10-22 10:30:37', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 08:27:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 4, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 25, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(114, 'Trn ng Tun: Nc mnh ngho, nhng c n mc ny khng?', 'trn-ng-tun-nc-minh-ngheo-nhng-co-n-mc-nay-khong', '', '<h1 class="title"><span style="color: black;">Trn ng Tun: Nc mnh ngho, nhng c n mc ny khng? </span></h1>\r\n<div class="time"><span style="color: black;">Th t 28/09/2011 00:53 </span></div>\r\n<div class="sapo"><span style="color: black;">(GDVN) - Mnh bit nc ta ngho (ni chung, rt chung thi), nhng c ngho n th khng ?</span></div>\r\n<div id="ctl00_PrimaryContent_ctl00_divRelatedContents">\r\n<ul class="article-link">\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="body">\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: black;">Nh  bo Trn ng Tun, nguyn Ph Tng Gim c i Truyn hnh Vit Nam,  va tr v t Sui Ging (Yn Bi) vi nhng tri nghim y xc ng.  Chng ti xin trch ng cu chuyn gin d t blog c nhn ca ng.<br />Sng  nay, ln u tin ln Sui Ging (Yn Bi), xe ln n trung tm x  Sui Ging, th no li  ngay trc ca trng hc. My trm a tr  con ang tp th dc. Ngay cnh  l my dy nh ni tr. Khng hiu  sao, c nhn thy tr con min ni l mnh m.<br /></span></div>\r\n<span style="color: black;"><strong>Nh nc khng h tr</strong><br />\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">Cu  ch qun trc ca trng, c v l gio vin, cho bit: Trng tiu  hc c 80 a ni tr. Phi c t 100 a ni tr tr ln mi c ch   h tr ca nh nc. Khu ni tr ny dn nui hon ton. Cha m gp 2kg  go/tun, 5.000 ng tin thc n/tun.<br /> \r\n<table class="picBox" border="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://giaoduc.net.vn/Uploaded/haiyen/2011_09_28/22092011045_copy.jpg" border="0" width="475" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="desc">Nh bo Trn ng Tun xung thm bp n ca cc em nh</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nBn  mnh khng tin, c lc vn mi: Sao li 5.000 th chng n n ung  kiu g?. Cu ta c khng khng ng th, ng th. Va lc c mt bc  H.Mng xch x nc i ngang, cu ch qun bo: y, ng ny nu cm cho  chng n . <br />Th l bn mnh i theo lun. Tro tt qua my dy nh  trn i, i thng vo cng y ban X Sui Ging, ri vng ra sau nh  y ban, th c ci lu tng che g vn, gia c ci bp ang  la,  ngoi ca c ci chu tm ln y nhng ci bt to bn cha ra. Trong  bp ngoi ni cm ang nu, mt ni na chc  nu canh, cn th chng  c  c g c.<br />- 80 a ch n ci ni cm ny  ?. <br />Bc H Mng: Ni to lm y, 13 - 14 cn go mi y y. <br />- Th n cm vi ci g?<br />Bc H Mng: Vi canh rau... <br />By  gi mi nhn ra ch ti ti, c my b rau ci b to, m li  a  vng mt na. Khng hiu canh nu vi g, v mm mui giu  u, ch  khng c trong bp. <br />- Sao t rau th ?<br />Bc H Mng: , khng  u, phi mua thm na y<br />- Th c tht c n bao gi khng ?<br />Bc H Mng: Khng c u, bao gi b m ng thm tin th mua cho n mt ba c tht.<br />Mt  ni cm (hy vng l ) v mt ni canh rau ci ( gm x nc va c  xch ln, my b rau, chc t mui, mm, du m cho vo na- nhng qu  tht bn mnh khng thy chng c ct ch no, chc khng c trong bp  v s ch mo hay n trm chng?) -  l ba n tra cho 80 mm non  ca t nc vo ngy 22 thng 9 nm 2011, tc l khi t nc  bc  vo thp k th hai ca th k 21, l sau mt nm tng bng k nim 1000  nm Thng Long, l nm u ca nhim k i Hi 11...<br />Bn mnh ni: Tra nay bc mua tht cho chng n n c khng?. Bn mnh a t tin. Mnh a thm na, <br />Sng  th chc c thi, nhng mnh ngh hc kh vo lm. Hi i hc, lc  no mnh cng mun n, d b m nui nng y  hn bn tr con hng  xm nhiu. Khi i bt u i hc i hc  Thanh xun, c ngy thy i.  n tp th, xong ba, ra bt cm v, dc ng t nh n n phng    thy thm n na. Ngi trn lp ,lc no cng ngh n n. <br />Ti  bn chng n r sang phng con gi tn, mnh khng i, v nhn mt con  gi cng thch nhng ang ni chuyn t nhin thy i th khng thch  g ni na. <br />Ch hc sinh ni tr  c ging tng, mi bung c bng  ghi  ca: Nhm bn Lp, Nhm bn... Chn chiu bn lm. Nhng  thi, ci ny mnh nhn thy nhiu ri. c ci nh cng kn, ma ng  trn ni nh kn l quan trng nht.<br />Gp c H Mong tr b con chc  mi 7-8 thng tui, ngi trn tng . Hi ra mi bit t bn xung thm  con  ni tr cp mt, ang i gi tan hc  gp con. a b ngoan  tht, ngi l b c ci toe tot. Cn c m cng hm ra pht, mnh hi  a  Cho tao mang v nui nh, th tr li  , cho y,  a khc  c m !. My anh em cho t tin gi l mng tui b th  mt gt  ra, phi di vo tay mi chu ly.<br />Theo Bn,  hc sinh Sui Ging c 1 ba tht/ ngy, ai nn u t?<br />\r\n<div id="survey">\r\n<div class="modcontents">\r\n<ul class="choice">\r\n<li><input id="vote71_0" name="vote71" type="radio" value="Nh nc u t" /> Nh nc u t </li>\r\n<li><input id="vote71_1" name="vote71" type="radio" value="Nh ho tm u t" /> Nh ho tm u t </li>\r\n<li><input id="vote71_2" name="vote71" type="radio" value="Nh nc v nh ho tm cng u t" /> Nh nc v nh ho tm cng u t </li>\r\n<li style="border-right: medium none;"><input id="vote71_3" name="vote71" type="radio" value="Khng u t" /> Khng u t </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="sbm-choice"></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>C gio nhng cm HS</strong><br />Sang  bn khu ni tr (cng dn nui) ca trng trung hc c s th nh ca  c v tunh tong hn nhiu. Ma ng th ny cht rt mt. Nhng c  ci n ung c v quy c hn.<br />Cc c gio  ngay cng dy vi hc  sinh. Mt c khi t di i ln nhn c tng hc sinh,v thp nh, mc  ci o khoc trng nh ng phc, n ni nghe c y ni mi hiu l c  gio.<br />Bp chung lun vi khu ging tng, c hai bp u  la hun hai ci ni to en, m ra thy mt ni cm, mt ni canh b. <br />- Th c mn g na khng h c?<br />C  gio ch gi nilon nh trn bn, mnh cm ln xem, th ra my ming c  kh. C 45 a cp hai ni tr n  y, cng tiu chun 5 ngn /tun.  Nhng bn ny c v c n kh hn l cp 1. Cc c gio bt tin lng  ca mnh, cng vo tin b m gp,  mua thc n. <br /> \r\n<table class="picBox" border="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://giaoduc.net.vn/Uploaded/haiyen/2011_09_28/22092011043_copy.jpg" border="0" width="475" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="desc">"Khng hiu sao, c nhn thy tr em min ni l mnh m"</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nTheo  nhm tnh th mi thng 45 a c 900 ngn tin thc n (tr go) do b  m gp. Tin cc c gio cho thm cng chng y na. Bnh qun mi chu  c 2.000  tin thc phm/ngy (bn cp 1 ch 1 ngn/ngy). Bn ny u  n mi tun c mt ba n tht. <br />C th l: Mua di ch 1 kg  loi tht r nht, ri kho ln vi u ph. Hm  gn Mo Vc mnh cng  nhn tr con trng ni tr n cm, thy chng n n ci mn g c trng  trng, mnh cm bt ln nhn k , th ra l u ph mu trng c ln  tht m bo nho, cng mu trng, ci bt nhm mo cng trng trng na,  ha ra mt mn mu sc nh vy. Hm  cc thy c gio ni tht l c  khch n thm nn mi thm mn , ch theo lch th cha n ngy c  mn n mn.<br />Li nh  6-7 nm trc, lm Ni vng tay ln, mnh c  my nhm i vo cc min ngho. M Linh (gi vn dn Vn ha- S kin v  nhn vt trn VTV3) i mi Ty Bc quay cnh ba cm ca HS dn tc ni  tr.<br />Ri hm pht trc tip, M Linh va dn chng trnh va khc  nc trc bao triu ngi xem TV, khc tht s, d c nn, khi ni n  chuyn: ch cn 2 ngn ng/ngy cho mi a b thi th hng ngy th  ba n c mu sc hn, ch by gi ch thy c mu trng ca cm v  trng ca mng nu mui...<br />Bng y nm tri qua. Nm va ri l nm  u tin mnh khng cn ch tr lm Ni vng tay ln ca VTV. Nhng hm  nay ln Sui Ging, vn thy ba cm nh th, ri vn thy con s 2 ngn  ng th mi ngy s c tht n, nhng vn cha c c ci hai ngn  y. M hai ngn ng cch y 7 nm to hn 2 ngn ng by gi lm ch.<br /><strong>D n 9 triu/thng v nim t ho ca mt ng vin</strong><br />Trn  ng tr ra, mnh tnh k:  mi khu ni tr (80 a cp mt, 45 a  cp hai) ngy nu mt ba c tht kho ln u ph, s cn 2kg tht cho  cp 1, 1kg cho bn cp hai, km u ph na l 300 ngn/ngy, hay l 9  triu ng/thng. Mi nm s cn 108 triu ng. Nu c hai ba c tht  trong ngy th cn gp i: 18 triu/thng, hay 216 triu/nm.<br /> c  125 a tr c m n trong c nm, c kho khon, u c sng lng  th thm s tin  c gi c l nhiu khng? Mnh bit nc ta ngho  (ni chung, rt chung thi), nhng c ngho n th khng ?.<br />Mnh  quyt nh l v nh gi ngay cho bn b  bn v d n cm tht km  u cho 125 chu  Sui Ging ny. Bc u l 1 ba c tht/ngy, hay  cn gi d n 9 triu. Ko c thm bn b th chuyn cng nhanh cng  tt sang 2 ba c tht/ngy, hay d n 18 triu/thng. Ly gii, ng c  lm pht hay tng gi na nh!<br /> \r\n<table class="picBox" border="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://giaoduc.net.vn/Uploaded/haiyen/2011_09_28/22092011041.jpg" border="0" width="475" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="desc">Nh bo Trn ng Tun trn tr vi cuc sng ca tr em vng cao</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nHay  l bn vi bn b lp hi nhng ngi bn ca tr em vng cao? By gi  c bao ngi i pht vng cao, gp mi ngi mt cht cho cc b. Lp  trang web<br />Khi ri Sui Ging c vi chc cy s, cht nh chuyn  khng bit bui sng bn tr con ny n c c n g khng. Ni vi mi  ngi trn xe. Mi ngi on mt kiu, nhng khng ai dm chc.<br />Cht  nh lc  bp trng cp hai, mnh hi c gio: Th mi c gio phi  bt bao nhiu tin t lng ca mnh  mua thc n cho cc chu ?. C  gio tr li : D khng ging nhau, ngi lng cao hay l ng vin th  gp nhiu hn, gio vin hp ng hay qun chng th gp t hn. <br />Vy  l ng vin th san t lng gio vin min ni ca mnh s tin nhiu  hn ngi khc  mua thc n cho hc sinh. Qu tht,  lu lm ri,  mnh him khi nghe c mt iu p  nh vy v ng vin. M khng  phi nghe t mt din n hay khung cnh honh trng no. M nghe th  tin ngay. Nghe m thy lng  lnh. Bi mnh cng l ng vin  my  chc nm ri.<br />Theo Bn,  hc sinh Sui Ging c 1 ba tht/ ngy, ai nn u t?<br />\r\n<div id="survey">\r\n<div class="modcontents">\r\n<ul class="choice">\r\n<li><input id="vote71_0" name="vote71" type="radio" value="Nh nc u t" /> Nh nc u t </li>\r\n<li><input id="vote71_1" name="vote71" type="radio" value="Nh ho tm u t" /> Nh ho tm u t </li>\r\n<li><input id="vote71_2" name="vote71" type="radio" value="Nh nc v nh ho tm cng u t" /> Nh nc v nh ho tm cng u t </li>\r\n<li style="border-right: medium none;"><input id="vote71_3" name="vote71" type="radio" value="Khng u t" /> Khng u t </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="sbm-choice" style="text-align: right;"><br /> Theo bo Gio dc Vit Nam</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</span></div>\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="70%" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr align="center">\r\n<td align="center"></td>\r\n<td align="center"></td>\r\n<td align="center"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '', -2, 14, 0, 156, '2011-10-22 08:27:01', 62, '', '2011-10-23 05:59:20', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 08:27:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_categ