(113, 'Chung kt "Festival ting Anh cp THCS  Thnh ph H Ni 2011"', 'chung-kt-qfestival-ting-anh-cp-thcs-thanh-ph-ha-ni-2011q', '', '<table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 1px;" align="left" border="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://hanoi.edu.vn/images_upload/small_1443.jpg" border="0" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: xx-small;">Tit mc d thi ca THCS Cu Giy, qun Cu Giy</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><span style="color: black;"><strong><em>Ngy 2/10/2011, S GD&amp;T H Ni  t chc vng Chung kt "Festival ting Anh cp THCS - TP H Ni 2011". Chng trnh do S GD&amp;T H Ni v T chc gio dc - o to Language Link t chc. Sau vng s kho din ra ngy 18/9/2011 va qua,  c 17 tit mc xut sc p ng cc tiu ch ting Anh, hnh nh, k thut ca ht... c chn vo vng chung kt.</em></strong><br /> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-indent: 0.5in; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: black;">Pht biu ti cuc thi, Ph Gim c S GD&amp;T H Ni on Hoi Vnh nhn mnh: Festival thc s l ngy hi ni ting Anh, l sn chi b ch, l th cho hc sinh THCS, gip cc em nng cao trnh  ting Anh v chia s nhng kinh nghim hc tt mn ngoi ng ny. Cuc thi nm trong chng trnh trin khai  n Nng cao cht lng dy v hc ng n nm 2020 ca Th tng Chnh ph. Qua , cc trng s tip tc i mi ton din vic dy v hc ngoi ng, trin khai chng trnh dy v hc ngoi ng mi  cp hc mt cch hiu qu nht. Cng thng qua ngy hi ting Anh, gio vin c c hi tip cn vi i mi phng php, i mi hnh thc truyn t kin thc cho hc sinh thng qua cc hot ng ngoi kha bng ting Anh</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-indent: 0.5in; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: black;">Cc tit mc tham gia vng chung kho kh a dng, th hin  nhiu lnh vc khc nhau t ht, ma, nhy hip-hop, Aerobics n din kch bng ting Anh. Cc th sinh  th hin kh nng ni, ht ting Anh kh tri chy, nhun nhuyn v giu sc biu cm, sng to trong mi tit mc d thi. Kt qu, 3 gii Nht  c trao cho THCS Thng Long (qun Ba nh), THCS Cu Giy (qun Cu Giy), THCS Gip Bt (qun Hong Mai); 3 gii Nh thuc v: THCS Lomonoxop (huyn T Lim), THCS Tru Qu (huyn Gia Lm), THCS Tn Triu (huyn Thanh Tr), 3 gii Ba thuc v: THCS ng a (qun ng a), THCS Thch Tht (huyn Thch Tht), THCS an Phng (huyn an Phng). Cc tit mc cn li ginh gii khuyn khch ca cuc thi. </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: black;"><strong>Tp ch Gio dc Th </strong></span></p>', '', 1, 4, 0, 27, '2011-10-22 08:24:19', 62, '', '2012-04-10 07:33:03', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 08:24:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 246, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(112, 'HI NGH GIAO BAN LN TH NHT CM THI UA VNG 7 NGNH GIO DC V O TO NM HC 2011-2012', 'hi-ngh-giao-ban-ln-th-nht-cm-thi-ua-vung-7-nganh-giao-dc-va-ao-to-nm-hc-2011-2012', '', '<table style="border-collapse: collapse;" border="0" cellspacing="0" width="1" align="left">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://hanoi.edu.vn/images_upload/small_1459.JPG" border="0" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: xx-small;">Lnh o 5 S GD&amp;T k giao c thi ua</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><span style="color: black;"><strong><em>Thc hin nhim v nm hc  2011-2012, ngy14/10, Hi  ngh giao ban ln th Nht ngnh GD&amp;T  cm thi ua vng 7 nm thnh ph Cn Th - TP H Ch Minh -  Nng -  Hi Phng - H Ni  din ra ti thnh ph H Ni. ng ch Nguyn Vinh  Hin - Th trng B GD&amp;T  ch tr Hi ngh. Ti d Hi ngh c  cc ng ch: Trn Cng Phong - Ch tch Cng on gio dc Vit Nam;  Lnh o cc Cc, V, Vin ca B GD&amp;T; Ph Ch tch UBND ca 29  qun, huyn, th x; i din Lnh o cc S, ban ngnh thnh ph H  Ni; Ban Gim c, Ch tch Cng on Ngnh v lnh o ca cc phng  ban ca 5 S GD&amp;T; cc Trng phng GD&amp;T ca 29 qun, huyn,  th x; 16 cm trng cc Trng THPT; Ch nhim cc cu lc b THPT,  GDTX, TCCN trn a bn thnh ph H Ni.</em></strong><br /> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; font-size: 12pt;">Ti  Hi ngh, ng ch Nguyn Hu  - Thnh y vin, Gim c S GD&amp;T  H Ni, Trng cm thi ua vng 7  thay mt lnh o 5 S c bo co  tng hp v tnh hnh trin khai nhim v nm hc 2011-2012 ca ngnh  GD&amp;T 5 Thnh ph. </span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; font-size: 12pt;">Theo  bo co, y l nm hc u tin thc hin Ngh quyt XI ca Trung ng  ng vi ni dungi mi cn bn nn gio dc Vit nam theo hng  chun ha, hin i ha, x hi ha, dn ch ha v hi nhp quc t  Tp trung nng cao cht lng gio dc, o to, coi trng gio dc o  c, li sng, nng lc sng to, k nng thc hnh, kh nng lp  nghip Vi tinh thn , ngay t u nm hc, cc S  cn c vo  tnh hnh thc tin ca a phng  xy dng nhim v trng tm nm  hc, trong  tp trung cc vn  nh: Nng cao cht lng v hiu qu  hot ng gio dc; ch trng i mi ni dung, phng php gio dc  trong cc cp hc; tip tc i mi cng tc qun l gio dc; chm lo,  u t pht trin i ng nh gio v cn b qun l; pht trin mng  li trng, lp v tng cng CSVC, thit b gio dc</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; font-size: 12pt;">T  u nm hc n nay, cc S GD&amp;T  t chc nhiu lp tp hun,  bi dng cho CBQL, GV v chuyn mn nghip v v c cc gii php linh  hot trong khu tuyn dng gio vin, quan tm u tin c th trong  tuyn dng gio vin Mm non. Theo thng k, tng ch tiu tuyn dng  gio vin, nhn vin cc cp ca Thnh ph Cn Th l 442, TP H Ch  Minh l 3.240;  Nng l 1.100 v H Ni c ti 7.502.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; font-size: 12pt;">Cc   n Dy v hc ngoi ng trong h thng gio dc quc dn giai on  2008-2012 v  n xy dng ngun nhn lc cht lng cao c cc S  tip tc trin khai thc hin. Xy dng trng t Chun quc gia l mt  trong nhng iu kin quan trng  nng cao cht lng gio dc c 5  thnh ph quan tm v  c bc pht trin ng k (So vi nm hc  trc, H Ni tng thm 23 trng, Hi Phng tng 05 trng).</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; font-size: 12pt;">Phong  tro Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc tip tc c  y mnh, ch trng cng tc gio dc truyn thng, rn luyn k nng  sng cho HS. T chc cc lp tp hun v cng tc y t, v sinh an ton  thc phm nhm phng trnh v pht hin sm cc bnh hc ng, bnh  chn tay ming trong cc trng hc. Phi hp vi chnh quyn a phng  v lc lng cng an thc hin tt Thng ATGT. Ring Thnh ph H Ni   trin khai nhn rng m hnh th im v an ton giao thng v qun  l dng in thoi di ng ng mc ch, ng quy nh ti cc trng  THPT thuc cc qun ni thnh.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; font-size: 12pt;">Ti  Hi ngh, cc S GD&amp;T   xut v trao i mt s kin ngh vi  B GD&amp;T, trong  tp trung vo cc vn  nh: Cng tc ch o v  trin khai  n Dy v hc ngoi trong h thng gio dc quc dn  i vi cc trng Tiu hc, hc ting Anh t lp 3 v lp 4, bi trn  thc t cc trng cn kh khn v CSVC v trnh  GV  chun theo quy  nh; iu chnh quy nh v mc thu ph hot ng ca Ban i din  CMHS khng c s dng  khen thng CB, GV, CNV trong nh trng,  bi ni dung  cha ph hp vi thc t, do  s gp kh khn trong  vic huy ng cc ngun lc x hi ha gio dc phc v cho hot ng  dy v hc trong cc nh trng; Cng tc tuyn dng GV  cc trng MN  bn cng chuyn sang cng lp v m bo thc hin ch  cho GVMN hng  lng ng theo ngch bc c o to; Cho pho cc tnh, thnh ph  ch ng quyt nh im ti thiu mn ngoi ng bt buc v cc mn  chuyn trong k thi tuyn sinh vo cc trng chuyn, lp chuyn THPT.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; font-size: 12pt;">ng  ch Nguyn Vinh Hin - Th trng B GD&amp;T hoan nghn tinh thn lm  vic theo hng i mi ca Hi ngh v khng nh Cm thi ua vng 7  lun xng ng l ngn c u trong c nc v GD&amp;T. Do , 5 thnh  ph cn thc hin tt hn na cc nhim v trng tm nm hc, l u  tu v GD&amp;T  cc tnh bn hc tp. B GD&amp;T lun ng h vi   n xy dng m hnh trng hc cht lng cao, cc tnh nn ch ng   xut, tham mu vi UBND Thnh ph v trin khai theo tnh hnh thc  t ca a phng. i vi cc khon thu gp, thu t nguyn cn thc  hin ng theo quy trnh, cng khai v qun l theo ng quy nh ca  php lut, trnh s hiu lm trong ph huynh hc sinh v khng ng vin  c ngun x hi ha.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; font-size: 12pt;">Thay  mt Lnh o 5 S GD&amp;T, ng ch Nguyn Hu  - Gim c S  GD&amp;T H Ni  tip thu  kin ch o ca cc ng ch Lnh o B  GD&amp;T, ng thi 5 S  k Giao c thi ua, th hin s quyt tm  thc hin tt nhim v nm hc 2011-2012.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; font-size: 12pt;">Chiu  cng ngy, cc i biu tip tc d 3 Hi tho chuyn : Xy dng m  hnh trng tin tin, cht lng cao (do S GD&amp;T TP H Ch Minh  ch tr), Cng tc xy dng i ng nh gio v cn b qun l (do S  GD&amp;T  Nng ch tr) v Gio dc np sng thanh lch - vn minh  cho hc sinh ph thng (do S GD&amp;T H Ni ch tr).</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: black;"><strong><em><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; font-size: 12pt;"><span> </span>Vn phng S GDHN<br /></span></em></strong></span></p>', '', -2, 14, 0, 156, '2011-10-22 08:20:40', 62, '', '2011-10-22 09:26:27', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 08:20:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 6, 'robots=\nauthor=');
