(110, 'K hoch tp hun cn b qun l trng THPT v ni dung nghin cu khoa hc s phm ng dng nm 2011', 'k-hoch-tp-hun-cn-b-qun-ly-trng-thpt-v-ni-dung-nghien-cu-khoa-hc-s-phm-ng-dng-nm-2011', '', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class="txtNhodi">\r\n<td>S t liu:</td>\r\n<td><strong>1009/KH-BGDT</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="txtNhodi">\r\n<td>Ngy ban hnh:</td>\r\n<td><strong>07-10-2011</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="txtNhodi">\r\n<td>Tp nh km:</td>\r\n<td><strong><a>1009KH.doc</a></strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span>Cn  c Ch th s 40-CT/TW ngy 15/6/2004 ca Ban B th Trung ng ng v  xy dng, nng cao cht lng i ng nh gio v cn b qun l gio  dc; </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span>Cn c K hoch 702/KH-BGDT ngy 10 thng 11 nm 2011 v vic tp hun <span>cn b qun l trng trung hc ph thng v ni dung Nghin cu khoa hc </span></span><span>s phm</span> ng dng n<span>m hc 2010 - 2011 </span>;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span>Cn c K hoch s 666/KH-BGDT  ngy 17 thng 02 nm 2011 ca B Gio dc v o to v Chng trnh  cng tc nm 2011 ca B Gio dc v o to;</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span>Cn c Cng vn s 5516/BGDT - NGCBQLGD v vic Hng dn nhim v xy dng i ng NG&amp;CBQLCSGD nm hc 2011  2012;</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span>B Gio dc v o to ban hnh K hoch t<span>p  hun v ni dung Nghin cu khoa hc s phm ng dng cho cn b qun  l gio dc trung hc ph thng nm 2011, c th nh sau:</span></span></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><strong>1. Mc ch</strong></div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span>- Gip cho cn b qun l cc  trng trung hc ph thng nhn thc v vai tro, vi tri cua  Nghin cu khoa hc s phm ng dng trong qua trinh i mi, nng  cao cht lng giao duc ph thng. </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span>- Gip cho cn b qun l cc  trng trung hc ph thng nm vng phng phap, quy trinh va co  ky nng tin hanh Nghin cu khoa hc s phm ng dng mt cach  hiu qua.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span>- Gip cho cn b qun l cc  trng trung hc ph thng co kha nng t chc hoat ng nghin  cu khoa hc s phm ng dng trong nha trng; t o vn ng,  thuc y cn b qun l va giao vin thc hin cac nghin cu  khoa hc s phm ng dng thng xuyn  tng bc nng cao cht  lng giao duc.</span></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><strong>2. Yu cu</strong></div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Vic t chct<span>p hun v ni dung nghin cu khoa hc </span>s phm<span> ng dng phi m bo ung quy trinh, khoa hoc va phu hp i tng.</span></p>', '', -2, 16, 0, 159, '2011-10-22 08:19:02', 62, '', '2011-10-22 09:26:56', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 08:19:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 6, '', '', 0, 16, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(109, 'Ngi trng thn yu', 'ngoi-trng-than-yeu', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;" class="content">\r\n<p class="c2 c2"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="data/giaoduc/Sukien/dsc_1609.jpg" alt="" height="364" width="549" /><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Ai v n huyn ng Anh, n gh thm phong cnh Loa Thnh Thc Vng.Trong mi chng ta ,ai cng  tng mt ln gh thm di tch lch s C Loa. Ngi trng thn yu m ti ang hc tp v rn luyn rt vinh d mang tn di tch lch s ny, vi truyn thuyt An Dng Vng M Chu Trng Thy.Trng THPT C Loa  tri qua 7 thy c lm hiu trng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="c2 c2"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">1 <em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Thy Phan Th</span></em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="c2 c2"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">2 Thy Phan Thc Ti<br /></span></em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="c2 c2"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">3 C Nguyn Th Y</span></em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="c2 c2"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">4 Thy Ng B Dc</span></em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="c2 c2"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">5 Thy T B Cnh</span></em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="c2 c2"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">6 Thy Nguyn Hu ng</span></em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="c2 c2"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">7 Thy Ng c Nm</span></em> (hin ang lm hiu trng)</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="c2 c2"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Qua 45 nm xy dng, pht trin v trng thnh trng  gt hi c rt nhiu thnh tch v vang. Cc anh ch kha trc t gii rt cao trong cc cuc thi in hnh nh:ch <strong><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Nguyn Th An</span></em></strong> t gii nh mn vn cp quc gia; anh <strong><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Nguyn Vn Mnh</span></em></strong> t gii 3 mn ton quc gia; anh <strong><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Nguyn Ph Huy</span></em></strong>  th khoa trng i hc bch khoa H Ni vi s im tuyt i 30/30... v&nbsp;rt nhiu cc gii khc qua cc nm hc..  c c s thnh cng  ta khng th khng nhc n i ng cc thy c gio ca trng.C <strong><em>Phm Th Ngc Hu</em></strong> (b mn ton),c <strong><em>Trn Th Tu</em></strong>, c <strong><em>Nguyn Th Nhung</em></strong> (b mn vn),thy <strong><em>Trn Qu Nam</em></strong>, thy <strong><em>Nguyn Kh Th</em></strong> (b mn l),thy <strong><em>ng Thanh m</em></strong>(b mn ha),c <strong><em>Nguyn Th Thuy</em></strong>,c <strong><em> Th Phng</em></strong> (b mn sinh)...vv cng rt nhiu cc thy c gio dy gii khc  rt nhit tnh trong s nghip trng ngi ca mnh.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2011-10-22 08:07:55', 62, '', '2012-04-10 11:55:52', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 08:07:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 7, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 236, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(108, 'Hai hc sinh C Loa c Ch Tch nc trao gii thng Hoa Trng Nguyn!', 'hai-hc-sinh-c-loa-c-ch-tch-nc-trao-gii-thng-hoa-trng-nguyen', '', '<div style="text-align: justify;" class="content">\r\n<p>Hai hc sinh C Loa vinh d c gii Hoa Trng Nguyn l em o Thanh Tng 29,5 im th khoa i Hc Kinh T Quc Dn v em Nguyn Ngc H 28,5 im th khoa Hc Vin Quan H Quc T. Gii thng c ch thn ch tch nc Nguyn Minh Trit trao tng. Mt vinh d v t ho l ton thnh ph H Ni ch c trng THPT Chuyn H Ni- Amsterdam v THPT C Loa lm c iu ny.</p>\r\n<p>c bit hai em o Thanh Tng v Nguyn Ngc H  tng t gii ba k thi Hc sinh gii Thnh ph H Ni v nhiu nm lin l hc sinh gii ton din ca lp A1, THPT C Loa, Kha 2006-2009.</p>\r\n<p>Cc em c th xem thm:</p>\r\n(<strong>Sng 13/9, ti i hc Quc gia H Ni din ra L trao gii thng v tn vinh 852 Hoa Trng Nguyn 2009 ca 27 tnh, thnh ph khu vc pha Bc.</strong>\r\n<table class="c5" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="2">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p class="c1"><strong><img src="http://vtv6.com.vn/uploads/HoatrangNguyen3.jpg" border="0" height="352" width="514" /></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: justify;" class="c4">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;" class="c3"><em><span class="c2">Ch tch nc Nguyn Minh Trit <br />trao Gii thng Hoa Trng Nguyn</span></em></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="c6">y l nhng hc sinh t thnh tch: xut sc nht cc trng THPT; gii nht k thi hc sinh gii quc gia THPT cc mn vn ha; ot huy chng trong cc k thi Olympic Quc t v th khoa u vo cc trng i hc, hc vin nm 2009.</p>\r\nTham d bui l c Ch tch nc Nguyn Minh Trit, Ph Ch tch Quc hi Ung Chu Lu v i din lnh o su n v ng t chc Gii thng Hoa Trng Nguyn l Ban Tuyn gio Trung ng, Trung ng on, B Gio dc &amp; o to, i hc Quc gia H Ni, Hip hi cc trng i hc, cao ng ngoi cng lp v Tp on Tn to.\r\n<p class="c6">Pht biu ti bui l, Ch tch nc Nguyn Minh Trit by t vui mng trc nhng thnh tch m cc Hoa Trng Nguyn  t c trong nm qua.</p>\r\n<p class="c6">So vi nm 2008, s Hoa Trng Nguyn nm 2009  n r hn, tng thm 10 phn trm. iu ny cho thy tc ng ca gii thng ti phong tro thi ua hc tt  khp cc trng THPT trong c nc.</p>\r\n<p class="c6">Thnh tch m cc Hoa Trng Nguyn t c cng chnh l nim t ho ca th h tr Vit Nam hm nay vi kht vng vn ln khng nh bn lnh v tr tu Vit Nam snh vai vi cc cng quc nm chu nh Bc H mong c.</p>\r\n<p class="c6">Nm 2009 c nc c 1.655 hc sinh c tn vinh v trao gii thng Hoa Trng Nguyn, trong  min Bc 852 em, min Trung 195 em v min Nam 608 em.</p>\r\n<p class="c6">Nt mi gii thng nm nay l mi em t huy chng trong cc k thi hc sinh gii quc t s c Tp on Tn To ti tr mt b my vi tnh xch tay.</p>\r\n<p class="c6">500 em nhn gii thng Hoa Trng Nguyn 2008 v nm 2009 s c c hi c Hi ng Gii thng xt chn cp hc bng Ting Anh v hc bng ton phn vo Trng i hc Tn To nin kha 2010 - 2011 tr gi 16.000 USD - 27.500 USD/ nm v c hi hc tp ti cc trng i hc danh ting ca Hoa K lin kt vi Trng i hc Tn To.</p>\r\n<p class="c6">Ngy hi Hoa Trng Nguyn v L trao gii thng Hoa Trng Nguyn 2009 khu vc min Nam c t chc ngy 19-20/9; khu vc min Trung c t chc vo 26/9.</p>\r\n<p class="c7">Theo TTXVN</p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 4, 0, 25, '2011-10-22 07:52:34', 62, '', '2012-04-10 12:25:32', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-22 07:52:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 17, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 273, 'robots=\nauthor='),
