(100, 'Thnh C Loa - Kinh  ca nh nc u Lc', 'qua-trinh-phat-trin-trng-ptth-c-loa', '', '<div class="article-contents" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<div id="ctl00_mContent_pnImgCaption">\r\n<div class="img">\r\n<table style="border-width: 0px; float: left; width: 310px;" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="border-width: 0px; border-color: White;">\r\n<p><img src="http://hanoi.vietnamplus.vn/avatar.aspx?ID=127&amp;at=0&amp;ts=300&amp;lm=633898318680670000" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid;" border="0" height="257" width="342" /></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="border-width: 0px; border-color: White; text-align: center;" align="center" width="300px; text-align:center;"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>Thnh C Loa thuc x C Loa, huyn ng Anh, H Ni, l kinh  ca nh nc u Lc (tn nc Vit Nam thi ), di thi An Dng Vng vo khong th k th III trc Cng nguyn v ca nh nc Vn Xun (tn nc Vit Nam thi ) di thi Ng Quyn th k X sau Cng nguyn.<br /> <br /> Nm 1962, thnh C Loa c Nh nc xp hng di tch lch s vn ha cp quc gia.<br /> <br /> <strong>V tr a l</strong><br /> <strong> </strong><br /> <strong> </strong>Vo thi u Lc, C Loa nm vo v tr nh ca tam gic chu th sng Hng v l ni giao lu quan trng ca ng thy v ng b. T y c th kim sot c c vng ng bng ln vng sn a. <br /> <br /> C Loa l mt khu t i cao ro nm  t ngn sng Hong. Sng Hong (tc sng Thip) l mt con sng nhnh ln quan trng ca sng Hng, ni lin sng Hng vi sng Cu trong h thng sng Thi Bnh.<br /> <br /> V phng din giao thng ng thy, C Loa c mt v tr v cng thun li.  l v tr ni lin mng li ng thy ca sng Hng cng vi mng li ng thy ca sng Thi Bnh. <br /> <br /> Qua con sng Hong, thuyn b ngc ln sng Hng l vo vng Bc hay Ty Bc ca Bc B, nu xui sng Hng, thuyn ra n bin c, nu n vng pha ng Bc b th qua sng Cu vo h thng sng Thi Bnh n sng Thng v sng Lc Nam.<br /> <br /> a im C Loa chnh l t Phong Kh, lc  l mt vng ng bng tr ph c xm lng, dn c ng c, sng bng ngh lm rung, nh c v th cng nghip. Vic di  t Phong Chu v y, nh du mt giai on pht trin ca dn c Vit c, giai on ngi Vit chuyn trung tm quyn lc t vng Trung du bn sn a v nh c ti vng ng bng.<br /> <br /> <strong>Cu trc Thnh C Loa</strong><br /> <br /> Thnh C Loa c cc nh kho c hc nh gi l "ta thnh c nht, quy m ln vo bc nht, cu trc cng thuc loi c o nht trong lch s xy dng thnh ly ca ngi Vit c".<br /> <br /> Khi xy thnh, ngi Vit c  bit li dng a hnh t nhin, tn dng chiu cao ca cc i, g, p thm t cho cao hn  xy nn hai bc tng thnh pha ngoi, v th hai bc tng thnh ny c ng nt un ln theo a hnh.<br /> <br /> Cht liu ch yu dng  xy thnh l t, sau  l  v gm v.  c dng  k cho chn thnh c vng chc. Cc on thnh ven sng, ven m c k nhiu  hn cc on khc. <br /> <br />  k l loi  tng ln v  cui c ch ti t cc min khc. Xen gia m t  l nhng lp gm c ri dy mng khc nhau, nhiu nht l  chn thnh v ra thnh  chng st l.<br /> <br /> Thnh C Loa theo tng truyn gm 9 vng xoy trn c, nhng hin cn 3 vng thnh. Chu vi vng Ngoi 8km, vng Trung 6,5km, vng Ni 1,65km, din tch trung tm ln ti 2km<sup>2</sup>.<br /> <br /> Thnh c xy theo phng php o t n u, khot ho n , thnh p n u, ly xy n . Mt ngoi ly, dc thng ng, mt trong xoi  nh vo th kh, trong nh ra th d. Ly cao trung bnh t 4m-5m, c ch cao n 8m-12m. Chn ly rng 20m-30m, mt ly rng 6m-12m. <br /> <br /> + Thnh Ni hnh ch nht, cao trung bnh 5m so vi mt t, mt thnh rng t 6m-12m, chn rng t 20m-30m, chu vi 1.650m v c mt ca nhn vo ta kin trc Ng triu di quy.<br /> <br /> Hin nay, qua cng lng, cng l cng thnh Ni l ti nh lng C Loa. Theo truyn thuyt th  l nn c ca in ng triu, ni b quan hi triu nn trong nh cn tm honh phi "Ng triu di quy". Cnh nh l Am B Cha tc l miu th cng cha M Chu, trong am c mt tng  hnh ngi ct u, l tng M Chu.<br /> <br /> Qua am M Chu ti n Thng, tc n An Dng Vng, tng truyn l dng trn nn ni cung ngy trc. n ny mi trng tu, tn to u th k XX, c i rng   bc tam cp ca n l di vt i Trn. <br /> <br /> Trong n c tng An Dng Vng bng ng. Trc n l Ging Ngc, tng truyn l ni Trng Thu t t v hi hn. Nc ging ny m em ra ngc trai th ngc sng bi phn.<br /> <br /> Ni y, c y  cc loi hnh di tch: nh, n, cha, am, miu. Trong  hm cha bit bao gi tr vn ha Vit Nam qua bao th h.<br /> <br /> + Thnh Trung l mt vng thnh khng c khun hnh cn xng, chu vi 6.500m, ni cao nht l 10m, mt thnh rng trung bnh 10m, c nm ca  cc hng ng, nam, bc, ty bc v ty nam, trong  ca ng n thng vi sng Hong.<br /> <br /> + Thnh Ngoi khng cn hnh dng r rng, chu vi hn 8.000m, cao trung bnh 3m-4m (c ch ti hn 8m).<br /> <br /> Mi vng thnh u c ho nc bao quanh bn ngoi, ho rng trung bnh t 10m n 30m. Cc vng ho u thng vi nhau v thng vi sng Hong. S kt hp ca sng, ho v tng thnh khng c hnh dng nht nh, khin thnh nh mt m cung, l mt khu qun s va thun li cho tn cng va tt cho phng th.<br /> <br /> Sng Hong c dng lm ho thin nhin cho thnh Ngoi  v pha Ty Nam v Nam. Phn ho cn li c o st chn tng thnh t g Ct C n m C. Con ho ny ni vi ho ca thnh Trung  m C v Xm Mt, chy qua ca Cng Song ni vi nm con lch, vo vng ho ca thnh Ni. Thuyn b i li d dng trn ba vng ho  n tr u  m C hoc ra sng Hong v t  c th ta i khp ni. <br /> <br /> Theo truyn thuyt, An Dng Vng thng dng thuyn i khp cc ho ri ra sng Hong.<br /> <br /> <strong>Gi tr ca thnh C Loa</strong><br /> <br /> Trong cu trc chung ca thnh C Loa cn c mt yu t khc lm phong ph thm tng th kin trc ny.  l nhng g t di hoc trn c p ri rc gia cc vng thnh hoc nm ngoi thnh Ngoi, c dn chng gi l ng Dn, ng Chung, ng Bn. Cc , ly ny c dng lm cng s, c nhim v ca nhng pho i tin v, phi hp vi thnh, ho trong vic bo v v chin u.<br /> <br /> V mt qun s, thnh C Loa th hin s sng to c o ca ngi Vit c trong cng cuc gi nc v chng ngoi xm. Vi cc bc thnh kin c, vi ho su rng cng cc , ly, C Loa l mt cn c phng th vng chc  bo v nh vua, triu nh v kinh . ng thi l mt cn c kt hp hi ha thy binh cng b binh, khi tc chin.<br /> <br /> V mt x hi, vi s phn b tng khu c tr cho vua, quan, binh lnh, thnh C Loa l mt chng c v s phn ha ca x hi thi y. Thi k ny, vua quan khng nhng  tch khi dn chng m cn phi c bo v cht ch, x hi  c giai cp r rng hn thi Vua Hng.<br /> <br /> V mt vn ha, l mt ta thnh c nht cn  li du tch, C Loa tr thnh mt di sn vn ha, mt bng chng v s sng to, v trnh  k thut cng nh vn ha ca ngi Vit C.  k chn thnh, gm ri ra thnh, ho nc quanh co,  ly phc tp, ha mai chc chn v nht l a hnh him tr ngon ngoo, tt c lm nn ngh thut kin trc v vn ha thi An Dng Vng.<br /> <br /> <strong>Di vt kho c</strong><br /> <br /> Trn khu vc thnh C Loa, cc nh kho c  khai qut c nhiu m c, hng vn mi tn ng ba cnh, ru li xo bng ng, tin ng, li cy, cc vt dng bng gm, t nung v trng ng C Loa t thi An Dng Vng. <br /> <br /> Cc nh kho c  pht hin c di tch ni c tr  tn ti trc khi xy dng thnh C Loa thuc bui u thi i  st./.</div>\r\n<p class="author" style="text-align: right;"><strong><span id="ctl00_mContent_lbSource">(TTXVN/Vietnam+)</span></strong></p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2011-10-21 17:00:00', 62, '', '2012-04-10 12:09:56', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-10-21 17:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 9, 0, 6, '', '', 0, 124, 'robots=\nauthor='),
